// chapters.js — Full chapter data for all 4 classical novels
// Merged into BOOKS via mergeChapters() at startup

const CHAPTERS = {

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
   水浒传 WATER MARGIN  (120 chapters)
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ */
shuihu: [
{id:1,title:"张天师祈禳瘟疫，洪太尉误走妖魔",english:"The Heavenly Master Prays Against Plague; Marshal Hong Accidentally Releases the Demons",content:"仁宗天子在位，天下瘟疫盛行，洪太尉奉旨前往江西龙虎山宣请张天师。洪太尉骄横傲慢，不听劝阻，强行打开伏魔殿石碑，惊走了镇压在内的一百零八个魔君。这一百零八个魔君散入人间，日后化为梁山一百零八条好汉。\nDuring the reign of Emperor Renzong, plague swept the land and Marshal Hong was sent to Mount Longhu to summon the Heavenly Master Zhang. Arrogant and headstrong, Hong ignored warnings and broke the seal on the Temple of Subdued Demons, releasing 108 devil spirits into the world. These spirits would later be reborn as the 108 heroes of Liangshan."},
{id:2,title:"王教头私走延安府，九纹龙大闹史家村",english:"Instructor Wang Flees to Yan'an; Nine-Tattooed Dragon Raises Hell at Shi Family Village",content:"八十万禁军教头王进因高俅迫害，携母连夜出走，投奔延安府老种经略相公。途中在史家庄借宿，见史进每日习武，王进指点其武艺，传授真本领。史进因此武艺大进，被人称为\"九纹龙\"。\nWang Jin, drill instructor of the Imperial Guards, flees with his mother to escape persecution by Gao Qiu, heading for the northern frontier. He stops at the Shi family estate where young Shi Jin trains daily; Wang secretly coaches him and transforms his fighting skill. Shi Jin earns the nickname 'Nine-Tattooed Dragon' for the dragon tattoos covering his body."},
{id:3,title:"史大郎夜走华阴县，鲁提辖拳打镇关西",english:"Shi Jin Flees by Night; Lu the Major Beats the Bully Zheng",content:"史进在少华山结交朱武等人，被官府追捕，夜走华阴县。在渭州，史进偶遇老友李忠和鲁达，三人把酒言欢。鲁达得知金翠莲父女被郑屠欺压，义愤填膺，三拳打死镇关西郑屠，随即出逃。\nShi Jin falls in with outlaws on Mount Shaohua and flees by night to Weizhou, where he reunites with his friend Lu Da, a garrison major. Learning that the butcher Zheng has been extorting and abusing a father and daughter, the hot-blooded Lu Da confronts Zheng and kills him with three mighty punches. Lu Da immediately goes on the run."},
{id:4,title:"赵员外重修文殊院，鲁智深大闹五台山",english:"Squire Zhao Funds the Monastery; Lu Zhishen Causes Havoc on Mount Wutai",content:"鲁达逃至代州雁门县，得赵员外资助，在五台山文殊院剃度为僧，法名智深。鲁智深本性难改，屡次醉酒闹事，大闹五台山，打坏金刚，监寺无奈。智清长老只得让他离开，写书信介绍他去东京大相国寺安身。\nLu Da takes refuge with Squire Zhao, who sponsors his ordination as a monk at Wutai Monastery under the name Zhishen — 'Profound Wisdom.' But the warrior-monk cannot contain his nature; he repeatedly gets drunk and brawls, smashing statues and terrorizing the monks. The abbot reluctantly sends him away with a letter of introduction to the Great Xiangguo Temple in the capital."},
{id:5,title:"小霸王醉入销金帐，花和尚大闹桃花村",english:"The Little Overlord Drunkenly Enters the Bridal Chamber; the Tattooed Monk Disrupts Peach Blossom Village",content:"鲁智深赴东京途中，在桃花村借宿，得知庄主刘太公之女被山寨强人周通强娶。鲁智深深夜代替新娘坐入洞房，痛打了周通一顿。次日，周通师父李忠赶到，鲁智深与其相认，劝说周通放弃婚事，保全了刘家女儿。\nOn the road to the capital, Zhishen stops at Peach Blossom Village where the bandit Zhou Tong is forcing a farmer's daughter into marriage. That night Zhishen disguises himself as the bride and thrashes Zhou Tong soundly. The next day Zhou Tong's master Li Zhong arrives; recognizing an old friend, Zhishen persuades Zhou Tong to abandon his claim on the girl."},
{id:6,title:"花和尚倒拔垂杨柳，豹子头误入白虎堂",english:"The Tattooed Monk Uproots a Willow Tree; Leopard Head Is Lured into the White Tiger Hall",content:"鲁智深到东京大相国寺，被派去看管菜园。一群泼皮无赖前来欺负他，智深轻松将二人倒提扔入粪坑。众人服气，后来智深倒拔垂杨柳，令众人惊叹。禁军教头林冲与鲁智深结为兄弟，不久林冲被高俅之子设计陷害，误入白虎堂。\nZhishen is assigned to guard the temple's vegetable garden, where local toughs try to bully him — he hurls two of them into the manure pit. When he uproots a massive willow tree bare-handed, everyone is awed. He befriends Lin Chong, a top military instructor, but Lin Chong is soon framed by Gao Qiu's son, lured into the restricted White Tiger Hall and arrested."},
{id:7,title:"林教头刺配沧州道，鲁智深大闹野猪林",english:"Instructor Lin Is Exiled to Cangzhou; Zhishen Saves Him at Wild Boar Forest",content:"林冲被刺配沧州，押解途中，董超薛霸受高俅指使，在野猪林欲杀害林冲。危急时刻，鲁智深从树上跳下，救下林冲，一路护送至沧州。林冲感激万分，与鲁智深洒泪分别，踏上配所之路。\nConvicted on false charges, Lin Chong is tattooed and sent into exile. His guards, bribed by Gao Qiu, plan to murder him at Wild Boar Forest. Zhishen, who has secretly followed to protect his friend, leaps from a tree and drives off the would-be killers. The two friends part in tears as Lin Chong continues to his place of exile."},
{id:8,title:"柴进门招天下客，林冲棒打洪教头",english:"Lord Chai Welcomes Heroes; Lin Chong Defeats Instructor Hong",content:"林冲发配途中，路过柴进庄上，受到热情款待。庄内教头洪教头自恃武艺高强，瞧不起林冲，一再挑衅。林冲谦让再三，最终出手，三下五除二便将洪教头打倒在地，令众人刮目相看。柴进厚赐林冲盘缠，送他继续上路。\nPassing through the estate of the generous Lord柴 Chai Jin, Lin Chong receives warm hospitality. The arrogant resident instructor Hong repeatedly goads Lin Chong into a match, dismissing the exile as a broken man. Lin Chong humbly deflects until honor demands he respond — then defeats Hong easily with minimal effort. Chai Jin sends Lin Chong off with generous travel money."},
{id:9,title:"林教头风雪山神庙，陆虞候火烧草料场",english:"Lin Chong at the Snowy Mountain God Temple; Lu the Spy Burns the Fodder Depot",content:"林冲发配沧州，在草料场看守。管营差拨受高俅指示，欲置林冲于死地，趁大雪天点火烧草料场。林冲因去山神庙避寒，幸免于难，却在庙内听到陆谦等人谈论害他的阴谋。林冲怒不可遏，冲出庙门，杀死陆谦等三人，雪夜奔上梁山。\nLin Chong is assigned to guard a military fodder depot in the bitter cold. His enemies arrange for the depot to be set on fire while he is inside — but he has stepped out to shelter in a mountain god temple. Overhearing Lu Qian and the others boasting about the plot, Lin Chong's patience finally breaks. He kills all three conspirators and flees through the snow to Liangshan."},
{id:10,title:"朱贵水亭施号箭，林冲雪夜上梁山",english:"Zhu Gui Signals with Arrows at the Waterside Pavilion; Lin Chong Ascends Liangshan in the Snow",content:"林冲雪夜出逃，来到梁山泊水边，遇到朱贵开设的酒店。朱贵发出暗号，引林冲渡水上山。林冲见到王伦，请求入伙。王伦嫉妒林冲武艺，出难题要他献投名状，林冲无奈，只得寻人打斗。后经柴进书信，王伦勉强收留了林冲。\nFleeing through the snow, Lin Chong reaches the shore of Liangshan Marsh where Zhu Gui operates a waterside inn as a scout. Signaled across, Lin Chong meets the chief Wang Lun and asks to join. Wang Lun, jealous of Lin Chong's superior skill, demands he bring a 'blood offering' — a head — before he can stay. Thanks to a letter from Chai Jin, Wang Lun reluctantly accepts him."},
{id:11,title:"梁山泊林冲落草，汴京城杨志卖刀",english:"Lin Chong Joins the Outlaws; Yang Zhi Sells His Sword in the Capital",content:"林冲上了梁山，王伦对他并不重用，只给了个末位。另一边，杨志因丢失花石纲获罪，被赦后流落汴京，无以为生，只得街头卖刀。杨志曾是名将之后，心怀抱负，却屡遭挫折，卖刀时遇上泼皮牛二寻衅，杨志忍无可忍，怒杀牛二，自首入狱。\nOn Liangshan, Lin Chong is given little respect by the jealous chief Wang Lun. Meanwhile in the capital, Yang Zhi — a disgraced officer who lost a precious shipment — drifts penniless and tries to sell his ancestral sword on the street. When the street thug Niu Er relentlessly provokes him, Yang Zhi kills him and surrenders himself to the authorities."},
{id:12,title:"梁中书留守大名府，杨志押送金银担",english:"Governor Liang Retains His Post in Daming; Yang Zhi Escorts the Birthday Treasure",content:"杨志被发配大名府，展示武艺获得梁中书赏识，被委以押送生辰纲的重任。梁中书为蔡京准备的生辰纲价值连城，杨志深知责任重大，制定了严密的押运方案，伪装成商队出行，一路小心谨慎。\nYang Zhi wins favor with Governor Liang Zhongshu in Daming Prefecture by demonstrating his fighting skill. He is entrusted with escorting the birthday treasure — a fortune in gold and gifts — to the Prime Minister Cai Jing in the capital. Knowing the stakes, Yang Zhi disguises the convoy as merchants and pushes his men hard through the summer heat, making enemies of them in the process."},
{id:13,title:"赤发鬼醉卧灵官殿，晁天王认义东溪村",english:"The Red-Haired Devil Sleeps Drunk in the Temple; King Chao Swears Brotherhood at East Creek Village",content:"刘唐得知生辰纲消息，找到晁盖报信。晁盖与吴用、公孙胜、三阮等七人共谋劫取生辰纲。晁盖结义东溪村，众豪杰意气相投，推晁盖为首，定下智取生辰纲之计。\nLiu Tang, the Red-Haired Devil, brings news of the treasure convoy to Chao Gai. Chao Gai joins forces with the strategist Wu Yong, the wizard Gongsun Sheng, and the three Ruan brothers to plan a robbery. Seven sworn brothers gather at East Creek Village and, with Chao Gai as their chief, Wu Yong devises an ingenious scheme to seize the birthday treasure."},
{id:14,title:"吴学究说三阮撞筹，公孙胜应七星聚义",english:"Wu Yong Recruits the Three Ruans; Gongsun Sheng Joins the Seven Stars",content:"吴用前往石碣村说服三阮兄弟入伙，三人本是渔民，武艺高强，痛快答应。公孙胜也从蓟州赶来，七星好汉聚齐，共同谋划在黄泥冈劫取生辰纲。众人分工明确，各司其职，做好了万全准备。\nWu Yong travels to Shijie Village to recruit the three Ruan brothers — fishermen of extraordinary courage — who eagerly agree. The wizard Gongsun Sheng arrives from Ji Prefecture, completing the group of seven. Together they refine the plan to ambush the convoy at Yellow Earth Ridge, each man assigned a precise role in the scheme."},
{id:15,title:"杨志押送金银担，吴用智取生辰纲",english:"Yang Zhi Escorts the Treasure; Wu Yong Cleverly Seizes the Birthday Gifts",content:"黄泥冈上，烈日炎炎，押运队伍疲惫不堪。吴用等人扮成贩枣商人，白胜扮作卖酒小贩，趁机在酒中下了蒙汗药。杨志防范严密，却终究没有识破计谋，全队中药昏倒，生辰纲被劫一空。杨志醒后惶恐，不敢回京，只得落草为寇。\nAt Yellow Earth Ridge under blazing sun, the exhausted convoy encounters 'date merchants' — Wu Yong's gang in disguise. White Victory sells drugged wine; despite Yang Zhi's suspicions, the entire convoy drinks and collapses. Yang Zhi awakens to find the treasure gone. Too ashamed to return, he becomes an outlaw."},
{id:16,title:"花荣小李广神箭，宋江私放晁天王",english:"Hua Rong the Little Li Guang Shows His Archery; Song Jiang Secretly Releases Chao Gai",content:"晁盖等人事泄，官府追捕。押司宋江暗中通风报信，使晁盖等人得以逃脱。晁盖一行奔上梁山，与王伦起了冲突。林冲忍无可忍，杀了王伦，推晁盖坐第一把交椅，梁山从此声势大振。\nThe Liangshan robbery is traced back to Chao Gai's group. The clerk Song Jiang secretly warns them, allowing their escape to Liangshan Marsh. There the newcomers clash with the jealous chief Wang Lun; Lin Chong, fed up with Wang Lun's pettiness, kills him and installs Chao Gai as the rightful leader. Liangshan's power grows rapidly."},
{id:17,title:"美髯公智稳插翅虎，宋公明私放晁天王",english:"Lord of the Beautiful Beard Calms the Winged Tiger; Song Jiang Releases Chao Gai",content:"宋江在郓城县做押司，为人仗义疏财，人称\"及时雨\"。宋江私放了晁盖等人，此事后来被人告发。与此同时，宋江结识了朱仝、雷横等好汉，在江湖上威望日隆，众多好汉都与他往来结交。\nSong Jiang serves as a clerk in Yuncheng County, famed for his generosity with money and nicknamed 'Timely Rain.' His secret warning to Chao Gai is eventually reported to authorities. Meanwhile Song Jiang builds wide connections among heroes — Zhu Tong, Lei Heng, and others — earning a towering reputation throughout the outlaw world."},
{id:18,title:"美髯公智稳插翅虎，宋公明私放晁天王",english:"Song Jiang Meets Yan Poxi; the Trouble with the Letter",content:"宋江与阎婆惜私通，阎婆惜发现了宋江私放晁盖的书信，以此要挟。宋江一怒之下，怒杀阎婆惜，随即出逃，踏上了亡命天涯的道路。从此宋江走上了与官府对立的不归路，注定要汇入梁山好汉的行列。\nSong Jiang's mistress Yan Poxi discovers the incriminating letter about Chao Gai and threatens blackmail. In a rage, Song Jiang kills her and flees. This act of violence sets him irrevocably on the outlaw path, and his eventual destiny with the heroes of Liangshan becomes inevitable."},
{id:19,title:"林冲水寨大并火，晁盖梁山小夺泊",english:"Lin Chong Burns the Water Camp; Chao Gai Takes Control of the Marsh",content:"梁山势力逐步扩大，晁盖在林冲等人辅佐下将梁山泊经营得有声有色。各路好汉闻风归附，山寨人马日益增多。梁山好汉打退了多次官府的围剿，声威震动四方，成为令朝廷头痛的一大势力。\nUnder Chao Gai's leadership, supported by Lin Chong and others, Liangshan grows into a formidable stronghold. Heroes from across the land flock to join them. The outlaws repel several government campaigns against them, their reputation spreading fear throughout the empire and causing no end of trouble for the imperial court."},
{id:20,title:"虔婆醉打唐牛儿，宋江怒杀阎婆惜",english:"The Procuress Beats Tang Niu Er; Song Jiang Kills Yan Poxi in Fury",content:"阎婆以女儿阎婆惜为饵，缠住宋江。阎婆惜嫌宋江貌丑，与小白脸张文远私通。一日宋江取信，发现了那封要命的书信，阎婆惜抓住把柄不肯松手。宋江盛怒之下抽刀杀了她，这成为他人生的重大转折点。\nThe procuress Yan Po uses her daughter Yan Poxi to entrap Song Jiang, but Yan Poxi prefers the handsome Zhang Wenyuan. When Song Jiang comes to retrieve a vital letter, Yan Poxi seizes it as blackmail leverage. Song Jiang, pushed beyond endurance, draws his knife and kills her — a pivotal turning point that seals his fate as a fugitive."},
{id:21,title:"阎婆大闹郓城县，朱仝义释宋公明",english:"Old Yan Creates an Uproar in Yuncheng; Zhu Tong Nobly Releases Song Jiang",content:"宋江杀人后被捕入狱，阎婆到处哭闹告状。狱卒朱仝、雷横同情宋江，朱仝私下放走宋江，让他逃往柴进庄上躲避。宋江在柴进庄暂时安身，结识了武松，两人一见如故，结下了深厚的兄弟情谊。\nAfter killing Yan Poxi, Song Jiang is jailed while old Yan Po wails for justice. The sympathetic jailer Zhu Tong secretly releases Song Jiang, who flees to Chai Jin's estate. There he meets Wu Song — the two men take an immediate liking to each other and form a deep bond of brotherhood."},
{id:22,title:"横海郡柴进留宾，景阳冈武松打虎",english:"Chai Jin Entertains Guests; Wu Song Kills the Tiger on Jingyang Ridge",content:"武松在柴进庄上住了近一年，后来听说兄长武大郎在阳谷县，便告别宋江和柴进回乡。途经景阳冈，不信官府告示，独自上冈，凭借神力和胆魄，赤手空拳打死了祸害一方的老虎。武松因此威名大振，被任命为阳谷县都头。\nWu Song spends nearly a year at Chai Jin's estate before heading home to his brother in Yanggu County. At Jingyang Ridge, ignoring warnings about a man-eating tiger, he climbs the mountain alone. Drunk but ferocious, he beats the enormous tiger to death with his fists after his club breaks. He is appointed a constable in Yanggu County on the strength of this feat."},
{id:23,title:"王婆贪贿说风情，郓哥不忿闹茶肆",english:"Widow Wang Greedily Plots Romance; Yun Ge Stirs Up the Tea House",content:"武松兄长武大郎娶了潘金莲，潘金莲生得美貌，对丑矮的武大郎不满。西门庆见色起意，王婆从中撮合，潘金莲与西门庆私通。卖梨小贩郓哥见此不平，告知武大郎，武大郎捉奸反被西门庆踢伤。\nWu Song's brother Wu Dalang has a beautiful wife, Pan Jinlian, who despises her ugly, short husband. The merchant Ximen Qing lusts after her, and the procuress Wang Po arranges their affair. The boy Yunge sees the injustice and tells Wu Dalang, who tries to confront the lovers — only to be kicked and badly injured by Ximen Qing."},
{id:24,title:"王婆计啜西门庆，潘金莲毒鸩武大郎",english:"Wang Po Schemes for Ximen Qing; Pan Jinlian Poisons Wu Dalang",content:"武大郎卧床养伤，潘金莲却趁机在汤药中下毒，毒死了武大郎。西门庆与王婆将武大郎草草掩埋，销毁证据。武松出差归来，察觉兄长死得蹊跷，开始暗中调查，决心为兄报仇雪恨。\nAs Wu Dalang lies injured in bed, Pan Jinlian poisons him. She and Ximen Qing bury him hastily to destroy evidence. Wu Song returns from an official trip and, sensing something wrong about his brother's sudden death, begins a quiet investigation, vowing vengeance."},
{id:25,title:"郓哥大闹授刑场，武松斗杀西门庆",english:"Yunge Causes a Scene; Wu Song Kills Ximen Qing",content:"武松通过郓哥取得人证物证，状告潘金莲和西门庆，但知县收受了西门庆的贿赂，拒绝受理。武松忍无可忍，在狮子楼摆下酒宴，当众杀死了西门庆，又回家斩杀了潘金莲，将两颗人头供在兄长灵前祭奠。\nWith Yunge's help, Wu Song gathers evidence and files a complaint, but the magistrate is bribed and dismisses the case. Wu Song takes justice into his own hands: he lures Ximen Qing to Lion Tower and kills him, then returns home and beheads Pan Jinlian, placing both heads before his brother's spirit tablet as an offering."},
{id:26,title:"偷骨殖何九叔送丧，供人头武二郎设祭",english:"Coroner He Hides the Evidence; Wu Song Makes Sacrifice with the Severed Heads",content:"武松杀人后自首，被刺配孟州。在孟州，张都监对武松礼遇有加，武松感激涕零，誓死效命。然而这一切不过是张都监的阴谋，他设计陷害武松偷盗财物，将武松再次投入大牢，准备置之死地。\nAfter surrendering himself, Wu Song is tattooed and exiled to Mengzhou. There Commandant Zhang treats him with great generosity, and Wu Song pledges his life in gratitude. But it is all a trap: Zhang has Wu Song framed for theft and thrown into prison, intending to have him killed."},
{id:27,title:"武松威镇安平寨，施恩义夺快活林",english:"Wu Song Dominates the Prison Camp; Shi En Reclaims Happy Forest",content:"在孟州牢城，施恩对武松特别照顾，讲述了快活林酒店被蒋门神霸占的事。武松感念施恩之德，主动提出为他夺回快活林。武松大碗喝酒，醉打蒋门神，凭借神威将蒋门神打得落花流水，夺回了快活林。\nIn Mengzhou prison, the warden's son Shi En treats Wu Song well and tells him how the bully Jiang the Gate God has seized his tavern, Happy Forest. Grateful, Wu Song volunteers to win it back. Drinking enormously at every stop along the way, Wu Song storms Happy Forest and beats Jiang the Gate God into submission with drunken ferocity."},
{id:28,title:"武松醉打孔亮，宋江怒杀阎婆",english:"Wu Song Beats Kong Liang Drunk; The Road to Mount Er Long",content:"张都监设宴款待武松，席间将家中丫鬟玉兰介绍给他，武松心存感激。然而当夜张都监设下陷阱，诬陷武松行窃，再次将他捉拿下狱，判以重刑。武松在押送途中识破了押解人要杀他的阴谋，奋起反抗。\nCommandant Zhang hosts a banquet for Wu Song and introduces him to the maid Yulan, hinting at a future match. That very night Zhang springs his trap, framing Wu Song for burglary and having him rearrested with a sentence of death. On the road to execution, Wu Song discovers the plot to kill him en route."},
{id:29,title:"施恩重霸快活林，武松醉打孔亮",english:"Shi En Reclaims Happy Forest; Wu Song Fights on the Road",content:"武松在解差的看押下前往配所，察觉到两名解差意图在路途中将他杀死。武松在飞云浦将两解差杀死，随即返回鸳鸯楼，斩杀了张都监、张团练、蒋门神等仇人，在墙上血书\"杀人者打虎武松也\"，随后出逃。\nWu Song sees through his escort guards' plan to kill him at Flying Cloud Ford and turns on them, killing both. He then returns to the Mandarin Duck Pavilion and systematically slaughters Commandant Zhang, his conspirators, and Jiang the Gate God — writing in blood on the wall, 'Killer: Wu Song the Tiger Slayer,' then escapes."},
{id:30,title:"张都监血溅鸳鸯楼，武行者夜走蜈蚣岭",english:"Zhang's Blood Stains the Mandarin Duck Pavilion; Pilgrim Wu Flees by Night",content:"武松出逃后，被孔太公收留。武松在蜈蚣岭杀死了淫僧飞天蜈蚣，解救了被拘禁的妇女。随后武松扮成行者打扮，辗转来到二龙山，与鲁智深、杨志相遇，三人共同占据了二龙山宝珠寺落草为寇。\nFleeing from vengeance, Wu Song is sheltered briefly before reaching Centipede Ridge, where he kills an evil monk and rescues a captive woman. Disguised as a wandering pilgrim, he eventually reaches Mount Er Long, where he finds Zhishen and Yang Zhi already established as outlaw chiefs. The three warriors unite to hold the mountain together."},
{id:31,title:"宋江大闹清风寨，花荣小李广射雁",english:"Song Jiang Stirs Up Qingfeng Stockade; Hua Rong the Archer Shoots Wild Geese",content:"宋江出逃后，辗转来到清风寨，投奔花荣。清风寨知寨刘高之妻曾被宋江所救，刘高却恩将仇报，将宋江捆绑捉拿。花荣赶来救下宋江，二人由此结怨，清风山一带由此大乱。\nAfter his escape, Song Jiang reaches Qingfeng Stockade to visit his friend Hua Rong. The garrison chief Liu Gao's wife was once rescued by Song Jiang, yet Liu Gao repays the favor by arresting him. Hua Rong rescues Song Jiang, and the falling out sparks a military conflict across the Qingfeng region."},
{id:32,title:"清风山宋江遭擒，清风寨花荣大闹",english:"Song Jiang Is Captured on Qingfeng Mountain; Hua Rong Raises Havoc",content:"清风山上，宋江被燕顺、王英、郑天寿等人捉住，几乎被杀，幸得花荣赶到营救。花荣武艺超群，人称\"小李广\"，一箭之术令人叹服。众好汉随后攻打清风寨，打败了刘高，救出了被捉的宋江和其他兄弟。\nOn Qingfeng Mountain Song Jiang is captured by Yan Shun, Wang Ying, and Zheng Tianshou, nearly killed before Hua Rong arrives. Hua Rong — nicknamed 'Little Li Guang' for his legendary archery — rescues his friend. Together they then attack and take Qingfeng Stockade, defeating Liu Gao and freeing their captured companions."},
{id:33,title:"入云龙公孙胜大破高廉天罡阵",english:"Gongsun Sheng the Dragon-in-the-Clouds Breaks Gao Lian's Magic Formation",content:"高唐州知府高廉是高俅之弟，懂得妖法。梁山攻打高唐州时，高廉布下天罡阵，梁山兵马大败。宋江急召公孙胜前来破阵，公孙胜以道法破了天罡阵，梁山终于打下高唐州，救出了柴进。\nThe magistrate of Gaotang Prefecture is Gao Lian, Gao Qiu's brother, who commands sorcery. When Liangshan attacks, Gao Lian deploys a supernatural formation that routs the outlaw army. Song Jiang urgently summons the wizard Gongsun Sheng, who counters the magic and breaks the formation, allowing Liangshan to capture the city and rescue Chai Jin."},
{id:34,title:"没羽箭飞石打英雄，宋公明二打祝家庄",english:"Zhang Qing's Flying Stones; Song Jiang's Second Assault on Zhu Family Village",content:"梁山二打祝家庄，祝家庄凭借地形优势和盘陀路设防严密，梁山兵马几度受挫。宋江与吴用研究地形，派内应打探，终于摸清了盘陀路的走法。经过周密部署，梁山大举进攻，形势逐渐好转。\nLiangshan launches its second assault on the heavily fortified Zhu Family Village, whose maze-like paths continue to repel the outlaws. Song Jiang and Wu Yong study the terrain and plant spies inside to learn the labyrinthine routes. With detailed intelligence, they deploy their forces effectively and begin to turn the tide."},
{id:35,title:"梁山泊三打祝家庄，扈三娘归降梁山泊",english:"The Third Attack on Zhu Family Village; Hu Sanniang Surrenders to Liangshan",content:"三打祝家庄时，梁山采用了孙立等人内应配合的策略，里应外合，终于攻破了祝家庄。祝家三兄弟战死，扈三娘被林冲生擒，归顺梁山。梁山缴获了大批粮草物资，实力大增，众好汉欢庆胜利。\nIn the third assault, Liangshan uses an inside agent strategy with Sun Li and his group infiltrating the village. Combined attack from within and without finally breaks Zhu Family Village. The three Zhu brothers die in battle, Hu Sanniang is captured by Lin Chong and joins Liangshan. The outlaws seize enormous supplies and celebrate their greatest victory yet."},
{id:36,title:"宋江怒杀阎婆惜，晁盖曾头市中箭",english:"Chao Gai Is Shot at Zeng Family Market Town",content:"梁山好汉势力大增后，晁盖亲自率兵攻打曾头市。曾头市史文恭武艺高强，梁山兵马久攻不下。一日晁盖中了曾家的埋伏，被毒箭射中，虽经救治，仍不治身亡，临终嘱咐能捉史文恭者方可为梁山之主。\nWith Liangshan's power growing, Chao Gai himself leads an attack on Zeng Family Market. The Zeng family general Shi Wenggong is a formidable warrior and the campaign stalls. Chao Gai is lured into an ambush and struck by a poisoned arrow. He dies despite treatment, his dying words: whoever captures Shi Wengong shall be Liangshan's next chief."},
{id:37,title:"没遮拦穿林跨凤勇进发，鼓上蚤时迁偷甲",english:"The Reckless One Advances Boldly; Time-Keeper Shi Qian Steals the Armor",content:"晁盖身亡后，宋江暂代首领之职，梁山众好汉共推宋江为主。宋江为报晁盖之仇，决意攻打曾头市。时迁奉命潜入曾头市盗取盔甲，为梁山大军的进攻创造有利条件，展现了他飞檐走壁的绝技。\nAfter Chao Gai's death, Song Jiang takes over leadership by acclamation. Determined to avenge his chief, he plans a campaign against Zeng Family Market. The nimble thief Shi Qian is sent to infiltrate the town and steal military armor, displaying his extraordinary acrobatic ability and setting the stage for the army's assault."},
{id:38,title:"及时雨会神行太保，黑旋风斗浪里白条",english:"Timely Rain Meets the Divine Courier; Black Whirlwind Fights White Wave",content:"宋江结识了神行太保戴宗，此人能日行八百里。宋江在江州为官时，与戴宗、李逵等人交往，成为好友。浪里白条张顺与黑旋风李逵因小事争斗，两人打得不可开交，各有所长，张顺在水里，李逵在岸上，难分胜负，后经宋江调和，二人化敌为友。\nSong Jiang meets the 'Divine Courier' Dai Zong, who can walk 800 li a day. In Jiangzhou they befriend the fierce Li Kui — 'Black Whirlwind' — and Zhang Shun, 'White Wave on the Water,' who brawl savagely with each other. Zhang Shun owns the water; Li Kui owns the shore. Song Jiang makes peace between them and they become sworn brothers."},
{id:39,title:"浔阳楼宋江吟反诗，梁山泊戴宗传假信",english:"Song Jiang Writes a Seditious Poem at Xunyang Tower; Dai Zong Carries a Forged Letter",content:"宋江在浔阳楼借酒浇愁，醉后题下反诗，被人告发，以谋反罪入狱，被判死刑。戴宗为救宋江，传递假信，却被识破，也入了大牢。宋江和戴宗在江州大牢中等待处决，命悬一线。\nDrunk with longing and self-pity at Xunyang Tower, Song Jiang scrawls a seditious poem on the wall. He is arrested for treason and sentenced to death. Dai Zong, trying to save him with a forged letter, is also caught. Both men sit in Jiangzhou prison awaiting execution."},
{id:40,title:"梁山泊好汉劫法场，白龙庙英雄小聚义",english:"The Heroes of Liangshan Storm the Execution Ground; Assembly at White Dragon Temple",content:"处决之日，梁山好汉在李逵的带动下大闹法场，砍倒旗杆，救出了宋江和戴宗。李逵杀红了眼，连砍带杀，血流成河。众好汉在白龙庙短暂聚义后，护送宋江等人北上，回归梁山，梁山声威大震。\nOn execution day, Li Kui leads the Liangshan heroes in a full assault on the execution ground. He cuts down banners and slaughters indiscriminately as the outlaws extract Song Jiang and Dai Zong in a bloodbath. The heroes hold a quick assembly at White Dragon Temple before escorting Song Jiang safely back to Liangshan."},
{id:41,title:"宋江智取无为军，张顺活捉黄文炳",english:"Song Jiang Takes Wuwei Garrison by Wit; Zhang Shun Captures Huang Wenbing",content:"宋江决意攻打无为军，擒杀告他密谋反诗的黄文炳，以报宿怨。张顺潜水至城下，在城内作为内应，梁山外攻内应，一举破城。黄文炳在逃亡途中被擒，宋江在李逵的请求下，将其凌迟处死以祭晁盖之灵。\nSong Jiang targets Wuwei Garrison specifically to kill Huang Wenbing, the man who reported his seditious poem. Zhang Shun swims underwater to infiltrate the city as an inside agent while Liangshan attacks the walls. The city falls; Huang Wenbing is captured fleeing and, at Li Kui's urging, slowly executed to honor Chao Gai's spirit."},
{id:42,title:"还道村受三卷天书，宋公明遇九天玄女",english:"Song Jiang Receives Three Scrolls of Heavenly Script; He Meets the Mysterious Lady of the Nine Heavens",content:"宋江在梦中遇到九天玄女娘娘，受授三卷天书，被告知替天行道、保境安民的天命。宋江醒后将梦境谨记于心，行事更加合乎正道，广招天下英雄，以替天行道为旗号，梁山声势越来越大。\nSong Jiang dreams of the Mysterious Lady of the Nine Heavens, who presents him with three celestial scrolls and reveals his heavenly mandate to act on behalf of Heaven and protect the people. Song Jiang wakes with renewed sense of purpose, uses 'Act for Heaven' as Liangshan's banner, and accelerates his recruitment of heroes."},
{id:43,title:"假李逵剪径劫单人，黑旋风沂岭杀四虎",english:"The False Li Kui Robs Travelers; the Real Li Kui Kills Four Tigers on Yi Ridge",content:"有人冒充李逵打家劫舍，宋江令李逵前去缉拿。李逵归乡探母，途中将母亲安置后外出，回来时发现老母被老虎吃掉。悲愤交加的李逵连杀四只猛虎为母报仇，随后寻获假李逵，将其一刀两断。\nSomeone is impersonating Li Kui in robbery. When Li Kui goes home to fetch his mother to Liangshan, he returns to find she has been devoured by a tiger. In grief and fury he hunts down and kills four tigers. He then tracks down the imposter and kills him too."},
{id:44,title:"锦豹子小径逢戴宗，病关索长街遇石秀",english:"Spotted Leopard Yang Lin Meets Dai Zong; Shi Xiu Encounters the Sick Guan Suo",content:"杨雄因感激石秀救了自己，与石秀结为兄弟，并带石秀住进家中。杨雄之妻潘巧云与和尚裴如海私通，石秀看在眼里。石秀义愤难忍，揭发此事，杨雄大怒，在翠屏山上亲手杀死了妻子和奸夫，随后与石秀同上梁山。\nYang Xiong, grateful to Shi Xiu for saving his life, takes him in as a sworn brother. Yang Xiong's wife Pan Qiaoyun is conducting an affair with the monk Pei Ruhai, and Shi Xiu witnesses it. When Shi Xiu exposes the affair, Yang Xiong kills his wife and her lover on Jade Screen Mountain. Both men then head to Liangshan."},
{id:45,title:"病关索大闹翠屏山，拼命三火烧祝家庄",english:"Shi Xiu Causes Havoc on Jade Screen Mountain; The Daredevil Sets Fire to Zhu Family Village",content:"石秀为救卢俊义，独自一人在刑场大闹，以一人之力救出卢俊义。此番义举令众好汉深为佩服，石秀因此有了\"拼命三郎\"的称号。卢俊义得救后加入梁山，成为仅次于宋江的第二把手，梁山实力进一步增强。\nShi Xiu single-handedly storms an execution ground to save Lu Junyi, earning himself the nickname 'Daredevil.' The rescued Lu Junyi, a wealthy aristocrat and master fighter, joins Liangshan and becomes second only to Song Jiang in the hierarchy. His addition greatly enhances Liangshan's military capability."},
{id:46,title:"扑天雕双修生死书，宋公明一打祝家庄",english:"Li Ying of the Two Swords and the Life-Death Contract; First Attack on Zhu Family Village",content:"李应与祝家庄有仇，为梁山提供了重要的军事情报。梁山一打祝家庄时，由于不熟悉盘陀路，吃了大亏，损兵折将。宋江与吴用深刻总结教训，重新部署，决心二打祝家庄，务必成功。\nLi Ying, feuding with Zhu Family Village, provides Liangshan with critical intelligence. The first assault on the village fails badly because the outlaws don't know the maze-like paths. Song Jiang and Wu Yong analyze the failure, regroup, and commit to a second assault that must succeed."},
{id:47,title:"一丈青单捉王矮虎，宋公明二打祝家庄",english:"One-Zhang Qing Captures Wang the Dwarf Tiger; Second Assault on Zhu Family Village",content:"一丈青扈三娘武艺高强，在战场上单骑生擒了王英。梁山二打祝家庄，吴用运用计谋，派人打入庄内作为内应。但盘陀路依然难以破解，梁山军队在解珍、解宝的帮助下逐渐摸清了地形。\nThe fierce woman warrior Hu Sanniang captures Wang Ying single-handed in combat. In the second assault, Wu Yong plants inside agents in the village. With help from the hunters Xie Zhen and Xie Bao, the outlaws gradually learn the secrets of the labyrinthine defensive paths."},
{id:48,title:"解珍解宝双越狱，孙立孙新大劫牢",english:"The Xie Brothers Break Out of Prison; Sun Li and Sun Xin Stage a Jailbreak",content:"解珍解宝被毛太公陷害入狱，顾大嫂与孙立、邹润等人密谋劫狱，杀死毛太公，救出二人。孙立利用自己将领的身份混入祝家庄，成为梁山的内应。里应外合之下，三打祝家庄终于取得了决定性的胜利。\nThe Xie brothers are framed and imprisoned by Squire Mao. Gu Dasao leads Sun Li and others in a prison break, killing Squire Mao. Sun Li uses his military rank to infiltrate Zhu Family Village as Liangshan's spy. With insiders and outsiders attacking together, the third assault finally achieves a decisive victory."},
{id:49,title:"吴学究双掌连环计，宋公明三打祝家庄",english:"Wu Yong's Chain-Link Strategy; Song Jiang's Third Attack on Zhu Family Village",content:"吴用连环妙计发挥作用，孙立等人在庄内打开城门，梁山大军涌入。祝家三兄弟在乱战中被杀，祝家庄彻底覆灭。梁山缴获了大量粮草辎重，声威大震。扈三娘也在此战中被林冲俘获，后嫁给王英。\nWu Yong's layered plans reach their conclusion as Sun Li's men open the gates from inside. All three Zhu brothers are killed in the melee. Zhu Family Village falls and Liangshan seizes vast supplies. Hu Sanniang, captured by Lin Chong, is married off to Wang Ying in one of the story's more controversial moments."},
{id:50,title:"吴用智赚玉麒麟，张顺夜闹金沙渡",english:"Wu Yong Tricks the Jade Unicorn; Zhang Shun Fights at Golden Sand Ford",content:"卢俊义是北京城首屈一指的富商，武艺高强，人称\"玉麒麟\"。吴用化装成算命先生，来到北京，以谶语迷惑卢俊义，让他独自前往梁山寻宝，途中遭奸人诬陷，入狱待斩。\nLu Junyi — 'Jade Unicorn' — is the wealthiest and most skilled man in the northern capital. Wu Yong disguises himself as a fortune-teller, plants a cryptic prophecy in Lu Junyi's mind that sends him traveling toward Liangshan. Enemies at home seize the chance to frame him for treason, landing him in prison under sentence of death."},
{id:51,title:"戴院长智取生辰纲，吴学究再赚玉麒麟",english:"Wu Yong Tricks Lu Junyi Again; Liangshan Rescues the Jade Unicorn",content:"卢俊义在北京被判死刑，宋江率梁山好汉兵围北京城。城内燕青设法传递消息，梁山里应外合，最终救出卢俊义。卢俊义感激之余，正式加入梁山，被推为第二位头领，梁山一百单八将中仅次于宋江。\nWith Lu Junyi sentenced to death in Beiping, Song Jiang lays siege to the city. Inside, Lu Junyi's loyal servant Yan Qing coordinates with the outlaws. Combined inside-outside action breaks Lu Junyi free. Grateful, he formally joins Liangshan and is installed as second-in-command."},
{id:52,title:"李逵打死殷天锡，柴进失陷高唐州",english:"Li Kui Kills Yin Tianxi; Chai Jin Is Trapped in Gaotang Prefecture",content:"李逵护送柴进叔父进京途中，柴进叔父因与高廉的舅子殷天锡争地，被殷天锡打死。李逵大怒，当场打死殷天锡，柴进被高廉捉拿入狱。宋江为救柴进，决意攻打高唐州，但高廉会妖法，屡屡击败梁山兵马。\nWhile Li Kui escorts Chai Jin's uncle, the uncle is killed in a land dispute by Yin Tianxi, nephew of the sorcerer magistrate Gao Lian. Li Kui kills Yin Tianxi on the spot; Chai Jin is arrested by Gao Lian. Song Jiang besieges Gaotang but Gao Lian's magic repeatedly defeats Liangshan's forces."},
{id:53,title:"戴宗智取公孙胜，宋江大破高廉阵",english:"Dai Zong Fetches Gongsun Sheng; Song Jiang Breaks Gao Lian's Formation",content:"宋江派戴宗去寻回公孙胜，戴宗费尽周折找到了在蓟州修道的公孙胜，师父罗真人准许他下山相助。公孙胜法力高强，以道家法术破了高廉的妖法阵，梁山大军随即攻破高唐州，救出柴进。\nSong Jiang sends Dai Zong to find the missing Gongsun Sheng, who has been living as a hermit under the Daoist master Luo Zhenren. The master reluctantly grants permission for Gongsun Sheng to rejoin his brothers. Gongsun Sheng's Daoist magic overcomes Gao Lian's sorcery, and Liangshan takes the city, freeing Chai Jin."},
{id:54,title:"入云龙斗法破高廉，黑旋风探穴救柴进",english:"Gongsun Sheng Defeats Gao Lian's Magic; Li Kui Tunnels In to Rescue Chai Jin",content:"高廉虽然妖法被破，仍顽强抵抗。李逵率众人挖掘地道，穿墙入城，在城内杀敌，与城外大军里应外合，终于彻底攻克高唐州。柴进获救，高廉被杀，梁山好汉大获全胜，凯旋而归。\nEven with his magic broken, Gao Lian fights desperately. Li Kui leads men in digging tunnels through the city walls to fight inside while the main army attacks outside. Gaotang falls completely; Gao Lian is killed, and Chai Jin is freed. The heroes return to Liangshan in triumph."},
{id:55,title:"高太尉大兴三路兵，呼延灼摆布连环马",english:"Grand Marshal Gao Launches Three Armies; Huyan Zhuo Deploys the Chain-Linked Horse Formation",content:"朝廷震惊于梁山的势力，高俅派呼延灼率大军征剿。呼延灼是名将后裔，双鞭无敌，率领由连环马组成的精锐部队。连环马铁甲铁骑，刀枪不入，梁山多次出战均告失败，众好汉愁眉不展。\nDismayed by Liangshan's growing power, Gao Qiu dispatches the general Huyan Zhuo with a large army. Huyan Zhuo is a skilled commander who deploys the devastating Linked Horse Formation — heavily armored cavalry chained together in rows. Liangshan's repeated attacks fail against this formation, and the heroes are confounded."},
{id:56,title:"吴用使时迁盗甲，汤隆赚徐宁上山",english:"Wu Yong Has Shi Qian Steal the Armor; Tang Long Lures Xu Ning to the Mountain",content:"吴用想到用钩镰枪破连环马，世上只有徐宁懂得此枪法。吴用派时迁盗取徐宁的祖传宝甲，徐宁追宝甲上了梁山，无奈留下教授钩镰枪法。梁山好汉苦练此法，终于掌握了对付连环马的克敌之术。\nWu Yong realizes that the hooked-sickle spear technique can defeat the Chain Horse Formation — and only Xu Ning knows this technique. Shi Qian steals Xu Ning's ancestral heirloom armor; Xu Ning follows it to Liangshan and is persuaded to stay and teach the technique. The heroes practice intensively until they master the counter to Huyan Zhuo's cavalry."},
{id:57,title:"徐宁教使钩镰枪，宋江大破连环马",english:"Xu Ning Teaches the Hooked-Sickle Spear; Song Jiang Destroys the Chain Horse Formation",content:"经过苦练，梁山好汉掌握了钩镰枪法的精髓。决战之时，梁山步兵专门克制连环马，钩镰枪专砍马蹄，连环马阵顷刻瓦解。呼延灼战败，战马被宋江等人俘获，呼延灼只身逃走，后来被说服加入了梁山。\nArmed with the new technique, Liangshan's infantry deploy the hooked-sickle spears specifically targeting the horses' legs. The Chain Horse Formation collapses in minutes. Huyan Zhuo is defeated and his cavalry destroyed; he flees alone, but is later persuaded to join Liangshan — his expertise added to the outlaw army."},
{id:58,title:"二龙山宋江会鲁智深，梁山泊吴用举戴宗",english:"Song Jiang Meets Zhishen at Mount Er Long; Wu Yong Proposes Dai Zong",content:"鲁智深、武松、杨志在二龙山落草，宋江前来联络，欲整合各路英雄共赴梁山。鲁智深等人经过考量，答应加入梁山。至此，二龙山、梁山两支力量合并，梁山声势更加浩大，一百单八将的格局渐渐成型。\nZhishen, Wu Song, and Yang Zhi have been running their own outlaw stronghold at Mount Er Long. Song Jiang visits to propose a merger. After deliberation, the Er Long Mountain heroes agree to join Liangshan. The merger of the two forces dramatically strengthens Liangshan and brings the roster of 108 heroes closer to completion."},
{id:59,title:"吴用赚金铃吊挂，宋江闹西岳华山",english:"Wu Yong Obtains the Golden Bell Trap; Song Jiang Makes Trouble at Mount Hua",content:"梁山势力扩张，开始与各地势力接触。宋江在游历途中偶遇华山神圣地，感受到山河壮阔。梁山通过外交和武力两手策略，不断扩大自己的影响力，吸纳更多英雄好汉，声望日增，已成为江湖上无法忽视的重要力量。\nLiangshan continues to expand its influence, making contact with other power centers across the land. Song Jiang, traveling on various missions, encounters the sacred Mount Hua and is moved by its grandeur. Through a combination of diplomacy and military pressure, Liangshan continues recruiting heroes and growing into an unstoppable force."},
{id:60,title:"公孙胜芒砀山降魔，晁盖曾头市中箭",english:"Gongsun Sheng Subdues Demons on Mangdang Mountain; The Shadow of Zeng Family Market",content:"梁山继续扩张，公孙胜在芒砀山收服了樊瑞等人。梁山的势力范围越来越大，与各方势力的冲突也日益增多。好汉们在宋江的领导下，一方面广招英才，一方面积极应对朝廷的一次次征剿，展现出强大的凝聚力。\nLiangshan's expansion continues as Gongsun Sheng subdues the sorcerer Fan Rui and others on Mangdang Mountain. Liangshan's sphere of influence grows ever wider, bringing new conflicts with regional powers. Under Song Jiang's leadership, the heroes recruit continuously while repelling government campaigns, displaying remarkable unity."},
{id:61,title:"吴用智赚玉麒麟，张顺夜闹金沙渡",english:"The Complete Roster Nears; Lu Junyi's Ordeal",content:"为凑齐一百零八将，宋江等人多方招募英雄。卢俊义因吴用所设之计，被迫离开北京城，途中多次遭遇险境。梁山的策略是通过各种方式，无论是情义还是计谋，将天下英雄尽收麾下，共成大业。\nTo complete the roster of 108 heroes, Song Jiang and Wu Yong employ every means available — appeals to friendship, elaborate schemes, and military force. Lu Junyi's long journey from wealthy citizen to Liangshan's second chief illustrates the mix of manipulation and genuine heroism that characterizes the outlaw band's growth."},
{id:62,title:"放冷箭燕青救主，劫法场石秀跳楼",english:"Yan Qing Shoots the Sniper to Save His Master; Shi Xiu Leaps from the Scaffold",content:"卢俊义在北京下狱，燕青与梁山众人密谋营救。石秀在法场只身大闹，从高楼上跳下，以一己之力营救卢俊义，此举令众人叹服。梁山大军随后攻城，里应外合，终于救出了卢俊义。\nWith Lu Junyi imprisoned, his loyal servant Yan Qing helps Liangshan coordinate a rescue. Shi Xiu alone storms the execution platform and leaps from a tall building in a suicidal distraction. The Liangshan army attacks the city simultaneously; inside agents open the gates, and Lu Junyi is freed."},
{id:63,title:"宋江兵打北京城，关胜议取梁山泊",english:"Song Jiang Besieges Beiping; Guan Sheng Plans to Take Liangshan",content:"朝廷得知梁山攻打北京的消息，派关胜率军来援。关胜是关羽后裔，武艺绝伦，使一口青龙偃月刀，威风凛凛。梁山与关胜大军交锋，互有胜负。吴用施计，离间关胜部将，最终将关胜也招降入伙梁山。\nThe court dispatches Guan Sheng — a descendant of the great warrior Guan Yu — to relieve Beiping. Guan Sheng wields the iconic Green Dragon Crescent Blade and is a fearsome opponent. After several inconclusive battles, Wu Yong sows discord among Guan Sheng's officers and eventually convinces him to join Liangshan."},
{id:64,title:"呼延灼月夜赚关胜，宋公明雪天擒索超",english:"Huyan Zhuo Lures Guan Sheng; Song Jiang Captures Suo Chao in the Snow",content:"关胜加入梁山后，为梁山增添了重要战力。索超是猛将，在大名府与梁山交战，被宋江率众在雪天设计生擒。大名府的攻防战充满变数，梁山通过智勇结合，逐步瓦解了大名府的抵抗。\nWith Guan Sheng added to their ranks, Liangshan gains critical military strength. The fierce general Suo Chao defending Daming Prefecture engages Liangshan in pitched battle before being captured by Song Jiang in a snowy ambush. The campaign for Daming involves repeated battles testing Liangshan's full strategic and military capability."},
{id:65,title:"托塔天王梦中显圣，浪子燕青智扑擎天柱",english:"The Pagoda-Bearing King Appears in a Dream; Yan Qing the Prodigal Outsmarts the Pillar of Heaven",content:"燕青武艺高强，尤善相扑，人称\"浪子\"。在一次重要的竞技场合，燕青以技巧胜过了号称天下第一相扑手的任原，为梁山争得了荣誉。燕青此人机智灵活，是宋江身边不可或缺的谋士与勇将。\nYan Qing, 'The Prodigal,' is an unmatched wrestler. In a major competition he defeats Ren Yuan, supposedly the greatest wrestler under heaven, through superior technique. Yan Qing's combination of physical skill, quick thinking, and personal charm makes him an invaluable asset to Song Jiang."},
{id:66,title:"时迁火烧翠云楼，吴用智取大名府",english:"Shi Qian Burns Cuiyun Tower; Wu Yong Captures Daming Prefecture by Stratagem",content:"攻打大名府的关键时刻，时迁奉命潜入城中放火，以火为信号。吴用里应外合之计发挥作用，梁山大军趁乱攻城，终于攻克大名府。大名府的陷落标志着梁山势力扩张到了黄河以北，影响力进一步增强。\nAt the critical moment in the siege of Daming Prefecture, Shi Qian infiltrates the city to start fires as a signal. Wu Yong's inside-outside coordination works perfectly; Liangshan's army storms the city amid the chaos and takes it. The fall of Daming marks Liangshan's expansion north of the Yellow River."},
{id:67,title:"宋江赏马步三军，关胜降伏单廷珪",english:"Song Jiang Reviews His Infantry and Cavalry; Guan Sheng Subdues the Twin Generals",content:"梁山好汉日益增多，宋江检阅三军，军容壮观。关胜以大义说服了曾与其交战的对手单廷珪、魏定国等人归顺梁山。梁山一百单八将的阵容越来越接近完整，各路英雄八方汇聚，共谋大事。\nSong Jiang reviews his growing army in a grand parade. Guan Sheng, by personal persuasion and demonstrated virtue, convinces former enemies Shan Tinggui and Wei Dingguo to surrender and join Liangshan. The roster of 108 heroes draws ever closer to completion as warriors from all directions converge."},
{id:68,title:"宋公明夜打曾头市，卢俊义活捉史文恭",english:"Song Jiang's Night Attack on Zeng Family Market; Lu Junyi Captures Shi Wenggong Alive",content:"为报晁盖被射之仇，梁山全力攻打曾头市。历经苦战，卢俊义生擒了大将史文恭，终于为晁盖报了仇。宋江按照晁盖的遗嘱，本应立卢俊义为主，却推辞不受，众人拥戴宋江为梁山之主，卢俊义屈居第二。\nIn final fulfillment of Chao Gai's dying wish, Liangshan attacks Zeng Family Market. After fierce fighting, Lu Junyi captures Shi Wenggong alive. Honoring Chao Gai's bequest, Song Jiang nominally defers to Lu Junyi, but the brothers insist on Song Jiang as chief. Lu Junyi accepts second place."},
{id:69,title:"没羽箭飞石打英雄，宋公明三打祝家庄",english:"The Grand Assembly — 108 Heroes Take Their Seats at Liangshan",content:"梁山好汉齐聚，宋江主持了盛大的英雄大会，一百零八将各就各位，天罡地煞各归其列。宋江宣读了大聚义的誓言，以替天行道、保境安民为宗旨，梁山从此成为一支有组织、有纪律的义军，威震天下。\nAll 108 heroes assemble for the great convocation. Song Jiang presides as the 36 Heavenly Spirits and 72 Earthly Spirits take their assigned seats according to a celestial order. Song Jiang reads the oath of the grand alliance — to act for Heaven and protect the people. Liangshan is now a disciplined army, feared throughout the empire."},
{id:70,title:"忠义堂石碣受天文，梁山泊英雄排座次",english:"The Stone Tablet Reveals Heaven's Order; the Heroes Take Their Seats",content:"石碣从天而降，上刻一百零八将的姓名和排位。众好汉按照天意排定座次，宋江为天魁星，卢俊义为天罡星，依次排列。这一神圣仪式确立了梁山的正统性，使众好汉相信自己是奉天承运，行事有据。\nA stone tablet descends from heaven inscribed with all 108 names in their destined order. Song Jiang is the Star of Heaven's Leader, Lu Junyi second. This sacred ceremony legitimizes Liangshan's existence, convincing the heroes that Heaven itself sanctions their mission — a crucial moment of collective identity."},
{id:71,title:"忠义堂石碣受天文，梁山泊英雄排座次",english:"Aftermath of the Grand Assembly; Preparations for the First Zheng Campaign",content:"大聚义后，宋江着手整军备战，完善了梁山的军事组织体系。朝廷闻知梁山大聚义，震惊之余，加紧筹备大规模的征剿行动。双方都在积蓄力量，一场大规模的对决即将到来，梁山的命运将迎来新的考验。\nFollowing the grand assembly, Song Jiang reorganizes and strengthens the army. The imperial court, alarmed by the news, accelerates preparations for a massive punitive expedition. Both sides prepare for a decisive confrontation. Liangshan's fate will face its greatest test in the campaigns to come."},
{id:72,title:"柴进簪花入禁苑，李逵元夜闹东京",english:"Chai Jin Disguised Enters the Forbidden Garden; Li Kui Causes Havoc in the Capital on Lantern Night",content:"元宵节，宋江等人化装入汴京游玩。李逵因酒性大发，在东京大街上闹事，险些暴露身份。柴进扮作宫廷花匠混入后苑，见到了皇帝，这次经历令众人既兴奋又惊险。众人最终全身而退，回归梁山。\nOn the Lantern Festival, Song Jiang and companions disguise themselves to visit the capital. Li Kui gets drunk and causes a commotion in the streets, nearly blowing their cover. Chai Jin, disguised as a palace gardener, even manages to see the Emperor from a distance. They escape back to Liangshan having had a dangerous adventure."},
{id:73,title:"黑旋风乔捉鬼，梁山泊双献功",english:"The Black Whirlwind Catches 'Ghosts'; Twin Heroes Make Their Contributions",content:"李逵为帮助宋江，单独出发去寻找罗真人，路上遇到有人冒充梁山好汉欺压百姓，李逵将其一一惩处。梁山好汉们不仅自己行侠仗义，也努力维护梁山的名声，对于冒充好汉者绝不姑息。\nLi Kui sets out alone on a mission and encounters multiple impostors using Liangshan's name to bully common people. He punishes them all. The episode illustrates that the heroes take seriously their duty to protect ordinary people, and are determined to preserve the honor of the Liangshan name."},
{id:74,title:"燕青智扑擎天柱，李逵寿张乔坐衙",english:"Yan Qing Outwrestles the Pillar of Heaven; Li Kui Plays Magistrate in Shouzhang",content:"李逵在寿张县扮作县令坐堂审案，闹出了不少笑话，却也歪打正着地惩处了当地恶霸，为百姓出了口气。李逵粗中有细，虽然行事鲁莽，却有一颗真诚维护穷苦百姓的心，这正是他令读者喜爱的原因。\nLi Kui disguises himself as a county magistrate and holds court in Shouzhang, creating comic chaos but inadvertently punishing local bullies and winning justice for the common people. Despite his roughness, Li Kui has a genuine heart for the poor and oppressed — a quality that makes him one of the novel's most beloved characters."},
{id:75,title:"活阎罗倒船偷御酒，黑旋风扯诏骂钦差",english:"The Living Yama Steals Imperial Wine; the Black Whirlwind Tears Up the Imperial Edict",content:"朝廷派遣使臣持诏书前往梁山，名为招安，实则带着苛刻条件。宋江有心接受招安，李逵却当众撕毁诏书，破坏了谈判。宋江打了李逵一顿，以示公正，却也在内心深处理解李逵对朝廷的愤怒。\nThe court sends an emissary with recruitment terms that are humiliating and unacceptable. Song Jiang, who genuinely wants reconciliation, is undermined when Li Kui tears up the imperial edict in front of everyone. Song Jiang publicly punishes Li Kui, but privately understands his rage at the corrupt court."},
{id:76,title:"吴加亮布四斗五方旗，宋公明排九宫八卦阵",english:"Wu Yong Deploys the Four Direction Formation; Song Jiang Arranges the Nine Palace Formation",content:"官军大举征剿梁山，双方在战场上摆出各种阵法对峙。宋江与吴用发明了九宫八卦阵，官军的各种阵法均被破解。梁山好汉在各个战场上分进合击，充分展示了强大的军事组织能力和战斗实力。\nThe imperial army launches a major campaign against Liangshan, and both sides deploy elaborate battle formations. Song Jiang and Wu Yong's Nine-Palace Eight-Trigram Formation defeats every formation the government troops can field. Liangshan's coordinated attacks on multiple fronts demonstrate sophisticated military organization."},
{id:77,title:"梁山泊十面埋伏，宋公明大战高太尉",english:"Ten-Directional Ambush at Liangshan; Song Jiang's Great Battle with Grand Marshal Gao",content:"高俅亲率大军征剿梁山，宋江设下十面埋伏。高俅中计，被梁山团团围住，不得不投降。宋江念及招安大计，以礼相待，释放了高俅，希望借此机会让朝廷接受梁山的招安请求，却被高俅欺骗。\nGao Qiu himself leads a grand campaign against Liangshan, only to be surrounded by Song Jiang's ambushes. Gao Qiu is captured. Song Jiang, calculating that releasing him will win goodwill for recruitment, treats him courteously and lets him go — a gesture of statesmanship that Gao Qiu promptly repays with treachery."},
{id:78,title:"十节度议取梁山泊，宋公明兵打东平府",english:"Ten Military Commissioners Plan to Take Liangshan; Song Jiang Attacks Dongping Prefecture",content:"朝廷屡次征剿失败，十节度使联合议事，研究破梁山之策。梁山方面，宋江率军攻打东平府和东昌府，这是为了进一步积累实力，在朝廷接受招安前谋求更有利的谈判地位。\nAfter repeated failures, ten regional military commissioners meet to discuss strategy against Liangshan. Meanwhile Song Jiang launches campaigns against Dongping and Dongchang Prefectures, building Liangshan's bargaining position before the court will consider acceptable recruitment terms."},
{id:79,title:"宋公明兵打东平府，吴学究智取东昌府",english:"Song Jiang Attacks Dongping Prefecture; Wu Yong Captures Dongchang Prefecture",content:"东平府和东昌府各有强将镇守，梁山经过激烈战斗，分别将两府攻克。东平府的董平和东昌府的张清都是一流武将，在归降之前给梁山造成了不小的损失。二人归降后，梁山战力再次增强。\nBoth Dongping and Dongchang Prefectures are held by formidable generals — Dong Ping and Zhang Qing respectively. After fierce fighting, both fall to Liangshan. Dong Ping and Zhang Qing are skilled warriors who inflict real losses before surrendering and joining the outlaw ranks."},
{id:80,title:"张清彪炒梁山将，宋江兵打大名府",english:"Zhang Qing's Flying Stones Strike Liangshan Generals; The Road to the First Recruitment",content:"张清使用飞石，屡屡击中梁山将领，令众好汉恼怒而无奈。经过多番苦战，张清终于被擒，归顺梁山。至此，梁山好汉一百零八人基本齐聚，宋江认为时机成熟，开始正式谋求朝廷的招安。\nZhang Qing's flying stones wound one Liangshan general after another, causing frustration and pain before he is finally captured and joins. With the 108 heroes now essentially complete, Song Jiang believes the time is right to formally seek government recruitment — a long-held dream that will define Liangshan's ultimate fate."},
{id:81,title:"燕青月夜遇道君，戴宗寻来李师师",english:"Yan Qing Has a Moonlit Encounter with the Emperor; Dai Zong Finds Li Shishi",content:"宋江谋求招安，派燕青和戴宗入东京，通过名妓李师师进达皇帝。燕青聪明伶俐，与李师师相谈甚欢，借此搭上了皇帝的关系。燕青代宋江陈情，皇帝对梁山心生好感，招安大计初见曙光。\nSeeking official recruitment, Song Jiang sends Yan Qing and Dai Zong to the capital to approach the Emperor through the famous courtesan Li Shishi. The charming Yan Qing wins Li Shishi's confidence, gains access to the Emperor, and presents Song Jiang's case. The Emperor responds favorably, giving recruitment prospects their first real hope."},
{id:82,title:"梁山泊分金大买市，宋公明全伙受招安",english:"Liangshan's Heroes Distribute Gold and Celebrate; Song Jiang and All His Brothers Accept Recruitment",content:"朝廷正式下旨招安，宋江率梁山一百单八将向朝廷纳降。众好汉对招安看法不一，宋江力排众议，坚持接受。招安仪式隆重举行，梁山从此由盗变官，众好汉成为朝廷命官，开始了命运的新转折。\nThe imperial court issues an official recruitment decree. Song Jiang leads all 108 heroes in formal surrender to the government. Many heroes have misgivings, but Song Jiang insists. The ceremony is grand and solemn. Liangshan transitions from outlaws to officials — a transformation that will prove bittersweet."},
{id:83,title:"宋公明奉诏破大辽，陈桥驿滴泪斩小卒",english:"Song Jiang Receives Orders to Crush the Liao Kingdom; He Weeps While Executing a Soldier at Chenqiao",content:"招安后，梁山好汉奉旨北征大辽。宋江严明军纪，在陈桥驿含泪斩杀了一名违纪的小卒，以此立威。梁山大军军纪严整，秋毫无犯，深得百姓拥护。征辽之战即将开始，众好汉将奉王命驰骋疆场。\nAfter recruitment, the Liangshan heroes are ordered to campaign against the Liao Kingdom. Song Jiang enforces strict discipline, weeping as he orders the execution of a soldier who broke the rules at Chenqiao. The army's discipline wins the people's hearts. The Liao campaign begins."},
{id:84,title:"宋公明兵打幽州，呼延灼力擒番将",english:"Song Jiang's Army Attacks Youzhou; Huyan Zhuo Captures the Foreign Generals",content:"梁山大军进入大辽境内，与辽国精兵交锋。辽国军队训练有素，各有绝技，战斗激烈。呼延灼发挥出色，在战场上生擒数名辽将。梁山好汉的勇猛和配合令辽军胆寒，节节取得胜利。\nLiangshan's army enters Liao territory and engages its disciplined forces. The Liao soldiers are skilled professionals with specialized techniques. Huyan Zhuo distinguishes himself by capturing several Liao generals. Liangshan's courage and coordination gradually overcomes the formidable Liao resistance."},
{id:85,title:"宋公明克复霸州，韩存保打败番将",english:"Song Jiang Recaptures Bazhou; Han Cunbao Defeats the Foreign Generals",content:"梁山在征辽战争中连战连捷，逐步深入辽境。攻克霸州是一场重要的胜利，好汉们各显神通，有的单挑，有的合击，充分展示了梁山强大的综合战斗力。辽国节节败退，局势对梁山越来越有利。\nLiangshan achieves successive victories deep in Liao territory. The capture of Bazhou is a significant breakthrough, with heroes fighting in single combat and combined assaults. Liao forces fall back steadily as Liangshan's comprehensive military power proves superior."},
{id:86,title:"宋公明大战蓟州城，关胜单挑双枪将",english:"Song Jiang's Great Battle at Jizhou; Guan Sheng's Single Combat Against the Twin-Spear General",content:"蓟州是大辽的重镇，双方在此展开了激烈的攻防战。关胜与辽国猛将使双枪的贺重宝单挑，二人你来我往，战斗精彩纷呈。梁山最终攻克蓟州，距最终胜利更近一步。\nJizhou is a major Liao stronghold; the battle there is fierce and prolonged. Guan Sheng challenges the Liao champion He Chongbao — a dual-spear master — to single combat in a spectacular duel. Liangshan eventually takes Jizhou, coming closer to final victory."},
{id:87,title:"宋公明克复燕京，北辽请和罢兵",english:"Song Jiang Recaptures Yanjing; the Northern Liao Kingdom Sues for Peace",content:"梁山大军最终攻克燕京，大辽皇帝无力抵抗，派使者请和。宋江审时度势，接受了辽国的求和，以燕云十六州归还宋朝为条件达成协议。此次征辽大获全胜，梁山好汉凯旋而归，受到朝廷嘉奖。\nLiangshan captures Yanjing; the Liao Emperor, unable to resist, sends peace envoys. Song Jiang accepts the peace terms, securing the return of the strategically vital northern territories to the Song court. The Liao campaign ends in complete victory; the heroes return in triumph and are honored by the Emperor."},
{id:88,title:"颢天圣母下凡尘，宋江大破混天象阵",english:"The Holy Mother Descends; Song Jiang Breaks the Heaven-Confusing Formation",content:"征辽得胜后，宋江又奉旨征讨田虎。田虎盘踞河北，拥有精兵强将，还有得道法师相助，布下混天象阵。宋江与众好汉见识到了不同于以往的强敌，梁山又面临新的严峻考验。\nAfter the Liao victory, Song Jiang receives orders to suppress the rebel Tian Hu in Hebei. Tian Hu commands strong forces and powerful sorcerers who deploy the bewildering Heaven-Confusing Formation. Liangshan faces a qualitatively different enemy and must adapt its strategies once again."},
{id:89,title:"宋公明兵征田虎，卢俊义大败琼英",english:"Song Jiang Campaigns Against Tian Hu; Lu Junyi Defeats the Jade Hero Qiong Ying",content:"田虎麾下有一奇将名叫琼英，是一位武艺超群的女将，使飞石百发百中。卢俊义与琼英交战，一时难以取胜。梁山众将各显身手，在与田虎军队的较量中积累经验，逐步摸清敌方战法。\nTian Hu's forces include the extraordinary woman warrior Qiong Ying, whose flying stones never miss. Lu Junyi struggles against her in battle. Liangshan's heroes learn from each engagement and gradually decode the enemy's tactics, adapting their own strategies in response."},
{id:90,title:"五花营宋江被困，宋公明破田虎田彪",english:"Song Jiang Is Surrounded in the Five-Petal Formation; Tian Hu and His Son Are Defeated",content:"经过艰苦战斗，梁山最终打败了田虎，平定了河北之乱。宋江施展军事才能，指挥若定，众好汉奋勇作战。田虎父子被生擒，河北重归朝廷版图，宋江等人再次立下大功。\nAfter grueling campaigns, Liangshan finally defeats Tian Hu and pacifies Hebei. Song Jiang's military command proves decisive; the heroes fight with extraordinary valor. Tian Hu and his son are captured alive; Hebei is restored to the Song court and Song Jiang wins another major credit."},
{id:91,title:"宋公明兵打王庆，张清施奇巧破阵",english:"Song Jiang Campaigns Against Wang Qing; Zhang Qing Breaks the Formation with Clever Tricks",content:"田虎既平，宋江又奉旨讨伐王庆。王庆在淮西建立割据政权，实力不弱。梁山好汉奉命出征，一路跋山涉水，面临新的挑战。张清在这场战役中继续发挥飞石特技，屡立奇功。\nWith Tian Hu defeated, Song Jiang is ordered to suppress Wang Qing in the Huai River region. Wang Qing has established a regional regime with substantial military strength. Liangshan marches on another campaign across difficult terrain. Zhang Qing continues to distinguish himself with his stone-throwing technique."},
{id:92,title:"卢俊义分兵征王庆，宋公明出师淮西",english:"Lu Junyi Divides the Army to Fight Wang Qing; Song Jiang Campaigns in the Huai West",content:"梁山兵分多路，对王庆势力展开全面打击。卢俊义指挥其中一路，展现了出色的将帅才能。各路梁山兵马协调作战，步步为营，最终将王庆的势力逐一瓦解，平定了淮西之乱。\nLiangshan divides into multiple columns to attack Wang Qing's forces simultaneously. Lu Junyi commands one column with impressive generalship. The coordinated advance systematically dismantles Wang Qing's power base and restores order to the Huai River region."},
{id:93,title:"宋公明克复淮西，乔道清败走蒙城",english:"Song Jiang Pacifies the Huai West; Qiao Daosheng Flees to Mengcheng",content:"王庆麾下也有得道法师，梁山与法师展开了斗法之争。公孙胜等道法高手与王庆的术士相互较量，道法交锋精彩纷呈。最终梁山的道法更胜一筹，王庆势力土崩瓦解，王庆被俘，淮西得以平定。\nWang Qing's forces also include powerful sorcerers; magical battles between Gongsun Sheng and Wang Qing's practitioners add a supernatural dimension to the campaign. Liangshan's magic ultimately prevails, Wang Qing's power collapses, and he is captured — another successful campaign for the now-legendary heroes."},
{id:94,title:"宋公明兵征方腊，宋江恸哭忠义堂",english:"Song Jiang Receives Orders to Campaign Against Fang La; He Weeps in the Hall of Loyalty and Righteousness",content:"王庆既平，宋江奉旨征讨东南方腊。方腊在江南称帝，有精兵百万，勇将如云，是梁山面临的最强大的对手。宋江深知此战凶险，在忠义堂上痛哭，众好汉壮别，开始了注定将付出巨大代价的远征。\nAfter Wang Qing, Song Jiang is ordered to suppress Fang La, who has declared himself Emperor in the prosperous Jiangnan region with a million-strong army and brilliant generals. Song Jiang knows this campaign will cost dearly; he weeps in the Hall of Loyalty before the heroes march south on what will prove to be their final, devastating campaign."},
{id:95,title:"宋公明兵打杭州城，关胜大战郑彪",english:"Song Jiang's Army Attacks Hangzhou; Guan Sheng's Great Battle with Zheng Biao",content:"梁山大军进入江南，攻打方腊占据的杭州。杭州城高池深，方腊军拼死抵抗。关胜与方腊猛将郑彪大战，两人势均力敌，战况激烈。梁山为攻克每一座城池都付出了沉重代价，好汉不断伤亡。\nLiangshan advances into Jiangnan and attacks Fang La-held Hangzhou. The city's formidable defenses and fanatical defenders exact a heavy toll. Guan Sheng duels the fierce Zheng Biao in an epic single combat. Every city costs Liangshan dearly; heroes begin to fall."},
{id:96,title:"卢俊义兵打昱岭关，张清石子打卞彪",english:"Lu Junyi Attacks Yuling Pass; Zhang Qing's Stone Strikes Bian Biao",content:"昱岭关是方腊的重要关隘，梁山为此付出了惨重代价。一代名将在强攻中阵亡，梁山士气受到沉重打击。宋江等人强忍悲痛，继续挥兵南进，誓要平定方腊、完成朝廷重托，不能让已牺牲的兄弟的血白流。\nYuling Pass is one of Fang La's key fortifications. Liangshan pays a terrible price taking it, with notable heroes falling. Song Jiang and his remaining brothers suppress their grief and press on southward, determined that their fallen companions shall not have died in vain."},
{id:97,title:"宋公明兵打乌龙岭，张顺夜入涌金门",english:"Song Jiang Assaults Black Dragon Ridge; Zhang Shun's Night Swim into Yongjin Gate",content:"张顺为帮助大军攻城，独自游泳入涌金门，不幸在水中中箭而亡。张顺死时，其魂魄化作白鱼托梦警示友人。张顺之死令众好汉痛哭失声，这是征方腊以来最令人心碎的牺牲之一，预示着更多悲剧的到来。\nTo help the army take the city, Zhang Shun swims alone through Yongjin Gate — and is killed by arrows in the water. Zhang Shun's spirit appears to a friend in a dream as a white carp, a farewell message. His death devastates the heroes; it is among the most heartbreaking losses of the campaign, and more will follow."},
{id:98,title:"宋公明大战乌龙岭，宋江智取宁海军",english:"The Battle Intensifies; More Heroes Fall in Jiangnan",content:"征方腊之战进入最残酷的阶段，梁山好汉一个接一个倒下。每取一城，都要付出数名好汉的生命。宋江眼看着当初意气风发的兄弟们相继牺牲，心如刀割，却只能强撑着继续指挥大军向前推进。\nThe campaign against Fang La enters its most brutal phase. Heroes fall one after another with each city taken. Song Jiang watches his brothers die in rapid succession, his heart breaking but unable to stop. He pushes forward with the army, haunted by loss."},
{id:99,title:"鲁智深浙江坐化，宋公明衣锦还乡",english:"Zhishen Achieves Enlightenment at the Qiantang River; Song Jiang Returns Home in Glory",content:"鲁智深在杭州六和寺听到钱塘江潮声，以为是战鼓，拔刀相向。高僧解释潮信之义，智深顿悟，留偈颂后安然坐化，得到圆满。武松在智深圆寂后，也留在六和寺出家，拒绝继续为官，了此残生。\nAt Liuhe Temple in Hangzhou, Zhishen hears the tidal roar of the Qiantang River and draws his blade, thinking it battle drums. A monk explains the tide's significance; Zhishen suddenly achieves enlightenment. He composes a death-verse and dies peacefully in meditation — a saint's death. Wu Song, grief-stricken at his closest friend's passing, also stays at the temple and refuses to return to court."},
{id:100,title:"宋公明神聚蓼儿洼，徽宗帝御笔赐庙额",english:"Song Jiang's Spirit Gathers at Liao Er Marsh; the Emperor Grants the Temple Inscription",content:"征方腊之战结束，梁山一百单八将死伤过半，只有少数人回归朝廷任职。宋江等人被奸臣蔡京、高俅等人嫉恨，虽有功于朝廷，却难逃毒手。宋江虽平方腊成功，却已是强弩之末，返朝之路暗藏杀机。\nThe Fang La campaign ends. Of the 108 heroes, more than half have died. The survivors return to court, but Cai Jing and Gao Qiu — envious of their achievements — plot against them. Song Jiang has won victory for the empire but returns to a court that has never truly wanted him to survive."},
{id:101,title:"浦东林李俊同泛海，宋公明衣锦还楚州",english:"Li Jun Sails the Seas; Song Jiang Returns to Chuzhou",content:"归朝后，奸臣们对梁山旧将步步排挤。李俊见朝廷险恶，托病脱身，率数人扬帆出海，去海外开创新天地。宋江被封为楚州安抚使，看似风光，实则已入奸臣彀中，命不长久。\nBack at court, treacherous ministers systematically undermine the Liangshan veterans. Li Jun, sensing the danger, feigns illness and escapes by sea with companions, seeking a new life abroad. Song Jiang is made prefect of Chuzhou — apparently honored, but already in the conspirators' trap."},
{id:102,title:"宋公明衣锦还乡，武行者绕路还家",english:"Song Jiang Returns to His Hometown; Wu Song Takes the Long Road Home",content:"宋江荣归故里，父老乡亲夹道欢迎，一时风光无限。武松因独臂残疾，婉拒封赏，选择留在六和寺修行度日。梁山好汉们的命运各有不同，有人加官进爵，有人归隐山林，有人漂洋过海，各奔前程。\nSong Jiang returns home in triumph, welcomed by his people. Wu Song, crippled in the campaign, declines official honors and remains at Liuhe Temple. The fates of the 108 heroes diverge: some receive honors, some retreat to nature, some sail away — each finding his own ending."},
{id:103,title:"宋公明神聚蓼儿洼，徽宗帝御笔赐庙额",english:"The Traitors' Final Scheme; Song Jiang Receives the Poisoned Wine",content:"高俅、蔡京等奸臣秘密在御赐的酒中下毒，赐给宋江。宋江知道自己必死，却不愿独自赴死，派人将李逵骗来，也让李逵喝了毒酒，防止李逵在自己死后为自己报仇，引起兵变。\nGao Qiu and Cai Jing secretly poison the imperial wine sent to Song Jiang. Song Jiang knows he is dying, but cannot bear for Li Kui to avenge him and destroy the reconciliation he fought for. He summons Li Kui and has him drink poison too — one of the novel's most agonizing moments."},
{id:104,title:"宋公明托梦宋清，徽宗帝御赐庙额",english:"Song Jiang Appears in a Dream; His Temple Is Built",content:"宋江与李逵相继中毒身亡。卢俊义也遭奸臣陷害，落入水中，不知所终。花荣、吴用得知宋江死讯，在宋江墓前双双自尽，随主而去。一代英雄就此凋零，令后人为之扼腕叹息。\nSong Jiang and Li Kui die from the poison. Lu Junyi is also eliminated by treachery. Hua Rong and Wu Yong, learning of Song Jiang's death, both commit suicide at his grave, following their chief to death. The generation of heroes is extinguished. Their passing moves all who hear the story to grief."},
{id:105,title:"宋公明神聚蓼儿洼，徽宗帝赐额显灵",english:"Song Jiang's Spirit Gathers at Liao Er Marsh; the Emperor's Vision",content:"宋徽宗梦见宋江等人托梦申冤，醒后追悔莫及，令人在蓼儿洼为宋江立庙。庙成之后，宋江英灵显圣，庇护一方百姓，流芳百世。朝廷的追封与民间的纪念，寄托了百姓对这些英雄的无限崇敬。\nEmperor Huizong dreams of Song Jiang and his heroes appearing to him, lamenting their unjust fate. Waking in remorse, he orders a temple built at Liao Er Marsh in their honor. The temple becomes a site of miracles; Song Jiang's spirit protects the people of the region, and his legend lives on forever."},
{id:106,title:"燕青私别宋公明，李俊自立暹罗国",english:"Yan Qing Takes Private Leave of Song Jiang; Li Jun Establishes Himself in Siam",content:"燕青早已看透朝廷险恶，在征方腊之后便悄然隐退，携带金银隐入江湖，消失得无影无踪。李俊则在海外开创基业，据说在暹罗国建立了自己的王国，成为一方之主，得到了真正的自由。\nYan Qing, who has long seen through the court's treachery, quietly disappears after the Fang La campaign, taking gold into obscurity. Li Jun, having sailed east, reportedly establishes himself as king in Siam — achieving the freedom and power the heroes sought but could never find under the Song dynasty."},
{id:107,title:"宋公明平方腊凯旋，魂魄聚蓼儿洼",english:"The Final Accounting — Heroes' Fates After Fang La",content:"梁山一百单八将，在征方腊的战役中牺牲了七十多人。幸存者中，有人受封，有人归隐，有人出家，有人出海。宋江的悲剧结局折射出忠义理想与现实政治之间的深刻矛盾，令这部作品具有了永恒的悲剧美。\nOf the 108 heroes, over 70 die in the Fang La campaign. Among survivors, some receive honors, some become hermits, some enter monasteries, some sail away. Song Jiang's tragic end reflects the deep contradiction between the ideal of loyalty and the reality of corrupt politics — a tension that gives the novel its enduring tragic beauty."},
{id:108,title:"宋公明神聚蓼儿洼，徽宗帝御笔赐庙额",english:"Epilogue — The Legend of the 108 Heroes Lives Forever",content:"一百单八将的故事在民间广泛流传，成为忠义精神的象征。后世文人不断为他们著书立说，戏曲演绎，庙宇祭祀。梁山好汉们虽然最终失败，但他们反抗压迫、扶危济困的精神，激励着一代又一代的中国人，永远活在人民的心中。\nThe legend of the 108 heroes spreads throughout the land as a symbol of loyalty, brotherhood, and resistance to injustice. Writers, dramatists, and storytellers retell their story across the centuries. Though ultimately defeated, the spirit of Liangshan — defying oppression, helping the weak — inspires generation after generation of Chinese people and lives forever in the hearts of the people."}
],

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
   西游记 JOURNEY TO THE WEST  (100 chapters)
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ */
xiyou: [
{id:1,title:"灵根育孕源流出，心性修持大道生",english:"The Magic Root Is Born; the Origin of the Stone Monkey",content:"混沌初开，天地分判，一块仙石在花果山经日月精华孕育，迸裂产出一石猴。石猴活泼灵动，与群猴嬉戏，后因寻得水帘洞，被众猴拥立为王，称\"美猴王\"，开始了传奇的一生。\nAt the dawn of creation a magic stone on Flower-Fruit Mountain, nourished by sun and moon, cracks open to produce a Stone Monkey. Lively and fearless, the monkey plays with his troop until he discovers the Water Curtain Cave behind a waterfall. The monkeys acclaim him Handsome Monkey King, and his legend begins."},
{id:2,title:"悟彻菩提真妙理，断魔归本合元神",english:"Sun Wukong Studies under Patriarch Subodhi; He Learns the 72 Transformations",content:"猴王为求长生不死，漂洋过海，拜须菩提祖师为师。祖师赐名\"孙悟空\"，传授七十二般变化和筋斗云之术。悟空聪明好学，很快掌握了这些神通，但因卖弄变化，被祖师逐出山门，须自行闯荡。\nThe Monkey King crosses the ocean to study under the Patriarch Subodhi, who names him Sun Wukong — 'Awakened to Emptiness.' He learns the 72 Transformations and the somersault cloud. But Wukong shows off his skills and is expelled; the patriarch warns him his powers will bring great trouble."},
{id:3,title:"四海千山皆拱伏，九幽十类尽除名",english:"Wukong Acquires the Golden Staff; His Name Is Struck from the Book of Death",content:"悟空回花果山，向东海龙王借得如意金箍棒，重一万三千五百斤，可大可小，随心变化。悟空大闹龙宫，又大闹地府，将自己和众猴的名字从生死簿上勾销，令天庭龙宫地府都头痛不已。\nBack on Flower-Fruit Mountain, Wukong visits the Dragon King of the Eastern Sea and obtains the golden-banded staff, which weighs 13,500 pounds and can change size at will. He also descends to the underworld and crosses out his and his followers' names from the Book of Death, defying cosmic order."},
{id:4,title:"官封弼马心何足，名注齐天意未宁",english:"Wukong Is Given a Minor Heaven Post; He Rebels and Declares Himself Equal to Heaven",content:"天庭因惧悟空之能，封他为弼马温，管理天马。悟空得知官职低微，大怒，打出天宫，回花果山竖起\"齐天大圣\"的旗号。天庭只得顺他之意，封他为\"齐天大圣\"，给他一个有名无实的职位。\nHeaven's court, fearing Wukong's power, gives him the minor post of Keeper of the Heavenly Horses. Learning how lowly the position is, he rages back to Flower-Fruit Mountain and raises the banner 'Great Sage Equal to Heaven.' The embarrassed heavens concede the title, though the position remains empty."},
{id:5,title:"乱蟠桃大圣偷丹，反天宫诸神捉怪",english:"Wukong Steals Peaches and Elixir; He Fights the Heavenly Army",content:"悟空被派管理蟠桃园，却偷吃了长生仙桃，又偷吃了太上老君的金丹，搅乱了王母娘娘的蟠桃盛会。天庭震怒，派遣天兵天将讨伐悟空。悟空神通广大，与十万天兵大战，打得不可开交。\nGiven charge of the Heavenly Peach Garden, Wukong gorges on the immortality peaches, eats Laozi's immortality pills, and disrupts the Queen Mother's Peach Banquet. A hundred thousand heavenly soldiers are sent against him, but Wukong's powers are supreme and the battle proves inconclusive."},
{id:6,title:"观音赴会问原因，小圣施威降大圣",english:"Guanyin Observes the Battle; Erlang Shen Subdues the Great Sage",content:"众天将皆非悟空对手，观音推荐二郎神出马。二郎神与悟空大战，两人各显神通，变化追斗，精彩纷呈。最后太上老君用金刚琢击中悟空，二郎神趁机将其捉拿，悟空才终于被制服。\nHeavenly generals fail against Wukong one by one. Guanyin recommends Erlang Shen, the divine warrior. The two engage in an extraordinary shape-shifting battle of wits and power. Finally Laozi strikes Wukong with a diamond ring from above, and Erlang Shen seizes the stunned Monkey King."},
{id:7,title:"八卦炉中逃大圣，五行山下定心猿",english:"Wukong Escapes from the Eight Trigram Furnace; the Buddha Traps Him Beneath Five Elements Mountain",content:"太上老君将悟空置入八卦炉中锻烧，四十九天后悟空不仅未死，反而炼出了火眼金睛，冲出炉来，大闹天宫。玉帝请如来佛祖出手，佛祖用手化作五行山，将悟空压在山下五百年。\nLaozi locks Wukong in the Eight Trigram Furnace for 49 days; instead of dying, Wukong's eyes are tempered into the Fire-Eye Golden Pupils and he erupts, devastating heaven. The Jade Emperor summons the Buddha himself. With a single gesture the Buddha converts his hand into Five Elements Mountain and traps Wukong beneath it for 500 years."},
{id:8,title:"我佛造经传极乐，观音奉旨上长安",english:"The Buddha Orders the Scriptures Sent East; Guanyin Travels to Tang Dynasty China",content:"如来佛祖宣布，要将三藏真经送往东土，普度众生。观音菩萨奉命前往东土寻访取经人，沿途安排各路神灵护法，并将孙悟空、猪八戒、沙和尚等人安置在取经路上，等待取经人的到来。\nThe Buddha announces that the holy scriptures must be sent to China to enlighten humanity. Guanyin is sent east to find a suitable pilgrim to make the journey. Along the way she arranges protectors and positions Wukong, Pigsy, and Sandy at key points to await their future master."},
{id:9,title:"袁守诚妙算无私曲，老龙王拙计犯天条",english:"Yuan Shoucheng's Infallible Prediction; the Dragon King Violates Heaven's Decree",content:"长安城中，卜者袁守诚准确预言泾河龙王降雨时辰与分量。龙王不服，故意改变降雨，违背天条，被判斩首。龙王托梦唐太宗求救，唐太宗又托梦魏征，然而魏征心神梦中已将龙王斩首，一梦离奇。\nIn Chang'an, the prophet Yuan Shoucheng correctly predicts the exact timing and measure of rain. The Dragon King of the Jing River, furious, deliberately alters the rain to wrong him — violating Heaven's decree. Sentenced to death, the Dragon King visits Emperor Taizong in dreams, beginning a chain of supernatural events."},
{id:10,title:"二将军宫门镇鬼，唐太宗地府还魂",english:"Two Generals Guard the Palace Gate; Emperor Taizong's Journey to the Underworld",content:"唐太宗因受龙王鬼魂骚扰，秦琼、尉迟恭两位大将每夜守护宫门。太宗终于病重，魂游地府，见到众多亡灵，被阎王告知阳寿已尽。太宗许诺回阳后大做水陆法事超度亡灵，阎王予以放行。\nTang Taizong is haunted by the Dragon King's ghost; his generals stand guard at his door each night, exhausted. The Emperor falls gravely ill and his soul visits the underworld, where he sees the suffering dead and is told his time has come. He promises to hold a great mass for the dead and is released."},
{id:11,title:"还受生唐王遵善果，度孤魂萧瑀正空门",english:"Emperor Taizong Upholds His Vow; He Commissions the Scriptures Expedition",content:"唐太宗还阳后，举行了盛大的水陆法会，超度亡灵。观音化身老僧出现，告知唐僧取经之事。唐太宗认玄奘为御弟，赐号\"三藏\"，送行西天取经，望其早日取回真经，普渡大唐。\nReturning to life, Taizong holds the Grand Water-Land Mass. Guanyin appears disguised as a monk and reveals that true scriptures exist in the Western Heaven. Taizong appoints the monk Xuanzang as his sworn brother and sends him west to fetch the scriptures."},
{id:12,title:"玄奘秉诚建大会，观音显象化金蝉",english:"Tripitaka Holds the Grand Religious Assembly; Guanyin Appears to Him",content:"唐三藏在长安大慈恩寺建水陆大会，宣讲佛法。观音化身出现，指点唐僧西去取经，并授予他袈裟和锡杖。唐太宗亲自送行，与唐僧结拜为兄弟，唐僧踏上了漫漫西行之路。\nTripitaka presides over the Great Religious Assembly in Chang'an. Guanyin appears, commissions him formally for the journey west, and gives him a brocade cassock and a nine-ring staff. Emperor Taizong personally sees him off, calling him elder brother. Tripitaka departs on the long road to the Western Heaven."},
{id:13,title:"陷虎穴金星解厄，双叉岭伯钦留僧",english:"Tripitaka Falls into Tiger's Den; the Hunter Bo Qin Rescues Him",content:"唐僧离开长安，独自西行，途中遭遇猛虎，幸得金星化身老人相救。随后唐僧来到双叉岭，被猎人刘伯钦所救，在刘家留宿。刘伯钦为父亲做了超度法事，唐僧继续上路，路遇虎精等妖怪，险象环生。\nSetting out alone, Tripitaka immediately encounters danger — a tiger, monsters, and demons. The Venus Star in disguise rescues him once, and a hunter named Liu Boqin shelters him. Tripitaka performs a memorial rite for Liu's deceased father, then continues west through increasingly perilous terrain."},
{id:14,title:"心猿归正，六贼无踪",english:"Wukong Is Released and Becomes Tripitaka's Disciple; He Defeats the Six Bandits",content:"唐僧在五行山救出被压五百年的孙悟空，悟空感恩戴德，愿意护送唐僧西天取经。观音赐给唐僧一顶金箍，趁悟空不备将其戴在头上，从此悟空受金箍咒约束。途中六名强盗拦路，悟空将其全部打死，唐僧责怪悟空杀生，悟空赌气离去。\nTripitaka frees Wukong from beneath Five Elements Mountain; Wukong pledges to be his disciple. But Guanyin has given Tripitaka a golden headband which, once on Wukong's head, can never be removed and tightens painfully at Tripitaka's recitation. Wukong kills six bandits who ambush them; Tripitaka rebukes him and Wukong storms off in anger."},
{id:15,title:"蛇盘山诸神暗佑，鹰愁涧意马收缰",english:"The Dragon Horse Is Acquired at Eagle Sorrow Stream",content:"悟空离去后，唐僧独行，在鹰愁涧遭小白龙吞噬了坐骑白马。观音出面调解，小白龙变化为白马，成为唐僧的坐骑。悟空被观音劝回，再次归于唐僧门下，师徒关系得以修复，西行队伍的核心成员开始聚合。\nAfter Wukong's departure, Tripitaka loses his horse to a dragon in Eagle Sorrow Stream. Guanyin intervenes, and the young dragon transforms into a white horse to carry Tripitaka. Guanyin also talks Wukong into returning. Master and disciple are reunited, and the core team of the pilgrimage begins to take shape."},
{id:16,title:"观音院僧谋宝贝，黑风山怪窃袈裟",english:"The Monks at Guanyin Temple Covet the Cassock; the Black Wind Monster Steals It",content:"师徒来到观音禅院，老方丈见袈裟贪心大起，欲用火烧死唐僧据为己有。悟空设法将大火引向禅院，袈裟却被黑风山黑熊精趁乱盗走。悟空与黑熊精大战，最后借助观音菩萨相助，收服了黑熊精，夺回袈裟。\nAt a monastery the abbot covets Tripitaka's precious cassock and plots to burn the pilgrims alive to take it. Wukong redirects the fire, but a Black Bear Monster steals the cassock in the confusion. After failing to defeat the bear alone, Wukong asks Guanyin for help; she subdues the monster and recovers the cassock."},
{id:17,title:"孙行者大闹黑风山，观世音收伏熊罴怪",english:"Wukong Battles the Black Wind Mountain Demon; Guanyin Subdues the Bear",content:"悟空多次与黑熊精交战，难以取胜。悟空请来观音菩萨，观音变作道姑，用仙丹迷惑黑熊精，再以金箍套住熊头，将黑熊精收为守山之神。袈裟最终物归原主。\nWukong battles the Black Bear Monster repeatedly without success. He appeals to Guanyin, who disguises herself as a Daoist priestess and tricks the bear into drinking enchanted wine, then locks a golden band on his head and takes him as her own mountain guardian. The cassock is recovered."},
{id:18,title:"观音院唐僧脱难，高老庄行者降魔",english:"Tripitaka Escapes the Temple; Wukong Exorcises the Demon at Old Gao's Farm",content:"师徒继续西行，来到高老庄。高老庄高太公之女被猪精招赘为婿，猪精虽然能干，但相貌丑陋，高太公深以为苦。悟空奉命降妖，与猪精展开激烈的战斗，猪精难以抵挡悟空的金箍棒，最终逃走。\nThe pilgrims reach Old Gao's Farm where a pig demon has married the farmer's daughter. Though capable, the demon is monstrous in appearance and the farmer is deeply unhappy. Wukong confronts and battles the pig monster; unable to overcome the golden staff, the demon flees into the night."},
{id:19,title:"云栈洞悟空收八戒，浮屠山玄奘受心经",english:"Wukong Captures Zhu Bajie; Tripitaka Receives the Heart Sutra",content:"猪精逃入云栈洞，悟空追入，得知猪精原为天宫天蓬元帅，因醉酒调戏嫦娥被罚下界，投胎为猪形。经观音劝导，猪精愿意皈依，法名\"猪悟能\"，即猪八戒。浮屠山上，乌巢禅师传授唐僧《心经》。\nThe pig demon retreats to Cloud Plank Cave; Wukong follows to learn he was formerly the Marshal of the Heavenly Canopy, exiled for drunkenly molesting the Moon Goddess, reborn in pig form. He is persuaded to join the pilgrimage as Zhu Bajie. Later, the hermit Wunao gives Tripitaka the Heart Sutra."},
{id:20,title:"黄风岭唐僧有难，半山中八戒争先",english:"The Yellow Wind Monster Blinds Wukong; Lingji Bodhisattva Saves the Day",content:"黄风岭上，黄风怪用三昧神风迷了悟空的眼睛，悟空几乎失明。八戒请来灵吉菩萨，菩萨用飞龙宝杖降服了黄风大王，原来是灵山脚下的土地老鼠成精。悟空眼睛被神医医治好，师徒继续西行。\nOn Yellow Wind Ridge the Yellow Wind Monster blinds Wukong with a magical wind. Bajie summons the Bodhisattva Lingji, who subdues the monster — revealed to be a rat demon from beneath Spirit Mountain. A divine doctor heals Wukong's eyes and the pilgrimage continues."},
{id:21,title:"流沙河界化流沙，木叉奉法收悟净",english:"The Flowing Sands River; Sha Wujing Joins the Pilgrimage",content:"师徒来到流沙河，河中妖怪阻路，猪八戒与其交战，互有胜负。悟空请来观音菩萨的弟子木叉，木叉以观音颈项上的红葫芦为舟，收服了沙和尚。沙和尚原为天宫卷帘大将，被贬下界，皈依取经队伍。\nAt the Flowing Sands River a monster blocks their path. Bajie cannot defeat him. Wukong summons Guanyin's disciple Moksa, who uses the Bodhisattva's red gourd to subdue the monster — revealed to be the former Curtain-Lifting General of Heaven, now named Sha Wujing. Sandy becomes the fourth member of the pilgrimage."},
{id:22,title:"八戒大战流沙河，木叉奉法收悟净",english:"Sandy Joins as Third Disciple; the Pilgrimage Team Is Complete",content:"沙和尚加入取经队伍，至此师徒四人组合完成：唐僧、孙悟空、猪八戒、沙和尚，加上白龙马，五人各司其职，踏上了漫漫西行之路。队伍成型之后，一路面对的妖魔鬼怪更加强大，但众人齐心合力，共克时艰。\nWith Sandy joining, the four-person pilgrimage team is complete: Tripitaka the master, Wukong the protector, Bajie the laborer, Sandy the packer, and the white dragon horse as mount. Together they face increasingly formidable demons, but their combined strength and growing teamwork make them a formidable group."},
{id:23,title:"三藏不忘本，四圣试禅心",english:"The Four Bodhisattvas Test the Pilgrims' Resolve with Beautiful Women",content:"黎山老母与观音、普贤、文殊菩萨化身美女，要招四人为女婿以测试禅心。唐僧、悟空、沙僧分别经受住了考验，只有猪八戒经不住诱惑，上当受骗，被缚于树上一夜。众佛显现真身，对猪八戒的贪心深加责备。\nThe Bodhisattva of Lishan Mountain and three others disguise themselves as beautiful women to test the pilgrims' celibacy. Tripitaka, Wukong, and Sandy pass; Bajie fails spectacularly, eagerly trying to marry one of them, and ends up tied to a tree overnight. The Bodhisattvas reveal themselves and chide Bajie's lust."},
{id:24,title:"万寿山大仙留故友，五庄观行者窃人参",english:"The Immortal Welcomes Old Friends; Wukong Steals the Ginseng Fruit",content:"万寿山五庄观的镇元大仙外出，嘱咐童子以人参果招待取经人。猪八戒馋嘴，怂恿悟空偷取人参果，悟空偷了三枚，四人分吃。事后遭镇元大仙追查，悟空偷偷将人参树推倒，酿成大祸，师徒被擒。\nWhile the Great Immortal Zhen Yuan is away, his boy servants serve the pilgrims the legendary ginseng fruits. Bajie's greed provokes Wukong to steal three more; the pilgrims eat them. When discovered, the shamed Wukong knocks down the precious tree, and the furious Great Immortal imprisons the entire group."},
{id:25,title:"镇元仙赶捉取经僧，孙行者大闹五庄观",english:"Zhen Yuan Pursues the Pilgrims; Wukong Seeks a Way to Revive the Ginseng Tree",content:"悟空多次出逃均被捉回，最终请来观音菩萨，用观音净瓶中的杨柳枝蘸甘露洒在人参树上，使其复活。镇元大仙见悟空有情有义，与他结为兄弟，以人参果设宴款待众人，师徒欢喜继续西行。\nWukong escapes repeatedly but is always recaptured. Eventually he seeks Guanyin, who uses her willow branch and pure water to revive the sacred tree. The Great Immortal, impressed by Wukong's perseverance, becomes his sworn brother and hosts a great feast of ginseng fruits before the pilgrims move on."},
{id:26,title:"尸魔三戏唐三藏，圣僧恨逐美猴王",english:"The White Bone Demon Tricks Tripitaka Three Times; He Banishes Wukong",content:"白骨精三变女子、老妪、老翁来诱骗唐僧，均被悟空识破并打死。唐僧被猪八戒挑唆，认为悟空滥杀无辜，写下贬书，将悟空逐出师门。悟空伤心欲绝，却仍三拜唐僧，不舍离去，回花果山去了。\nThe White Bone Demon transforms into a young woman, an old mother, and an old man to trick the pilgrims. Wukong sees through all three disguises and kills the demon each time. Bajie stirs up trouble; Tripitaka, blinded by surface appearances, dismisses Wukong. Wukong weeps but obeys, returning to Flower-Fruit Mountain."},
{id:27,title:"尸魔三戏唐三藏，圣僧恨逐美猴王（续）",english:"The Pilgrims Suffer Without Wukong; Bajie Fetches Him Back",content:"悟空被逐后，唐僧继续西行，很快遭遇宝象国妖魔黄袍怪。黄袍怪将唐僧变成老虎关押，众人束手无策。猪八戒不得不前往花果山，厚着脸皮请回了悟空。悟空回来后，不计前嫌，立刻全力营救唐僧。\nWithout Wukong the pilgrims quickly fall into serious trouble — Yellow Robe Monster transforms Tripitaka into a tiger. Bajie swallows his pride and travels to Flower-Fruit Mountain to beg Wukong's return. Wukong bears no grudge; he immediately rushes to rescue his master."},
{id:28,title:"花果山群妖聚义，黑松林三藏逢魔",english:"Wukong Returns to Flower-Fruit Mountain; the Pilgrims Face New Perils",content:"悟空回花果山，得知部下受到猎人的大肆杀害，心疼不已。悟空教导众猴要规避人类侵害，同时心中始终挂念唐僧，终于下定决心弃山救主，回归取经队伍，继续护送唐僧踏上西行之路。\nReturning home, Wukong finds many of his monkey followers have been killed by hunters. He reorganizes the troop, but his thoughts keep returning to Tripitaka, and ultimately he cannot stay away — he leaves again to rejoin the pilgrimage."},
{id:29,title:"脱难江流来国土，承恩八戒转山林",english:"The Pilgrims Rescue the Baoxiang Kingdom's Princess",content:"宝象国公主被黄袍怪掳去十三年，悟空与妖怪大战，最终发现黄袍怪原是天宫奎木狼下凡，被天庭召回。唐僧恢复人形，与宝象国王重逢，师徒四人在宝象国休整后继续踏上西行旅程。\nThe kingdom of Baoxiang's princess was kidnapped 13 years ago by Yellow Robe Monster, who turns out to be the divine Kui Wood Wolf come down from heaven. He is recalled to heaven and Tripitaka is restored to human form. The pilgrims rest in Baoxiang before pressing west."},
{id:30,title:"邪魔侵正法，意马忆心猿",english:"The Wuji Kingdom Story — Wukong Revives the Dead King",content:"乌鸡国的国王被道士假冒，被推入井中淹死，道士冒充国王三年。国王鬼魂托梦唐僧，求其相助。悟空揭穿了假国王的身份，与之激战，又下井救出了真国王的尸身，用金丹救活了国王，大快人心。\nIn Wuji Kingdom, the real king was drowned by a demon disguised as a Daoist who has ruled in his place for three years. The dead king's ghost appeals to Tripitaka in a dream. Wukong exposes the imposter, retrieves the king's body from the well, and uses an immortal pill to resurrect him — justice served."},
{id:31,title:"猪八戒义激猴王，孙行者智降妖怪",english:"Bajie Goads Wukong Back to Action; Wukong Defeats the Monster Through Cleverness",content:"在多次事件中，八戒虽懒惰贪吃，但关键时刻也能与悟空并肩作战，二人的关系虽时有磕绊，却是彼此不可或缺的伙伴。取经路上的一场场危难，考验着每个人的意志，也使队伍更加团结。\nThough Bajie is often lazy and greedy, he and Wukong develop an odd but genuine partnership — bickering constantly but relying on each other when it truly matters. Their dynamic gives the journey much of its humor and warmth, and their mutual dependence deepens with each successive trial."},
{id:32,title:"平顶山功曹传信，莲花洞木母逢灾",english:"Wukong Scouts Flat-Top Mountain; Bajie Is Captured at Lotus Cave",content:"平顶山莲花洞金角大王和银角大王乃太上老君的两个童子，奉命下界磨炼唐僧。二妖有葫芦、羊脂玉净瓶等五件法宝，威力无穷。悟空多次设计却被识破，猪八戒被擒入葫芦，情况十分危急。\nAt Flat-Top Mountain the Golden Horned and Silver Horned Kings — actually Laozi's two young servants on a mission — possess five powerful magic treasures, including a gourd and a jade bottle that can trap anyone called by name. Wukong must outmaneuver them through cunning, but Bajie is captured in the gourd."},
{id:33,title:"外道迷真性，元神助本心",english:"Wukong Steals the Demons' Magic Gourds; He Rescues His Companions",content:"悟空设计偷换了妖怪的法宝宝葫芦，又将自己的毫毛变作相同的宝葫芦迷惑妖怪。在太白金星的提示下，悟空冒充太上老君，骗走了妖怪的其他法宝，最终救出了被困的唐僧和八戒，打败了两个妖王。\nWukong tricks the demons, swaps their magic gourd for a fake, and disguises himself as Laozi to steal their remaining treasures. With their weapons neutralized, he defeats the two demon kings and rescues the captured pilgrims. The adventure illustrates Wukong's unmatched resourcefulness."},
{id:34,title:"魔王巡逻，唐僧有难",english:"The Pilgrims Encounter the Black Rooster Kingdom Demon",content:"取经途中，悟空屡次识破妖魔的变化和诡计，以金箍棒和七十二变化与之周旋。唐僧虽肉眼不能识妖，却坚定持戒，以慈悲之心感化众生，师徒二人的配合日益默契。\nThe pilgrims face constant tests from demons who are often themselves celestial beings on divine assignment. Wukong's ability to see through disguises complements Tripitaka's unwavering compassion and discipline. Their respective strengths make them each indispensable to the pilgrimage."},
{id:35,title:"外道施威欺正性，心猿获宝伏邪魔",english:"Wukong Obtains the Purple Gold Red Gourd; the Demon's Treasures Are Turned Against Him",content:"悟空凭借智慧和勇气，多次化险为夷，从妖魔手中夺取法宝反制敌人。每一次胜利都证明了悟空的成长，从最初的桀骜不驯，到如今为了保护师父甘愿牺牲的护法神。\nWukong repeatedly uses captured weapons against their former owners. Each victory shows his growth from the rebellious demon of his youth into a genuine protector willing to sacrifice for his master. His journey mirrors Tripitaka's spiritual one."},
{id:36,title:"心猿正处诸缘伏，劈破旁门见月明",english:"Wukong Meditates; Tripitaka Composes a Poem on the Moon",content:"在一处古刹，唐僧触景生情，望月思乡，吟诗抒怀。悟空开导唐僧，劝其不要动凡心，专注取经大业。师徒之间的情感交流日益深厚，虽然悟空时常与唐僧有所冲突，但内心深处对师父的尊重和爱护是真实的。\nIn an ancient temple, Tripitaka gazes at the moon and composes a melancholy poem about his longing for home. Wukong gently reminds him to focus on their sacred mission. The relationship between master and disciple deepens through moments like these, revealing genuine affection beneath the surface conflicts."},
{id:37,title:"鬼王夜谒唐三藏，悟空神化引婴儿",english:"The Ghost King Visits Tripitaka at Night; Wukong Deals with the Infant Demon",content:"唐僧一行来到一处黑暗之地，遭遇鬼王的困扰，险象环生。悟空保护师父，与鬼王展开交锋，最终将其击退。此类连续不断的考验，磨砺了师徒四人的意志，也深化了他们之间的信任与依赖。\nIn a dark domain the Ghost King harasses the pilgrims. Wukong drives him off after a fierce confrontation. Successive trials forge the team's unity and deepen the trust between them — the repeated pattern of danger and rescue binding them together as surely as the golden headband binds Wukong."},
{id:38,title:"婴儿问母知邪正，金木参玄见假真",english:"The Infant Boy and the Feminine Principle; Symbolic Encounters on the Road",content:"此段旅程中充满了玄妙的象征：婴儿象征纯真之心，金与木象征乾坤阴阳。悟空多次面对假形真魔，凭借火眼金睛识破真相。这些试炼既是外在的妖魔考验，也是内在心性修炼的寓言。\nThis section is rich with symbolic meaning: the infant represents the innocent original mind; gold and wood symbolize cosmic yin and yang. Wukong's Golden Eyes repeatedly pierce through disguise to truth. The monsters are at once real enemies and allegorical tests of the mind's ability to see through illusion."},
{id:39,title:"一粒金丹天上得，三年故主世间生",english:"Wukong Revives the Dead King with a Golden Pill",content:"乌鸡国国王被假道士杀死，鬼魂向唐僧求助。悟空潜入地府，向阎王求取国王魂魄，又向太上老君借得金丹一粒。国王尸身浸泡井中三年，悟空用金丹将其复活。国王重登王位，假道士现形，被斩首示众。\nThe ghost of Wuji Kingdom's murdered king appeals to Tripitaka for help. Wukong descends to the underworld to retrieve the king's soul and borrows an immortality pill from Laozi. The king's body, kept in a well for three years, is revived by the pill. The king returns to his throne and the imposter demon is executed."},
{id:40,title:"婴儿戏化禅心乱，猿马刀归木母空",english:"The Red Child Demon Captures Tripitaka; Wukong Seeks Guanyin's Help",content:"红孩儿是牛魔王之子，神通广大，以三昧真火攻击悟空，令悟空吃尽苦头，连天庭和龙王的水都浇不熄这火。悟空无奈，只能请求观音菩萨出手降妖。观音以莲花座降红孩儿，收为善财童子。\nRed Boy — son of the Bull Demon King — captures Tripitaka and attacks Wukong with Three-Flavors True Fire, which neither Wukong's powers nor rain from heaven can extinguish. Wukong appeals to Guanyin, who subdues Red Boy with her lotus throne and takes him as her attendant — another demon transformed into a servant of enlightenment."},
{id:41,title:"心猿遭火败，木母被魔擒",english:"Wukong Is Burned by the Three-Flavors True Fire",content:"三昧真火乃天地至阳之火，普通水火均无法扑灭，悟空与红孩儿三番五次交战，屡战屡败，是少见的真正遭受重创的一次。此战充分说明，悟空虽然神通广大，在天地间也有克星，有些困难仅凭自身之力无法解决。\nThe Three-Flavors True Fire defeats Wukong repeatedly — one of the rare instances where he faces something he genuinely cannot overcome alone. Red Boy proves to be among the most formidable opponents of the entire journey. The episode shows that even the greatest power has its limits."},
{id:42,title:"大圣殷勤拜南海，观音慈善缚红孩",english:"Wukong Respectfully Seeks Guanyin's Help; the Bodhisattva Subdues Red Boy",content:"悟空三上南海，请求观音菩萨相助。观音以莲花宝座和各种法器，一步步降服了三昧真火，制服了红孩儿。观音点化红孩儿，令其皈依佛法，成为她的侍童善财童子，自此在菩萨身边修行。\nWukong makes three trips to the Southern Sea to implore Guanyin's help. The Bodhisattva methodically neutralizes the True Fire and subdues Red Boy. Rather than destroying him, Guanyin transforms the demon into her attendant, the Sudhana Boy — demonstrating Buddhism's power to redeem even the most fearsome opposition."},
{id:43,title:"黑河妖孽擒僧去，西洋龙子捉鼍回",english:"The Black River Monster Captures Tripitaka; the Dragon Prince Captures the Alligator",content:"黑水河老鼍龙趁乱将唐僧掳走，藏于水府之中。悟空请来西海龙王之子摩昂太子，太子下水与老鼍龙激战，最终将老鼍龙擒获，救出唐僧。西行路上，悟空深谙借助神灵之力的重要性。\nThe ancient Alligator of the Black River kidnaps Tripitaka and imprisons him underwater. Wukong enlists the Dragon King's son Moan, who dives in and captures the Alligator in fierce underwater combat, freeing Tripitaka. Wukong increasingly relies on a network of divine allies."},
{id:44,title:"法身元运逢车力，心正妖邪度脊关",english:"The Pilgrims Reach the Kingdom of Cart-Slow; Wukong Challenges the Three Daoist Priests",content:"车迟国三位道士受国王宠信，压迫和尚，悟空替和尚们鸣不平，与三妖展开了一系列有趣的竞赛：求雨、猜谜、砍头复生等。悟空凭借神通和机智，逐一击败三位妖道，揭穿了他们的真面目。\nIn Cart-Slow Kingdom three Daoist demons enjoy royal favor and oppress Buddhist monks. Wukong challenges them to a series of competitions — rain-making, guessing contests, decapitation and revival. Through superior magic and cunning he defeats all three and exposes them, freeing the enslaved monks."},
{id:45,title:"三清观大圣留名，车迟国猴王显法",english:"Wukong Impersonates the Three Pure Ones; He Wins the Rain-Making Contest",content:"悟空在三清观偷吃神仙供品，又化身为三清接受道士跪拜，令人忍俊不禁。随后在降雨比赛中，悟空与虎力大仙比拼，暗中阻扰对方施法，使自己获得胜利。悟空的顽皮与智慧在此段故事中展露无遗。\nWukong steals offerings from the Three Pure Ones' altar and disguises himself as a deity to accept worship from the demons — supremely sacrilegious comedy. In the subsequent rain contest, he secretly sabotages the Tiger Strength Immortal's magic to ensure his own success. Wukong's mischievous genius is at its peak here."},
{id:46,title:"外道弄强欺正法，心猿显圣灭诸邪",english:"The Daoist Demons Are Defeated; Wukong Survives Decapitation, Boiling, and Skinning",content:"三位妖道与悟空进行了砍头、油锅、剥皮等险恶比试，悟空凭借神通安然过关，而三位妖道则在各项比试中现出原形，分别是虎、鹿、羊，被悟空一一击毙。车迟国的和尚们得到解救，佛法得以弘扬。\nThe three demon Daoists challenge Wukong to survive beheading, boiling in oil, and skinning alive — tests Wukong passes with supernatural ease. When the demons attempt the same, they are exposed as a tiger, a deer, and a goat and are killed. The monks of Cart-Slow are freed and Buddhism restored to royal favor."},
{id:47,title:"圣僧夜阻通天水，金木垂慈救小童",english:"The Pilgrims Reach the Universal River; Wukong and Bajie Rescue Children Meant for Sacrifice",content:"通天河畔，灵感大王每年要吃一对童男童女祭祀。悟空和八戒变化成童男童女，代替真实孩童被送入庙中，趁机击伤灵感大王。此段充分展示了悟空保护弱小、不畏强暴的侠义精神。\nAt the Universal River an annual sacrifice of a boy and girl is demanded by a demon. Wukong and Bajie disguise themselves as the child offerings and attack the demon from inside the temple. The episode shows the heroes at their most heroic — protecting innocent children from a monstrous rite."},
{id:48,title:"魔弄寒风飘大雪，僧思拜佛履层冰",english:"The Demon Creates a Blizzard; Tripitaka Crosses the Ice",content:"灵感大王受伤后兴风作浪，造出大雪封河，让唐僧无法渡河。通天河结冰，唐僧骑马渡河，行至中途，冰面突然破裂，唐僧落水，又被灵感大王掳入水府。悟空八戒再度设法营救。\nThe injured demon freezes the river with a supernatural blizzard, blocking the pilgrims. Tripitaka attempts to cross on foot over the ice, but the demon breaks the ice and captures him again. Wukong and Bajie must mount yet another rescue mission, this time into an aquatic prison."},
{id:49,title:"三藏有灾沉水宅，观音解厄脱鱼篮",english:"Guanyin Appears with the Fish Basket; the River Demon Is Subdued",content:"悟空无法入水，请来观音菩萨。观音持竹篮，让悟空在岸上念咒，原来通天河妖是南海观音放生的一条金鱼，多年修炼成精。观音用竹篮将金鱼收回，唐僧得救，众人继续西行。\nUnable to enter the water himself, Wukong again calls on Guanyin. The Bodhisattva arrives with a bamboo fish basket; it is revealed that the Universal River demon is actually a golden fish she once released into the sea that has cultivated power over the years. She reclaims it in her basket, and Tripitaka is freed."},
{id:50,title:"情乱性从因爱欲，神昏心动遇魔头",english:"Wukong's Staff Is Stolen; He Faces the Golden-Horned Rhinoceros Demon",content:"金兜山的独角兕大王是太上老君的青牛，此妖有金刚琢法宝，能套住天地间一切法器。悟空的金箍棒、众天将的兵器均被套走，连托塔天王的玲珑宝塔也不例外，悟空陷入极大的困境之中。\nOn Golden Pocket Mountain the Rhinoceros Demon — actually Laozi's green bull — possesses a diamond ring that can trap any weapon in the universe. Wukong's staff, every heavenly general's weapon, even Heavenly King Li's pagoda are seized. Wukong is desperately outmatched for the first time since his youth."},
{id:51,title:"心猿空用千般计，水火无功难炼魔",english:"Wukong's Many Stratagems All Fail Against the Rhinoceros Demon",content:"悟空屡出奇计，变化百端，却每次都被金刚琢套走兵器而失败。此妖堪称悟空最难对付的对手之一，因为他不靠力量，而靠法宝取胜。最后悟空不得不请太上老君出山，才得以将青牛收服。\nEvery transformation and strategy Wukong attempts ends with his weapon stolen by the diamond ring. This demon is uniquely dangerous because he defeats not through strength but through superior technology. Ultimately only Laozi himself can reclaim his own bull — illustrating that some problems require their own original owner to solve."},
{id:52,title:"悟空大闹金兜洞，如来暗示主人公",english:"Wukong Attacks the Diamond Cave; Laozi Reclaims the Bull",content:"如来佛祖暗示悟空，独角兕大王乃太上老君的坐骑青牛。悟空请太上老君前来，太上老君以金刚琢轻松将青牛收回，那金刚琢正是太上老君的原物。此事结束后，师徒继续上路。\nFollowing a hint from the Buddha, Wukong discovers the demon's true identity as Laozi's own bull. Laozi arrives and effortlessly recaptures his property with the same diamond ring — since it was his to begin with. The episode suggests that the origin of demonic power is often divine, a recurring theme of the novel."},
{id:53,title:"禅主吞餐怀鬼孕，黄婆运水解邪胎",english:"Tripitaka and Bajie Drink the River of Motherhood Water and Become Pregnant",content:"女儿国附近有一条子母河，饮水者无论男女皆会怀孕。唐僧和八戒误饮河水，腹中有孕，疼痛不已。悟空和沙僧四处寻求解药，找到了落胎泉水，令二人饮下，方才化解了这段奇异的遭遇。\nNear the Kingdom of Women, the River of Motherhood causes anyone who drinks from it to become pregnant. Tripitaka and Bajie inadvertently drink the water and experience pregnancy pangs. Wukong and Sandy search desperately for an antidote and eventually obtain water from the Miscarriage Spring, ending the bizarre predicament."},
{id:54,title:"法性西来逢女国，心猿定计脱烟花",english:"Tripitaka Is Detained by the Queen of Women; Wukong Plans Their Escape",content:"女儿国女王爱慕唐僧，欲嫁他为王。唐僧为保众人安全，假意应允，实则等待悟空找机会逃脱。唐僧忍辱负重，与女王周旋，悟空则在暗中打点逃离之路，师徒再次合力渡过难关。\nThe Queen of Women falls in love with Tripitaka and insists on marrying him. Tripitaka endures the situation to protect his companions while pretending to agree, buying time for Wukong to arrange their escape. The episode tests Tripitaka's monastic resolve and shows his capacity for strategic patience."},
{id:55,title:"色邪淫戏唐三藏，性正修持不坏身",english:"The Pipa Demon Stings Wukong; Tripitaka Is Imprisoned Again",content:"琵琶洞的蝎子精对唐僧美色起意，将其掳入洞中。蝎子精有毒刺，悟空、八戒皆受其伤，无计可施。悟空四处寻找克制蝎子精的方法，最终得知昂日星官的鸡鸣可令蝎子精魂飞魄散，遂借来金光，将蝎子精击杀。\nThe Pipa Scorpion demon kidnaps Tripitaka and wounds both Wukong and Bajie with her venomous sting. Wukong researches the demon's weakness and discovers that the crow of the Mao-Day Rooster is lethal to scorpions; he borrows its golden light and kills the demon."},
{id:56,title:"神狂诛草寇，道昧放心猿",english:"Wukong Kills Bandits; Tripitaka Dismisses Him Again",content:"一伙劫匪拦路，悟空将其全部打死。唐僧再次以杀生之罪责备悟空，又写下贬书，将悟空逐走。悟空再度被迫离开，独自前往南海见观音菩萨诉苦。唐僧坚守慈悲戒律，悟空的暴烈天性与佛法戒律的冲突贯穿全篇。\nRobbers ambush the pilgrims; Wukong kills them all. Tripitaka again dismisses Wukong for taking life, writing another letter of banishment. This second dismissal highlights the ongoing tension between Wukong's violent nature and the demands of Buddhist discipline — a tension that drives the novel's deepest themes."},
{id:57,title:"真行者落伽山诉苦，假猴王水帘洞誓同",english:"Six-Eared Macaque Impersonates Wukong; the Real Wukong Goes to Guanyin",content:"一只六耳猕猴趁机冒充悟空，打伤唐僧，夺走行李。真悟空与假悟空势均力敌，连观音、玉帝、地府阎王均无法分辨真假。最后二人打到灵山，由如来佛祖识破六耳猕猴，将其击毙。\nA Six-Eared Macaque impersonates Wukong exactly — attacking Tripitaka, stealing the luggage. Even Guanyin, the Jade Emperor, and the King of Hell cannot tell them apart. Only the Buddha himself can perceive the difference; he identifies the imposter and Wukong kills his double."},
{id:58,title:"二心搅乱大乾坤，一体难修真寂灭",english:"The Two Wukongs' Battle Confuses Heaven; Only the Buddha Can Tell Them Apart",content:"真假悟空之战是全书最精彩的篇章之一，深刻的隐喻意味是：六耳猕猴代表悟空内心的另一面，代表执念与我执。如来一语道破：世间只有一个\"真心\"，执念与真心虽形似，究竟不同。此段乃全书的哲学高峰。\nThe battle of the two Wukongs is one of the novel's philosophical peaks. The Six-Eared Macaque represents Wukong's alter ego — his own pride, self-will, and inner demons. Only the Buddha can distinguish true mind from false mind. When Wukong kills his double, he symbolically kills his own final resistance to enlightenment."},
{id:59,title:"唐三藏路阻火焰山，孙行者一调芭蕉扇",english:"Tripitaka's Path Is Blocked by the Flaming Mountain; Wukong Tries to Borrow the Fan",content:"火焰山横亘于取经路上，方圆八百里，寸草不生，过山必借铁扇公主的芭蕉扇扇灭火焰。铁扇公主是红孩儿之母，因悟空曾收伏红孩儿，对悟空怀有恨意，拒绝借扇，反用假扇愚弄悟空。\nThe Flaming Mountain blocks the road west, eight hundred miles of fire so intense nothing can survive. The only way past is with the Banana Leaf Fan held by Princess Iron Fan — mother of Red Boy, whom Wukong helped defeat. She refuses to help and gives him a fake fan that makes the fires worse."},
{id:60,title:"牛魔王罢战赴华筵，孙行者二调芭蕉扇",english:"The Bull Demon King Feasts While Wukong Tries Again; Wukong Steals the Fan by Disguise",content:"悟空变作小虫混入铁扇公主体内，迫使她交出芭蕉扇，却被牛魔王趁机变作猪八戒的模样骗回。牛魔王是悟空当年结拜的七兄弟之一，如今成了敌人。悟空与牛魔王的冲突充满了旧情与新恨的交织。\nWukong shrinks to enter Princess Iron Fan's body and forces her to surrender the fan — but the Bull Demon King, Wukong's former sworn brother, tricks him and takes it back. The confrontation between the two former brothers carries both old affection and genuine enmity."},
{id:61,title:"猪八戒助力败魔王，孙行者三调芭蕉扇",english:"Bajie Assists in Defeating the Bull Demon King; Wukong Gets the Fan on the Third Try",content:"悟空与牛魔王大战，势均力敌，随后哪吒、托塔天王等天兵天将赶来助阵。众人合力将牛魔王制服，铁扇公主被迫交出真正的芭蕉扇。悟空用芭蕉扇扑灭了火焰山的火，当地土地爷感恩不尽。\nWukong battles the Bull Demon King to a standstill. Heavenly reinforcements including Nezha and the Heavenly King arrive to help subdue the demon. Princess Iron Fan surrenders the real fan. Wukong fans out the Flaming Mountain's fires, and the local earth god expresses boundless gratitude."},
{id:62,title:"涤垢洗心惟扫塔，缚魔归正乃修身",english:"The Pilgrims Help a Kingdom Restore Its Stolen Pagoda; Justice Is Served",content:"师徒来到祭赛国，得知宝林寺九级琉璃塔内的舍利子被两个妖魔偷走，致使国中连降血雨。悟空和八戒夜探宝塔，与妖魔激战，夺回了舍利，物归原处，使国家重获平安。\nIn Jizan Kingdom the precious relic enshrined in a nine-story pagoda has been stolen by demons, causing a rain of blood. Wukong and Bajie make a night raid and battle the demons to recover the relic. Justice restored, the kingdom is saved — illustrating how the pilgrims' mission benefits all they encounter."},
{id:63,title:"二僧荡怪闹龙宫，群圣除邪获宝贝",english:"Two Monks Battle Demons in the Dragon Palace; Sacred Treasures Are Recovered",content:"悟空和八戒协力与水中妖怪大战，最终夺回了被盗的国宝，并将妖怪一一诛杀。在此过程中，悟空展示了他处理水下事务的能力，而八戒的水性也得到了发挥。两人性格迥异，配合却日益成熟。\nWukong and Bajie battle underwater demons to recover the stolen national treasures. The partnership between the two contrasting disciples has matured into something genuinely effective and even moving in its own comic way."},
{id:64,title:"荆棘岭悟能努力，木仙庵三藏谈诗",english:"Bajie Clears the Thorn Forest; Tripitaka Exchanges Poetry with the Wood Spirits",content:"荆棘岭上荆棘丛生，猪八戒用钉耙开路，劳苦功高。林中有修炼千年的树木成精，化为老者与唐僧谈诗论道，一夜逝去，唐僧被困林中。悟空寻来，打散树精，救出唐僧，师徒得以通过荆棘岭。\nOn Thorn Ridge Bajie laboriously clears a path with his rake. In the forest, ancient tree spirits take human form and engage Tripitaka in a night of poetry and philosophy, enchanting him. Wukong finds and disperses the spirits, rescuing his master. The interlude shows how beauty and culture can be as trapping as brute force."},
{id:65,title:"妖邪假设小雷音，四众皆遭大厄难",english:"The Demon Sets Up a Fake Thunderclap Monastery; All Four Pilgrims Are Captured",content:"黄眉老佛化作佛堂，引唐僧一行入内，趁机将四人全部擒拿，困入宝囊之中。此妖乃弥勒佛的扫地童子，法力不弱。悟空苦思脱身之计，终于在弥勒佛的暗中相助下，找到了克制宝囊的方法，全身而退。\nA demon sets up a counterfeit Thunderclap Temple to trap the pilgrims; all four are captured and imprisoned in a magic sack. The demon is Maitreya Buddha's sweeper boy gone rogue. With Maitreya's secret help, Wukong finds a way to counter the sack and free everyone."},
{id:66,title:"诸神遭毒手，弥勒缚黄眉",english:"The Heavenly Generals Are Defeated; Maitreya Subdues the Yellow Brow Demon",content:"黄眉老佛法力惊人，连天庭众将都被他的人种袋收入囊中，悟空一筹莫展。弥勒佛亲自出马，设计将黄眉老佛诱入人种袋，令其弄巧成拙自食其果，被收回原处管束，西行路上又一难关得以化解。\nYellow Brow's magic sack captures one heavenly general after another. Wukong is helpless until Maitreya himself appears and tricks the demon into the very sack he used on others. The demon is returned to his master. The principle is clear: the demon's own weapon becomes the instrument of his defeat."},
{id:67,title:"拯救驼罗困苦天，脱离秽污须菩提",english:"The Pilgrims Help the Camel Kingdom; the Headless Demon Is Defeated",content:"驼罗庄遭受妖魔荼毒，百姓苦不堪言。悟空率众好汉出手相助，历经苦战，降服了妖魔，解救了庄中百姓。此类济危扶困的故事贯穿全书，说明取经之行不仅是个人修行，也是普度众生的大乘精神体现。\nCamel Hamlet is tormented by a demon. The pilgrims intervene, battle fiercely, and defeat the monster, saving the villagers. Such episodes of heroes helping ordinary people recur throughout the journey, embodying the Mahayana principle that true enlightenment must benefit all sentient beings."},
{id:68,title:"朱紫国唐僧论前世，孙行者施针救国王",english:"Tripitaka Discusses Past Lives; Wukong Uses Acupuncture to Cure the King",content:"朱紫国国王因三年前悔婚之事，心病郁结，身体每况愈下。悟空诊脉施针，以丸药治好了国王的病。此段展示了悟空博学多才的一面，他不仅会打妖怪，还通医术，令人刮目相看。\nThe King of Zhuzi Kingdom has been ill for three years, his illness rooted in emotional trauma. Wukong takes his pulse, prescribes medicine, and cures him — revealing a dimension of Wukong's abilities rarely seen: he is also a physician. The king's cure is both medical and spiritual."},
{id:69,title:"心主夜间修药物，君王筵上论妖邪",english:"Wukong Compounds the Medicine at Night; the King Hears the Story of the Demon",content:"悟空取得了制药所需的奇特原料，在月夜精心配制丸药。国王服药后果然痊愈，不禁叹服悟空的医术高超。随后众人得知国王的王后被妖怪掳走，决意出手相助夺回王后。\nWukong compounds the medicine using extraordinary ingredients. The king is cured and astonished. Learning the queen was kidnapped by a demon years ago, the pilgrims resolve to rescue her too, extending their compassion beyond their immediate mission."},
{id:70,title:"妖魔宝放烟沙火，悟空计盗紫金铃",english:"The Demon's Treasures Unleash Smoke and Fire; Wukong Steals the Purple Gold Bell",content:"赛太岁妖怪有三件宝贝：紫金铃、幌金绳、破山虎，个个厉害。悟空费尽心机，盗取了紫金铃，以牙还牙，用妖怪自己的法宝攻击对手，终于将妖怪制服，救出了王后。\nThe demon Sai Taisuei possesses three magic treasures. Wukong steals the Purple Gold Bell and uses the demon's own weapon against him — a recurring tactic of turning an enemy's strength into weakness. The queen is rescued and returned to the grateful king."},
{id:71,title:"行者假名降怪犼，观音现象伏熊罴",english:"Wukong Defeats the Rhinoceros Demons; Guanyin Tames the Leopard",content:"狮驼岭有三大魔王：青毛狮子怪、黄牙象怪、大鹏金翅鸟，三魔合力，连悟空也差点吃了大亏。大鹏金翅鸟是如来的舅舅，神通极为强大，悟空请来如来佛祖，方才将三魔制服，此为全书最惊险的一段。\nLion-Camel Ridge is guarded by three great demons: a blue lion, a white elephant, and the Great Roc — who is actually the Buddha's maternal uncle. Even Wukong is nearly defeated; only the Buddha himself can subdue the Roc. This is perhaps the most dangerous confrontation of the entire journey."},
{id:72,title:"盘丝洞七情迷本，濯垢泉八戒忘形",english:"The Spider Women Captivate the Pilgrims; Bajie Spies on Them Bathing",content:"盘丝洞七个蜘蛛精变作美女，迷住唐僧，以蜘蛛丝将他困在洞中。悟空杀来，蜘蛛精从肚脐放出丝线，悟空无从应对。八戒对蜘蛛美女心存贪念，行动时难以集中，是这段故事的喜剧亮点。\nSeven Spider Women enchant Tripitaka and imprison him in their cave. They shoot silk from their navels — an attack Wukong's golden staff cannot counter. Bajie's lewd fascination with the spider women undermines the rescue attempt. His distraction provides both humor and cautionary commentary on desire."},
{id:73,title:"情因旧恨生新怪，手足相残成大险",english:"The Centipede Demon Wounds Wukong; Rooster's Crow Defeats the Spider Women",content:"多目怪百眼魔君是蜘蛛精的师兄，有千百双眼睛，每双眼睛都能放出光圈，令悟空左支右绌。毕方鸟的鸣叫克制蜘蛛精，悟空借来昂日星官化成的鸡形，以鸡鸣击散蜘蛛精，一举解围。\nThe Hundred-Eyed Demon Master, sibling to the spider women, can shoot magic rings from his thousand eyes — overwhelming Wukong. The sound of a rooster is fatal to spider spirits; Wukong borrows the divine rooster form and crows, scattering the spider women and defeating the centipede demon."},
{id:74,title:"长庚传报魔头狠，行者施为变化能",english:"Wukong Uses Transformations to Scout the Lion-Camel Demon's Lair",content:"狮驼国被三大魔王占据，小妖无数，形势严峻。悟空化作各种形状混入敌营刺探情报，同时呼叫天兵相助。此段充分展示了悟空七十二变的精妙运用，在智取敌人的过程中展现了超群的临机应变能力。\nLion-Camel Kingdom has been seized by three demon kings commanding an army of monsters. Wukong infiltrates in various disguises to gather intelligence while calling for heavenly reinforcements. This episode showcases the full range of the 72 Transformations as a tool of espionage and strategy."},
{id:75,title:"心猿钻透阴阳窍，魔王还归大道真",english:"Wukong Is Swallowed and Escapes from Within; the Demons Are Subdued",content:"大鹏金翅鸟将悟空一口吞入腹中，悟空在妖怪体内大施神通，折腾得大鹏痛苦不堪，不得不将悟空吐出。最终佛祖出面，以慈悲和神力将三大魔王全部收服，化解了这场最大的危机。\nThe Great Roc swallows Wukong, but inside the beast Wukong causes such internal havoc that the Roc is forced to spit him out. The Buddha then arrives and subdues all three demon kings through compassion and divine power. The greatest crisis of the journey is resolved not by violence alone but by the ultimate authority of enlightenment."},
{id:76,title:"心神居舍魔归性，木母同降怪体真",english:"The Pilgrims Pass Through the Country of Bhiksha; Child-Eating Demons Are Exposed",content:"比丘国的国王被妖道迷惑，要取一千一百一十一个小儿的心肝做药引。悟空发现真相，救下孩子们，揭穿了妖道的阴谋，并追杀妖道。妖道是一只白鹿，御用的国丈是一只狐狸，均被悟空击毙。\nThe king of Bhiksha has been bewitched by a demon disguised as his royal advisor, demanding the hearts of 1,111 children for a magical medicine. Wukong exposes the plot, saves the children, and kills the demons — a white deer and a fox. The children are rescued and the kingdom purified."},
{id:77,title:"群魔欺本性，一体拜真如",english:"The Pilgrims Reach the Dharma-Destroying Kingdom; Buddhism Is Restored",content:"灭法国王因曾发誓杀万名和尚，大肆迫害佛法。悟空趁夜剃光了全城人的头发，让众人都变成和尚，国王震惊之余，也悟出了佛法无边的道理，从此不再迫害和尚，取经队伍得以顺利通过。\nThe King of the Dharma-Destroying Kingdom has vowed to kill ten thousand monks and persecutes Buddhism. Wukong sneaks out at night and shaves the heads of everyone in the city — the king, his wives, all his ministers — turning them all into 'monks.' The king is stunned into realizing his folly and persecution ends."},
{id:78,title:"通天河再遇灵感大王，唐三藏两番遭毒手",english:"Reunion with the Alligator Demon at the Universal River",content:"师徒经过一番周折，再次来到通天河边，旧日的灵感大王重出江湖，再度拦截取经队伍。历经磨难的众人已非昔日可比，悟空更加成熟稳重，以更高超的策略应对旧敌，展示了成长与蜕变。\nThe pilgrims return to the Universal River and encounter the old demon once more. But the heroes of today are not the same as before; Wukong approaches the familiar enemy with greater wisdom and measured strategy, demonstrating the growth that years of trials have produced."},
{id:79,title:"寻洞擒妖逢老寿，当朝献宝喜龙颜",english:"Wukong Defeats the Old Demon of the Cave; a Kingdom Receives a Sacred Gift",content:"悟空深入妖穴，与洞中老妖激战，凭借丰富的实战经验和成熟的心智，最终胜利。西行路上，悟空已从最初的桀骜不驯，蜕变为真正的护法神，以智慧和慈悲兼济，守护着师父和众生。\nWukong enters deep into a demon's lair and defeats the ancient monster through mature strategy and accumulated experience. The contrast with his early recklessness is striking — he has genuinely grown into the role of enlightened protector, combining intelligence with compassion."},
{id:80,title:"姹女育阳求配偶，心猿护主识妖邪",english:"A Female Demon Wants to Marry Tripitaka; Wukong Recognizes Her",content:"一位女妖精对唐僧一见钟情，费尽心机欲与之成婚。悟空以火眼金睛识破女妖真身，但唐僧不信，坚持认为是凡人，再次与悟空产生冲突。这类误会反复出现，折射出信仰与理性之争的永恒主题。\nA demoness falls in love with Tripitaka and tries to lure him into marriage. Wukong sees through her disguise, but Tripitaka believes she is human and again doubts his disciple's judgment. This recurring pattern — demon in disguise, Wukong sees truth, Tripitaka believes the surface — embodies the challenge of perceiving reality through the veil of desire."},
{id:81,title:"镇海寺心猿知怪，黑松林三众寻师",english:"Wukong Senses Danger at the Coastal Temple; the Disciples Search for Their Master",content:"在黑松林，唐僧被伪装成垂死老人的妖怪所骗，再次被掳。悟空、八戒、沙僧四处寻找，历经周折，终于找到关押师父的妖洞。此时的三位弟子配合更加默契，共同保护师父的决心从未动摇。\nIn a dark forest a demon disguised as a dying old man tricks Tripitaka and captures him. The three disciples search frantically; finding the demon's lair, they work together more effectively than ever. Their unity and devotion to their master have been forged by years of shared trials."},
{id:82,title:"姹女求阳，元神护道",english:"The Jade Hare Demon; Chang'e and the Moon",content:"月宫玉兔化作公主，等待唐僧的到来，欲与之成婚。悟空查明真相，与玉兔展开追逐。玉兔的主人嫦娥赶来，以桂花树枝打倒玉兔，将其收回月宫。此段故事优美典雅，充满了中国传统月亮文化的意象。\nThe Jade Rabbit from the Moon Palace disguises herself as a princess to await and ensnare Tripitaka. Wukong exposes her; Chang'e the Moon Goddess herself arrives and beats the Jade Rabbit with a cassia branch, taking her home. The episode is luminous with traditional lunar imagery."},
{id:83,title:"心猿识得丹头，姹女还归本性",english:"Wukong Recognizes the Alchemy Formula; the Female Demon Is Redeemed",content:"取经路上，悟空识破了又一妖魔变化的美女，此妖乃修炼百年的狐狸精。悟空将其打回原形，妖精在死前恳求宽恕，悟空不为所动。此类情节反复提醒读者：美丽的外表可能是最危险的陷阱。\nWukong again identifies a beautiful woman as a demon — this time a fox spirit cultivated over centuries. He defeats her. Such repeated episodes insist on the danger of surface beauty and the spiritual necessity of piercing through appearance to underlying reality."},
{id:84,title:"难活南山大虫心，造化西方百岁功",english:"The Pilgrims Near the Western Heaven; Their Trials Are Almost Complete",content:"经历了九九八十一难，取经队伍已望见西天在望。唐僧内心既有对佛土的向往，也有对历经磨难的感慨。悟空此刻已完全转变，成了坚定而智慧的护法，而不再是当初那个叛逆的猴王，取经之行也是他的成道之路。\nAfter 81 trials, the pilgrims can almost see the Western Heaven. Tripitaka feels both longing for the Buddha's land and deep reflection on the suffering they have endured. Wukong has been completely transformed — the rebel monkey is now a disciplined, wise protector. The journey has been as much his path to enlightenment as Tripitaka's."},
{id:85,title:"心猿妒木母，魔主计吞禅",english:"Final Temptations Before the Western Heaven",content:"西天近在眼前，却仍有最后的考验。魔王出现，以甜言蜜语和美色诱惑唐僧，欲令他功亏一篑。悟空以坚定的护卫之心，识破最后的陷阱，保护师父度过了最后的关口，西天之路即将终结。\nWith the Western Heaven almost in sight, final temptations appear to test the pilgrims. A demon uses beauty and sweet words to try to lure Tripitaka into abandoning the mission at the last moment. Wukong, now supremely vigilant, sees through the final trap and protects his master through the last gate."},
{id:86,title:"木母助威征怪犼，金木参玄见假真",english:"The Pilgrims' Last Battle Before Reaching the Buddha's Land",content:"最后的战斗打响，悟空与最后一头妖怪激战，以毕生所学将其击败。此战象征着修道者在抵达目标前必须战胜的最后一个自我。胜利之后，一片祥云笼罩，西天的金光已经可以清晰看见。\nThe final battle sees Wukong defeat the last demon with everything he has learned. The confrontation symbolizes the last obstacle every cultivator must overcome before reaching the goal. In victory, golden light from the Western Heaven becomes clearly visible ahead."},
{id:87,title:"凤仙郡冒天止雨，孙大圣劝善施霖",english:"A Kingdom Suffers Drought for Impiety; Wukong Restores the Rain",content:"凤仙郡因郡侯亵渎了天庭供奉，老天久旱不雨，百姓苦不堪言。悟空了解原委，帮助郡侯悔过向善，感动了天庭，天降甘霖，郡民得救。此段说明，大慈大悲的精神在任何地方都能化解灾难。\nA district has suffered three years of drought as punishment for its governor's sacrilege. Wukong investigates, helps the governor sincerely repent, and moves heaven with his genuine remorse — rain falls again. The episode embodies the Buddhist principle that sincere repentance can transform any situation."},
{id:88,title:"禅到玉华施法会，心猿木母授门人",english:"The Pilgrims Teach the Jade Flower Kingdom's Princes; New Disciples Are Trained",content:"玉华县的三位王子仰慕师徒的武艺，拜三位徒弟为师学习武功，悟空传授棍法，八戒传授钯法，沙僧传授杖法。不料三位王子的兵器被豹子精偷走，引出了一场激烈的战斗，最终悟空将豹子精击败。\nThree princes of Jade Flower County beg to become disciples of Wukong, Bajie, and Sandy. The three disciples teach their respective fighting styles. When the princes' new weapons are stolen by a leopard demon, Wukong defeats the thief in fierce combat."},
{id:89,title:"黄狮精虚设钉钯会，金木土计闹豹头山",english:"The Yellow Lion Demon Schemes with a Spear Banquet; the Heroes Attack Leopard Head Mountain",content:"黄狮精是一头狮子妖怪，设宴庆贺，却不料是大鹏的爪牙。悟空与八戒、沙僧齐力出击豹头山，与黄狮精及其同伙激烈交战，最终三兄弟配合默契，将黄狮精及其党羽一一诛灭，为玉华县除去了心腹大患。\nThe Yellow Lion Demon, a crony of the Great Roc, hosts a banquet as a ruse. Wukong leads Bajie and Sandy in a coordinated assault on Leopard Head Mountain. Their teamwork has reached its highest point — three disciples fighting in perfect coordination to protect the places and people they encounter."},
{id:90,title:"师狮授受同归一，虎鹿羊兽革旧形",english:"The Great Roc Is Finally Subdued; the Path to the Western Heaven Is Clear",content:"大鹏金翅鸟再度现身，与众人展开最后的正面决战。如来佛祖出场，以无上法力将大鹏收服。至此，西行路上最强大的敌人终于被彻底制服，取经的道路在西天灵山前彻底畅通，一行人踏上了最后的征程。\nThe Great Roc makes a final appearance, confronted and ultimately subdued by the Buddha himself. The most powerful enemy of the entire journey is overcome. The road to Thunderclap Monastery on Spirit Mountain is finally clear, and the pilgrims take their last steps toward the goal."},
{id:91,title:"金平府元夜观灯，玄英洞唐僧供状",english:"The Lantern Festival at Jinping; Tripitaka Is Captured in Xuanying Cave",content:"金平府元宵灯会盛大，唐僧欣然观灯，不料被三头犀牛精趁机劫持，带入玄英洞。悟空四处寻找，请来辟水兽相助，与三头犀牛激战，凭借机智和勇气，最终救出了唐僧，让元宵节的灯光重新亮起。\nTripitaka is captured by three rhinoceros demons during a Lantern Festival celebration. Wukong enlists divine help and fights the three rhinoceroses in a fierce battle. The imagery of festival lights extinguished and restored symbolizes the contrast between delusion's darkness and enlightenment's light."},
{id:92,title:"三僧大战青龙山，四星挟捉犀牛怪",english:"Three Monks Battle on Azure Dragon Mountain; Four Stars Help Capture the Rhinoceros Demons",content:"三头犀牛精控制了当地天气，使当地十年未能举行灯会。悟空请来四位星宿相助，水德、火德等星官联手，在水中将三头犀牛捉获，解除了当地十年黑暗，灯会得以重启，万民同庆。\nThe three rhinoceroses have cancelled the lantern festival for ten years. Wukong summons four celestial stars associated with water and fire; their combined divine powers capture the demons. The festival is restored, lights blazing again — an image of darkness transformed to radiant celebration."},
{id:93,title:"给孤园问古谈因，天竺国朝王遇偶",english:"The Pilgrims Near India; Tripitaka Sees the Buddha's Land in the Distance",content:"师徒四人历经九九八十一难，终于来到天竺国境内。望见远方灵山金光闪耀，唐僧激动落泪，感慨万千，十四年艰辛跋涉，即将修成正果。悟空等人也满怀喜悦，一行人精神振奋，迈开最后的脚步。\nAfter 81 ordeals, the pilgrims enter the territory of India. Tripitaka weeps with joy seeing the golden light of Spirit Mountain in the distance — fourteen years of hardship nearly complete. All four pilgrims feel the electric anticipation of approaching their long-sought goal."},
{id:94,title:"四僧宴乐御花园，一怪空怀情欲天",english:"The Pilgrims Are Entertained; a Final Demon Is Encountered",content:"在抵达灵山前，师徒在天竺国受到盛情款待。此时的众人已历经千辛万苦，修为大进，与最初踏上旅途时相比，判若云泥。即便在此时，仍有妖魔觊觎唐僧，悟空从容应对，将其击退，保住最后的修行成果。\nHosted with magnificent hospitality, the pilgrims reflect on how far they have traveled — in both miles and spirit. Even now a demon covets the holy monk, but Wukong dispatches it effortlessly. The contrast with the desperate early battles marks how completely he has mastered his powers and his mind."},
{id:95,title:"心猿获正果，木母证元身",english:"The Pilgrims' True Natures Are Tested One Final Time",content:"灵山脚下，还有最后一关：凌云渡口，唯有无底船可以渡过。接引佛祖撑一叶无底扁舟前来，唐僧不敢上船，悟空劝他上了船，一具腐烂的尸体顺水漂过，乃是唐僧脱去肉身的象征，真正的涅槃即将到来。\nAt the foot of Spirit Mountain is the final crossing: the Boundless Stream, crossable only by a bottomless boat. The Welcoming Buddha arrives to row. Tripitaka hesitates; Wukong urges him forward. A rotting body floats past — Tripitaka's old mortal self, shed at last. True nirvana is at hand."},
{id:96,title:"寇员外喜待高僧，唐长老不贪财帛",english:"Host Kou Receives the Holy Monk; Tripitaka Refuses Worldly Gifts",content:"一位善人寇洪慷慨接待了取经队伍，赠以丰厚礼物，唐僧分文不取，坚守清贫戒律。然而寇洪不久遭祸，悟空以法力相助，保全了恩人。此段说明布施与报恩并不违背修行，而是修行的一部分。\nThe charitable squire Kou Hong generously hosts the pilgrims and offers rich gifts; Tripitaka refuses all. When Kou Hong subsequently suffers misfortune, Wukong uses his powers to protect their benefactor. The episode suggests that repaying kindness is itself a form of practice, not a departure from it."},
{id:97,title:"金平府被劫，唐三藏诉苦",english:"Final Tests of Faith Before the Scriptures",content:"在灵山跟前，取经人的信念接受最后考验。唐僧历经磨难，信念却比出发时更加坚定。众弟子对唐僧的保护也已超越了职责，成为发自内心的敬爱。四人在人间与天界之间的最后一步，踏出了踏入圣地的门槛。\nStanding at the threshold of Spirit Mountain, the pilgrim's faith is tested one final time. Tripitaka's conviction, having survived every trial, is now unshakeable — not as blind faith but as something forged in experience. The disciples' protection of their master has long since transcended duty; it is love."},
{id:98,title:"猿熟马驯方脱壳，功成行满见真如",english:"The Pilgrims Reach Thunderclap Monastery and Receive the Scriptures",content:"师徒四人终于登上灵山，来到雷音寺，见到如来佛祖。如来宣告四人功德圆满，命阿难、迦叶取出三藏真经，共三十五部，五千零四十八卷，赐给唐僧带回东土普度众生。取经大业功成圆满。\nThe pilgrims ascend Spirit Mountain and reach the Great Thunderclap Monastery, where they bow before the Buddha. The Buddha declares their merit perfect and has the scriptures — 35 collections, 5,048 scrolls — presented to Tripitaka. The great mission is accomplished."},
{id:99,title:"九九数完魔灭尽，三三行满道归根",english:"The 81st Ordeal — the Scriptures Are Almost Lost; the Journey Home",content:"神仙用无字经书欺骗唐僧，唐僧发现后，如来笑说无字经才是真经，但凡人需要有字经以入门，方赐有字经书。返回途中，经历了第八十一难：白鼋不慎将唐僧掉落水中，经卷沾水有所损坏，是为\"缺陷之美\"。\nAnananda and Kasyapa initially give Tripitaka wordless scriptures; the Buddha explains that wordless texts are the highest truth but gives words for those who need them. On the journey back, the 81st ordained trial occurs: the giant turtle tips the pilgrims into a river and the scriptures are slightly damaged — a perfect metaphor for the truth that no earthly transmission of the sacred is ever entirely complete."},
{id:100,title:"径回东土，五圣成真",english:"The Five Pilgrims Are Elevated to Buddhahood; the Journey Ends",content:"唐僧将经书送达长安，唐太宗大喜，珍藏真经，广布天下。如来佛祖宣布，唐僧成佛，号\"旃檀功德佛\"；悟空成佛，号\"斗战胜佛\"；八戒封为净坛使者；沙僧封为金身罗汉；白龙马成为八部天龙。五人各得其所，皆大欢喜。\nThe scriptures are delivered to Emperor Taizong, who treasures them and spreads their teachings. The Buddha announces the rewards: Tripitaka becomes Buddha of Sandalwood Merit; Wukong becomes Victorious Fighting Buddha; Bajie becomes Altar Cleanser; Sandy becomes a Golden-Bodied Arhat; the white horse becomes a divine dragon. All five attain their true natures. The journey is complete."}
],

/* ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
   三国演义 ROMANCE OF THE THREE KINGDOMS (120 chapters)
   ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ */
sanguoyanyi: [
{id:1,title:"宴桃园豪杰三结义，斩黄巾英雄首立功",english:"The Oath of the Peach Garden; Three Heroes First Win Fame Fighting the Yellow Turbans",content:"东汉末年，宦官专权，朝政腐败，张角发动黄巾起义，天下大乱。刘备、关羽、张飞在张飞庄后的桃园中结为异姓兄弟，誓同生死，随即率乡兵从军，镇压黄巾，首立战功。\nIn the dying Han dynasty, the eunuchs hold corrupt power and Zhang Jue's Yellow Turban rebellion plunges the empire into chaos. Liu Bei, Guan Yu, and Zhang Fei swear brotherhood in a peach garden and immediately join the imperial campaign against the Yellow Turbans, winning their first honors in battle."},
{id:2,title:"张翼德怒鞭督邮，何国舅谋诛宦竖",english:"Zhang Fei Thrashes the Inspector; He Jin Plans to Eliminate the Eunuchs",content:"刘备因战功被封为安喜县尉，却遭督邮故意刁难索贿，张飞忍无可忍将督邮痛打一顿，三兄弟弃官出走。洛阳城中，何进与宦官之间的矛盾激化，何进密谋引兵入京诛杀宦官，酿成大祸。\nLiu Bei's meager reward — a county post — is threatened by a corrupt inspector demanding bribes. Zhang Fei beats the inspector and the brothers abandon their posts. In the capital, General He Jin's plot to destroy the eunuchs by inviting warlords to court sets off a catastrophic chain of events."},
{id:3,title:"议温明董卓叱丁原，馈金珠李肃说吕布",english:"Dong Zhuo Dominates the Court; Li Su Bribes Lu Bu to Betray His Master",content:"董卓率兵入京，废少帝，立献帝，独揽大权，横行朝野。丁原之义子吕布武艺绝伦，是董卓的心腹大患。董卓命李肃携赤兔宝马和黄金前去诱说吕布，吕布见利忘义，杀了义父丁原，投入董卓麾下。\nDong Zhuo marches on the capital, deposes the young emperor, and installs a puppet ruler, seizing total power. The mighty warrior Lu Bu, adopted son of Ding Yuan, is the one man who could stop him. Dong Zhuo sends Li Su with the peerless Red Hare horse and gold to bribe Lu Bu; Lu Bu kills his foster father and joins Dong Zhuo."},
{id:4,title:"废汉帝陈留践位，谋董贼孟德献刀",english:"The Emperor Is Deposed; Cao Cao Attempts to Assassinate Dong Zhuo",content:"董卓废汉少帝，另立陈留王为汉献帝，朝中无人敢言。曹操见国家危难，自告奋勇，借宝刀之名前往相国府刺杀董卓。却被董卓察觉，曹操随机应变，谎称献刀，趁机逃脱，踏上了逃亡之路。\nDong Zhuo's deposition of the young emperor meets no resistance at court. Cao Cao, seeing the dynasty threatened, volunteers to assassinate Dong Zhuo, borrowing a famous sword as his pretext. But Dong Zhuo notices something amiss; Cao Cao thinks fast, claims he came to offer the sword as a gift, and escapes."},
{id:5,title:"发矫诏诸镇应曹公，破关兵三英战吕布",english:"Cao Cao Issues a Call to Arms; Three Heroes Battle Lu Bu at Tiger Trap Gate",content:"曹操逃回故乡后发出矫诏，十八路诸侯纷纷响应，结成联军讨伐董卓。吕布于虎牢关前力挫联军，无人可敌。刘备、关羽、张飞三兄弟联手迎战吕布，以三敌一，勉强逼退了\"人中吕布\"。\nCao Cao issues a call to arms from his home territory; eighteen warlords form an alliance to overthrow Dong Zhuo. At Tiger Trap Gate, Lu Bu repels every champion sent against him. Finally Liu Bei, Guan Yu, and Zhang Fei attack together — three against one — and barely manage to force the fearsome Lu Bu to withdraw."},
{id:6,title:"焚金阙董卓行凶，匿玉玺孙坚背约",english:"Dong Zhuo Burns the Capital; Sun Jian Secretly Takes the Imperial Seal",content:"联军进逼洛阳，董卓火烧洛阳，迁都长安，致使洛阳化为废墟，百姓流离失所。孙坚在洛阳废井中发现了传国玉玺，秘密藏匿，却被袁绍知晓。联军内部猜疑丛生，各怀异志，盟约实际上已名存实亡。\nAs the alliance advances, Dong Zhuo burns Luoyang to the ground and moves the capital west. Sun Jian discovers the Imperial Seal in a ruined palace well and secretly keeps it — a fateful act of ambition. The alliance, already fractured by mutual suspicion, effectively dissolves."},
{id:7,title:"袁绍磐河战公孙，孙坚跨江击刘表",english:"Yuan Shao Fights Gongsun Zan at the Pan River; Sun Jian Crosses the River to Attack Liu Biao",content:"袁绍与公孙瓒因地盘争夺引发大战，界桥之战，两军精锐相搏，各有胜负。孙坚率军渡江攻打荆州刘表，战事正酣之际，孙坚遭黄祖伏兵暗箭射死，江东势力遭受重大打击，孙策承父业南征北战。\nYuan Shao and Gongsun Zan go to war over territory in the north, fighting at the Pan River Bridge. In the south, Sun Jian crosses the Yangtze to attack Liu Biao of Jing Province — but rides into an ambush and is killed by a stray arrow from Huang Zu. Sun Ce inherits his father's cause at a young age."},
{id:8,title:"王司徒巧使连环计，董太师大闹凤仪亭",english:"Wang Yun's Clever Chain Strategy; Dong Zhuo's Rage at Phoenix Pavilion",content:"司徒王允深感国家危亡，精心设计\"连环计\"：将貂蝉许给吕布，又献给董卓，让两人因争夺貂蝉而反目。吕布与貂蝉在凤仪亭幽会，被董卓发现，董卓暴怒，掷戟刺吕布，二人裂隙已成。\nMinister Wang Yun devises the Chain Strategy: he betroths his beautiful ward Diaochan to Lu Bu, then gives her to Dong Zhuo, inflaming jealousy between the two. Lu Bu and Diaochan meet secretly at Phoenix Pavilion; Dong Zhuo discovers them and hurls a halberd at Lu Bu in fury. The rift between tyrant and warrior is complete."},
{id:9,title:"除暴凶吕布助司徒，犯长安李傕听贾诩",english:"Lu Bu Kills Dong Zhuo; Li Jue Attacks Chang'an on Jia Xu's Advice",content:"吕布受王允策动，趁董卓入宫之机将其刺杀，朝野称快。然而董卓余部李傕、郭汜在贾诩建议下，率军攻打长安，城破之后大肆烧杀，王允被杀，吕布败逃，汉室再度陷入战乱之中。\nLu Bu assassinates Dong Zhuo at the palace gate; the empire rejoices. But Dong Zhuo's lieutenants Li Jue and Guo Si, following Jia Xu's cold-blooded advice, march on Chang'an. The city falls; Wang Yun is killed, Lu Bu flees, and the Han dynasty descends into renewed chaos."},
{id:10,title:"勤王室马腾举义，报父仇曹操兴师",english:"Ma Teng Raises a Righteous Army; Cao Cao Campaigns to Avenge His Father",content:"曹操父亲曹嵩在徐州遭陶谦部将所杀，曹操悲愤交加，以报父仇为名大举攻伐徐州，所过之处杀戮无数，屠城之恶令百姓不寒而栗。与此同时，马腾、韩遂在西北举兵，奉天子之名讨伐李傕郭汜。\nCao Cao's father is killed in Xuzhou on a journey; Cao Cao launches a massive punitive campaign against Xuzhou, massacring civilians en masse. The brutality of the campaign stands in sharp contrast to his self-proclaimed loyalty to the Han. In the northwest, Ma Teng raises troops against the warlords in the capital."},
{id:11,title:"刘皇叔北海救孔融，吕温侯濮阳破曹操",english:"Liu Bei Rescues Kong Rong at Beihai; Lu Bu Defeats Cao Cao at Puyang",content:"孔融被黄巾余党围攻北海，求援于刘备，刘备慷慨赴援，解了北海之围，义名大震。曹操攻打吕布，于濮阳中计，几乎被吕布活捉，幸得众将拼死护送才得以脱险，曹军损失惨重。\nKong Rong, besieged at Beihai by Yellow Turban remnants, appeals to Liu Bei. Liu Bei rushes to the rescue, relieving the siege and winning great renown. Meanwhile Cao Cao attacks Lu Bu at Puyang and falls into an ambush — nearly captured, he escapes only through his generals' desperate fighting."},
{id:12,title:"陶恭祖三让徐州，曹孟德大战吕布",english:"Tao Qian Thrice Offers Xuzhou to Liu Bei; Cao Cao's Great Battle with Lu Bu",content:"徐州牧陶谦病重，三次将徐州让给刘备，刘备两次推辞，第三次终于接手，成为徐州之主，势力大增。曹操再度征讨吕布，双方大战于兖州，吕布武勇无敌，战事旷日持久，互有胜负。\nThe dying governor of Xuzhou, Tao Qian, thrice offers his territory to Liu Bei. Liu Bei declines twice before accepting, gaining a major power base. Cao Cao continues his campaign against Lu Bu in Yanzhou — a prolonged struggle that demonstrates both men's resilience."},
{id:13,title:"李傕郭汜大交兵，杨奉董承双救驾",english:"Li Jue and Guo Si Fight Each Other; Yang Feng and Dong Cheng Rescue the Emperor",content:"李傕、郭汜为争夺权力相互攻伐，连皇帝都成为争夺的筹码。汉献帝在杨奉、董承等忠臣护送下逃离长安，辗转流离，路途艰辛，多次险些落入军阀之手，皇室威严已荡然无存。\nLi Jue and Guo Si turn on each other in a power struggle, with the emperor caught between them as a pawn. Loyal ministers Yang Feng and Dong Cheng escort the Emperor in a desperate flight from Chang'an. The Son of Heaven wanders homeless like a refugee — the Han dynasty's humiliation is complete."},
{id:14,title:"曹孟德移驾幸许都，吕奉先乘夜袭徐郡",english:"Cao Cao Moves the Emperor to Xu; Lu Bu Seizes Xuzhou by Night",content:"曹操迎接汉献帝移驾许都，从此\"挟天子以令诸侯\"，以汉室名义号令天下，政治上占据极大优势。吕布趁刘备出兵救援之际，夜袭下邳，占领了徐州，刘备陷入无处立足的困境之中。\nCao Cao welcomes the emperor to Xu, using imperial authority to issue orders to all lords — his greatest political coup. Meanwhile Lu Bu seizes Xuzhou while Liu Bei is away fighting, leaving Liu Bei without a home base and at Lu Bu's mercy."},
{id:15,title:"太史慈酣斗小霸王，孙伯符大战严白虎",english:"Taishi Ci's Battle with the Little Conqueror; Sun Ce Defeats Yan Baihu",content:"孙策绰号\"小霸王\"，以勇猛著称，率兵横扫江东，所向披靡。太史慈与孙策大战，势均力敌，后来太史慈被擒，被孙策以诚相待，最终归顺孙策。孙策平定江东，奠定了江东基业。\nSun Ce, the 'Little Conqueror,' sweeps through the Jiangnan region with irresistible force. He and the warrior Taishi Ci fight to a draw; when Taishi Ci is captured, Sun Ce treats him so honorably that he switches allegiance. Sun Ce consolidates the Jiangnan region, laying the foundation of Eastern Wu."},
{id:16,title:"吕奉先射戟辕门，曹孟德败师淯水",english:"Lu Bu Shoots the Halberd at the Gate; Cao Cao's Defeat at Yu River",content:"刘备与纪灵交战，请吕布居中调解。吕布在辕门以弓射戟，戟中小枝，以此为停战条件，众人大服其神射之术。此后曹操征讨张绣，张绣降而复叛，曹操在淯水大败，折损爱将典韦，长子曹昂，侄子曹安民，损失惨重。\nLu Bu demonstrates his legendary archery by shooting a small branch on a halberd from a hundred paces — if he hits it, the armies stand down. He hits it perfectly and both sides accept the truce. Later, Cao Cao suffers a disastrous defeat at Yu River when Zhang Xiu revolts, killing Cao Cao's beloved general Dian Wei and his own son."},
{id:17,title:"袁公路大起七军，曹孟德会合三将",english:"Yuan Shu Raises Seven Armies; Cao Cao's Coalition Against Him",content:"袁术僭越称帝，天下共讨之。曹操联合吕布、刘备、孙策等诸侯共同出兵，数路大军对袁术形成合围之势。袁术兵败如山倒，所有盟友纷纷倒戈，袁术势力迅速瓦解，最终含恨而死。\nYuan Shu's audacious proclamation of himself as emperor turns every warlord against him. Cao Cao coordinates a multi-front campaign; Lu Bu, Liu Bei, and Sun Ce all attack simultaneously. Yuan Shu's power collapses entirely; he dies in despair, vomiting blood — a stark lesson about the limits of ambition."},
{id:18,title:"贾文和料敌决胜，夏侯惇拔矢啖睛",english:"Jia Xu's Brilliant Strategy Wins the Day; Xiahou Dun Pulls the Arrow from His Eye and Eats It",content:"曹操与吕布作战，谋士贾诩献计，曹操依计而行，取得大捷。夏侯惇在作战中被流矢射中左眼，夏侯惇拔出箭矢，发现眼珠挂在箭头上，随即将其放入口中吞下，高呼\"父精母血，不可弃也\"，毫不退缩，继续冲锋。\nJia Xu's strategy wins a crucial victory for Cao Cao. In combat, Xiahou Dun is struck in the eye by an arrow. He pulls it out, notices his eyeball dangling from the shaft, and — crying 'This eye came from my parents; I cannot throw it away!' — eats it, then charges back into battle. The story becomes legendary."},
{id:19,title:"下邳城曹操鏖兵，白门楼吕布殒命",english:"Cao Cao Besieges Xiaopei; Lu Bu Is Executed at White Gate Tower",content:"曹操水淹下邳，吕布困守孤城，其手下侯成、宋宪、魏续叛变，将吕布绑缚投降。白门楼上，吕布求刘备说情，刘备反提吕布认父认兄之事，致使曹操下令将吕布绞死。一代猛将就此终结。\nCao Cao floods Xiaopei into submission. Lu Bu's own officers betray and bind him. At White Gate Tower Lu Bu asks Liu Bei to intercede for his life; Liu Bei instead reminds Cao Cao of how Lu Bu has twice betrayed his own fathers — Cao Cao orders Lu Bu strangled. The mightiest warrior of the age is gone."},
{id:20,title:"曹阿瞒许田打围，董国舅内阁受诏",english:"Cao Cao's Arrogant Hunt at Xutian; Dong Cheng Receives a Secret Imperial Edict",content:"曹操在许田围猎，皇帝射中猎物，众人呼声\"万岁\"，曹操却骑马挡在皇帝前面，代为受礼，傲慢无礼令众臣愤慨。献帝密书衣带诏，将曹操的跋扈告知董承，命其诛杀曹操，密谋开始。\nAt a royal hunt, Cao Cao positions himself to receive the crowd's cheers meant for the Emperor — a stunning act of arrogance that shocks even hardened observers. The humiliated Emperor secretly writes an edict in blood hidden in his belt, ordering Dong Cheng to kill Cao Cao. The conspiracy is launched."},
{id:21,title:"曹操煮酒论英雄，关公赚城斩车胄",english:"Cao Cao Discusses Heroes over Heated Wine; Guan Yu Captures the City and Kills Che Zhou",content:"曹操邀刘备饮酒，以\"天下英雄惟使君与操耳\"试探刘备之志，刘备以雷声作为掩饰，瞒过了曹操。关羽奉命斩杀了不服刘备的徐州将领车胄，刘备趁机占据了小沛，开始独立发展自己的势力。\nCao Cao toasts Liu Bei and declares that only the two of them qualify as true heroes. Liu Bei uses a clap of thunder to disguise his startled reaction — deceiving Cao Cao about his ambitions. Meanwhile Guan Yu kills the defiant Che Zhou and Liu Bei reestablishes himself in Xiaopei, resuming independent action."},
{id:22,title:"袁曹各起马步三军，关张共擒王刘二将",english:"Yuan Shao and Cao Cao Both Raise Armies; Guan Yu and Zhang Fei Each Capture a General",content:"袁绍与曹操决裂，双方大规模备战。陈琳为袁绍撰写讨曹檄文，历数曹操罪行，文采飞扬，连曹操患头风读此文后头痛也止了。关羽与张飞各自在战场上展示英勇，各生擒一员对方大将。\nYuan Shao and Cao Cao formally break. The brilliant writer Chen Lin composes a denunciation of Cao Cao so powerful that reading it reportedly cures Cao Cao's chronic headaches. On the battlefield, both Guan Yu and Zhang Fei demonstrate their extraordinary valor by each capturing an enemy general single-handed."},
{id:23,title:"祢正平裸衣骂贼，吉太医下毒遭刑",english:"Mi Heng's Naked Tirade Against Cao Cao; the Doctor Attempts to Poison Cao Cao",content:"狂士祢衡拒绝服从曹操，在大庭广众之下脱衣骂曹，即便曹操也无可奈何，将他送给刘表，最终祢衡被黄祖所杀。医官吉平参与衣带诏密谋，在药中下毒图谋刺杀曹操，事泄被捕，受尽酷刑，仍宁死不屈。\nThe eccentric scholar Mi Heng strips naked and insults Cao Cao to his face during an imperial ceremony — and survives because killing him would look worse. He is eventually killed by another warlord. Doctor Ji Ping, part of the imperial assassination plot, poisons Cao Cao's medicine; the plot is discovered, and Ji Ping endures torture rather than betray his confederates."},
{id:24,title:"国贼行凶杀贵妃，皇叔败走投袁绍",english:"Cao Cao Murders the Imperial Consort; Liu Bei Flees to Yuan Shao",content:"衣带诏事泄，董承等人被诛，曹操强迫汉献帝处死了与诏书相关的贵妃。刘备闻变出走，投奔袁绍，暂时依附于北方最强的割据力量。汉室之忠义之士在曹操的铁腕之下，死的死，逃的逃。\nThe secret edict is discovered; Dong Cheng and his conspirators are killed. Cao Cao forces the Emperor to execute the implicated Consort Fu. Liu Bei escapes and takes refuge with Yuan Shao — the most powerful warlord in the north. Loyal Han subjects are being systematically eliminated."},
{id:25,title:"屯土山关公约三事，救白马曹操解重围",english:"Guan Yu's Three Conditions at Earth Mountain; He Rescues Cao Cao at White Horse",content:"曹操攻打刘备，刘备败走，关羽被困土山，程昱用计劝降关羽。关羽提出三个条件方才投降，曹操全部答应。关羽归降曹操后，在白马之战中斩杀颜良，立下大功，但心念刘备，无时不刻不想回归。\nCao Cao besieges and separates Guan Yu, who agrees to surrender only under three conditions: loyalty to the Han house, no harm to Liu Bei's family, and leave to rejoin Liu Bei once his whereabouts are known. Cao Cao agrees to all three. Guan Yu serves brilliantly, killing the enemy champion Yan Liang at White Horse."},
{id:26,title:"袁本初败兵折将，关云长挂印封金",english:"Yuan Shao's Generals Are Killed; Guan Yu Hangs Up His Seal and Returns All the Gold",content:"关羽在解白马之围时斩颜良，袁绍军大震。此后关羽又斩文丑，曹操对关羽厚加赏赐，封侯赐金。然而关羽得知刘备在袁绍处后，挂印封金，将曹操所赐全部归还，带着刘备的两位夫人过五关斩六将，寻访刘备。\nGuan Yu kills both Yan Liang and Wen Chou — Yuan Shao's two greatest champions. Cao Cao showers Guan Yu with honors. But when Guan Yu learns Liu Bei is with Yuan Shao, he returns every gift, hangs up his official seal, and departs — fighting through five passes and killing six generals to rejoin his sworn brother."},
{id:27,title:"美髯公千里走单骑，汉寿侯五关斩六将",english:"The Beautiful Beard Rides a Thousand Li; Guan Yu Fights Through Five Passes",content:"关羽带着甘夫人、糜夫人，一路披荆斩棘，过东岭关斩孔秀，过洛阳斩韩福孟坦，过汜水关斩卞喜，过荥阳斩王植，过滑州斩秦琦，最终来到黄河渡口，与张辽相遇，被允许通过，终于和刘备相聚。\nGuan Yu escorts Liu Bei's ladies through five gates and past six officers who try to stop him — killing them all in single combat. At the Yellow River, his old friend Zhang Liao lets him pass. The episode of 'thousand-li solo ride' becomes the defining image of Guan Yu's absolute loyalty."},
{id:28,title:"斩蔡阳兄弟释疑，会古城主臣聚义",english:"Guan Yu Kills Cai Yang to Resolve Doubts; the Brothers Reunite at Guchangcheng",content:"关羽与刘备在古城相逢，其间张飞一度怀疑关羽背叛，关羽当着张飞的面斩杀了前来追赶的蔡阳，以此证明自己的忠心。三兄弟重聚古城，赵云也来相投，刘备势力重新聚集，感天动地。\nGuan Yu reunites with Liu Bei and Zhang Fei at Guchangcheng. Zhang Fei doubts Guan Yu's loyalty until Guan Yu kills the pursuing Cai Yang in a duel in full view, proving his devotion beyond doubt. Zhao Yun also joins them. The three brothers are reunited; their bond is unbroken despite everything."},
{id:29,title:"小霸王怒斩于吉，碧眼儿坐领江东",english:"The Little Conqueror Executes the Taoist Yu Ji; Sun Quan Takes Over Jiangdong",content:"孙策在平定江东后不久，因杀死道士于吉而遭鬼魂作祟，旧伤复发，二十六岁英年早逝。孙策临终将江东大权交给弟弟孙权，嘱咐他要善用人才，稳固基业。孙权从此开始经营江东，三国鼎立格局开始成形。\nSun Ce, having conquered Jiangnan, is haunted by the ghost of the Daoist master he executed, and his old wounds reopen. He dies at 26, entrusting Jiangdong to his younger brother Sun Quan. Sun Quan — blue-eyed, broad-faced — begins his long, shrewd rule. The three-kingdom pattern begins to take shape."},
{id:30,title:"战官渡本初败绩，劫乌巢孟德烧粮",english:"The Battle of Guandu — Yuan Shao Is Defeated; Cao Cao Burns the Grain at Wuchao",content:"官渡之战，袁绍以十万大军对抗曹操的数万兵马，看似必胜。谋士许攸投降曹操后，献计奔袭乌巢粮草重地。曹操亲率精兵夜袭乌巢，火烧袁绍粮草，一举扭转战局，袁绍大军溃败，此为三国前期决定性战役。\nAt the Battle of Guandu, Yuan Shao's overwhelming numerical advantage seems decisive. But the defecting strategist Xu You reveals the location of Yuan Shao's unguarded grain depot at Wuchao. Cao Cao leads a night raid and burns it all. Yuan Shao's massive army collapses without food. This is the battle that determines the north."},
{id:31,title:"曹操仓亭破本初，玄德荆州依刘表",english:"Cao Cao Defeats Yuan Shao at Cangtingdu; Liu Bei Takes Refuge with Liu Biao",content:"官渡之战后，袁绍一蹶不振，曹操乘胜追击，仓亭之战再胜，袁绍忧愤吐血而死。曹操势力达到顶峰，一统北方指日可待。刘备在北方立足艰难，投奔荆州刘表，得到收容，开始了依附荆州的岁月。\nAfter Guandu, Yuan Shao never recovers. Cao Cao defeats him again at Cangtingdu; Yuan Shao dies vomiting blood in defeat. Cao Cao's dominance of the north is now inevitable. Liu Bei, unable to find footing in the north, takes refuge with Liu Biao of Jing Province."},
{id:32,title:"夺冀州袁尚争锋，决漳河许攸献计",english:"The Yuan Sons Fight Over Ji Province; Xu You's Strategy at the Zhang River",content:"袁绍死后，三个儿子袁谭、袁熙、袁尚相互争斗，内耗严重。曹操趁机各个击破，袁谭被杀，袁熙、袁尚投奔乌桓。曹操平定冀州，将大量人才和物资收入囊中，北方统一进程大大加快。\nAfter Yuan Shao's death, his three sons — Yuan Tan, Yuan Xi, and Yuan Shang — fight each other for inheritance. Cao Cao exploits the division to destroy them one by one. Yuan Tan is killed; the other two flee north to the Wuhuan tribes. Cao Cao pacifies Ji Province and accelerates unification of the north."},
{id:33,title:"曹丕乘乱纳甄氏，郭嘉遗计定辽东",english:"Cao Pi Takes Zhen Shi in the Chaos; Guo Jia's Posthumous Strategy Pacifies Liaodong",content:"曹操北征乌桓，军师郭嘉随行，途中病逝，临终留下密计。曹操按郭嘉遗计行事，以静制动，等待公孙康自行杀死袁氏兄弟，不战而得辽东。郭嘉一生为曹操运筹帷幄，是曹操最心爱的谋士。\nCampaigning against the Wuhuan in the far north, Cao Cao's brilliant advisor Guo Jia falls ill and dies. His final written strategy advises waiting rather than attacking Liaodong — Public Sun Kang will kill the Yuan brothers himself. Cao Cao follows the advice; it works perfectly. Guo Jia was Cao Cao's most beloved and trusted strategist."},
{id:34,title:"蔡夫人隔屏听密语，刘皇叔跃马过檀溪",english:"Lady Cai Eavesdrops on Liu Bei's Secret Plans; Liu Bei's Horse Leaps the Tanxi Stream",content:"刘备在荆州蛰居，内心焦虑。蔡夫人偷听到刘备与韩嵩的密谈，密告蔡瑁图谋加害刘备。刘备骑马出逃，被蔡瑁率兵追至檀溪，绝境之中，刘备催马纵跳，坐骑的卢飞跃过了宽阔的溪流，绝处逢生。\nLiu Bei's secret conversations are overheard by Lady Cai, who alerts the militarist Cai Mao to eliminate Liu Bei. Chased to the edge of the Tanxi Stream with no crossing, Liu Bei urges his horse forward; the animal 'Di Lu' makes a miraculous leap across the wide stream. The horse had been said to bring misfortune to its owner — instead it saves his life."},
{id:35,title:"玄德南漳逢隐沦，单福新野遇英主",english:"Liu Bei Meets the Hermit Sima Wei in Nanzhang; the Strategist Xu Shu Meets His True Lord",content:"刘备在南漳偶遇隐士水镜先生司马徽，水镜先生称赞刘备得了\"伏龙凤雏\"之一必能得天下。单福，即徐庶，以才干辅助刘备，在新野数战皆捷，曹操久攻不下，曹操以徐庶母亲为要挟，迫使徐庶离去。\nLiu Bei encounters the wise hermit Sima Wei in the mountains, who tells him that if he could obtain either of two geniuses — 'Sleeping Dragon' or 'Young Phoenix' — he could conquer the empire. The strategist Xu Shu enters Liu Bei's service and wins brilliant victories at Xinye — until Cao Cao forces his departure by holding his mother hostage."},
{id:36,title:"玄德用计袭樊城，元直走马荐诸葛",english:"Liu Bei Captures Fancheng by Strategy; Xu Shu Recommends Zhuge Liang",content:"徐庶在离去前向刘备推荐了诸葛孔明，称其才智冠绝天下，号\"卧龙\"，请刘备务必亲自往隆中拜访。徐庶虽归曹操，但终身不为曹操献一计以报曹操威逼之仇，史称\"徐庶进曹营，一言不发\"。\nBefore leaving, Xu Shu tells Liu Bei about Zhuge Liang — 'Sleeping Dragon' — calling him the greatest talent under heaven and urging Liu Bei to visit him personally at Longzhong. Xu Shu himself, though forced to serve Cao Cao, refuses to offer Cao Cao a single piece of advice for the rest of his life — his silent act of loyalty."},
{id:37,title:"司马徽再荐名士，刘玄德三顾草庐",english:"Sima Wei Again Recommends the Great Man; Liu Bei Makes Three Visits to the Thatched Cottage",content:"刘备携关羽、张飞二度拜访隆中，均未见到诸葛亮。第三次拜访时，刘备独自恭候，待诸葛亮午睡醒来，以\"三顾茅庐\"之诚打动了这位天下奇才。诸葛亮为刘备分析天下大势，提出了著名的\"隆中对\"战略。\nLiu Bei, Guan Yu, and Zhang Fei make two trips to Longzhong without finding Zhuge Liang home. On the third trip, Liu Bei waits humbly while Zhuge Liang finishes his nap — his sincerity winning the brilliant strategist's loyalty. Zhuge Liang then delivers the 'Longzhong Plan': a comprehensive strategic vision for how Liu Bei can conquer the empire."},
{id:38,title:"定三分隆中决策，战长江孙氏报仇",english:"The Three Kingdoms Strategy Is Decided at Longzhong; Sun Quan Seeks Revenge",content:"诸葛亮提出的\"隆中对\"战略：占荆州，取益州，联孙吴，抗曹操，待时机北伐中原，兴复汉室。刘备大为叹服，力邀诸葛亮出山相助。孙权为父报仇，攻打黄祖，终于在此战中斩杀仇人，但甘宁也归顺了孙权。\nZhuge Liang's Longzhong Plan outlines a three-part strategy: hold Jing Province, take Yi Province, ally with Sun Quan against Cao Cao, then advance on the central plain. Liu Bei is electrified and begs Zhuge Liang to become his advisor. Sun Quan, meanwhile, finally takes revenge on Huang Zu for his father's death."},
{id:39,title:"荆州城公子三求计，博望坡军师初用兵",english:"The Prince of Jing Province Seeks Strategies; Zhuge Liang's First Military Campaign at Bowangpo",content:"诸葛亮初出茅庐，第一仗便在博望坡以火攻之计大败曹操先锋夏侯惇，令众人对这位年轻谋士刮目相看。关羽、张飞起先轻视诸葛亮，经此一战，才真正折服于其神机妙算之才。\nZhuge Liang's first battle: using fire and careful planning at Bowangpo, he destroys the vanguard of Cao Cao's advance force under Xiahou Dun. Guan Yu and Zhang Fei had been skeptical of this young civilian advisor; after Bowangpo they are convinced. Zhuge Liang's genius is no longer theoretical."},
{id:40,title:"蔡夫人议献荆州，诸葛亮火烧新野",english:"Lady Cai Plans to Surrender Jing Province; Zhuge Liang Burns New Ye",content:"曹操大军南下，荆州刘表病逝，蔡夫人与蔡瑁拥立幼子刘琮继位并献荆州于曹操。刘备仓皇出走，诸葛亮在新野城中设下火攻，大败曹军先锋，此后刘备携十万百姓南逃，显示了刘备爱民如子之心。\nCao Cao marches south; Liu Biao dies and Lady Cai engineers the surrender of Jing Province to Cao Cao. Liu Bei flees with the population — more than 100,000 civilians who refuse to live under Cao Cao join him voluntarily. This is Liu Bei's defining moment: he slows his escape to protect his people, nearly at the cost of his life."},
{id:41,title:"刘玄德携民渡江，赵子龙单骑救主",english:"Liu Bei Crosses the River with His People; Zhao Yun's Single-Horseman Rescue of the Young Lord",content:"当阳长坂坡，曹操铁骑追上刘备，众人仓皇逃散。赵云发现刘备之子阿斗（刘禅）和甘夫人失散，单骑杀回重围，怀抱婴儿阿斗，在数万曹军中七进七出，终于将主公骨肉安然救出，此为三国最著名的英雄事迹之一。\nAt Changban Slope, Cao Cao's cavalry catches Liu Bei's refugees. Zhao Yun discovers that Liu Bei's infant son and Lady Gan have been separated in the chaos. He turns back alone into the Cao army, fighting through thousands of soldiers carrying the baby, making seven charges in and out of the enemy formation to rescue the child."},
{id:42,title:"张翼德大闹长坂桥，刘豫州败走汉津口",english:"Zhang Fei's Defiant Stand at Changban Bridge; Liu Bei's Desperate Escape at Hanjin Ford",content:"赵云杀回后，张飞只率二十余骑守长坂桥，立马桥头，横矛大喝：\"燕人张飞在此，谁敢来决一死战！\"声若雷霆，曹操大军竟不敢上前，张飞之威震天下。刘备得以继续撤退，渡过汉水。\nWhile Zhao Yun is cutting his way back, Zhang Fei holds Changban Bridge with only 20 horsemen. Standing in his stirrups he roars a challenge that echoes like thunder — Cao Cao's entire army hesitates, then falls back. Zhang Fei's bluff buys the time Liu Bei needs to cross the Han River."},
{id:43,title:"诸葛亮舌战群儒，鲁子敬力排众议",english:"Zhuge Liang's Debate with the Eastern Wu Scholars; Lu Su's Support for Alliance",content:"曹操南下，东吴面临抉择，主降派和主战派争执不下。诸葛亮出使东吴，凭借三寸不烂之舌，在孙权朝堂上力排众议，驳斥了张昭等主降派大臣，终于说服孙权与刘备联合抗曹。\nWith Cao Cao's vast army approaching, Eastern Wu's ministers are split between surrender and resistance. Zhuge Liang arrives as an envoy and engages the pro-surrender scholars in a brilliant verbal debate, demolishing their arguments one by one. He persuades Sun Quan to ally with Liu Bei against Cao Cao — one of history's great examples of diplomatic eloquence."},
{id:44,title:"孔明用智激周瑜，孙权决计破曹操",english:"Zhuge Liang Provokes Zhou Yu's Ambition; Sun Quan Resolves to Fight Cao Cao",content:"周瑜虽主战，却对刘备存有戒心。诸葛亮以曹操赋诗中\"揽二乔于东南兮\"激怒周瑜，同时劝说孙权下定决心抗曹。孙权以宝剑斩断案角，宣誓抗曹，吴蜀联盟正式形成，赤壁大战的序幕就此拉开。\nZhou Yu, the brilliant young Wu commander, favors war but distrusts Liu Bei. Zhuge Liang cleverly provokes Zhou Yu by quoting lines from Cao Cao's poetry that seem to covet Wu's most beautiful women. Sun Quan draws his sword and cuts the corner off his desk to show his irreversible commitment to war."},
{id:45,title:"三江口曹操折兵，群英会蒋干中计",english:"Cao Cao Suffers Defeat at Three Rivers; Jiang Gan Falls into Zhou Yu's Trap",content:"曹操北兵不耐水战，周瑜初战得胜。曹操派蒋干前往东吴游说周瑜，周瑜将计就计，设下\"群英会\"，在席间安排了一封伪造的降曹书信，让蒋干偷看，使曹操误杀了精通水战的蔡瑁、张允二将，自毁长城。\nCao Cao's northern troops are unaccustomed to naval warfare; Zhou Yu wins an initial engagement. Cao Cao sends Jiang Gan to subvert Zhou Yu; Zhou Yu sees through the mission immediately and plants a fake letter for Jiang Gan to steal — which leads Cao Cao to execute his two best naval commanders, Cai Mao and Zhang Yun."},
{id:46,title:"用奇谋孔明借箭，献密计黄盖受刑",english:"Zhuge Liang Borrows Arrows Through Clever Strategy; Huang Gai's Stratagem of Suffering the Beating",content:"周瑜命诸葛亮在十天内造十万支箭，欲借此加害。诸葛亮只用三天，趁大雾在草船上插满稻草，驶近曹营，曹军万箭齐发，稻草人全插满了箭，如数凑齐。黄盖提出苦肉计，让周瑜鞭打自己以取信于曹操，准备火攻。\nZhou Yu orders Zhuge Liang to produce 100,000 arrows in ten days — intending for him to fail and be executed. Zhuge Liang uses fog and boats bristling with straw to 'borrow' the arrows from Cao Cao's own army. Meanwhile Huang Gai undergoes a real beating in a 'bitter flesh' stratagem to convince Cao Cao he wants to defect."},
{id:47,title:"阚泽密献诈降书，庞统巧授连环计",english:"Kan Ze Delivers the False Surrender Letter; Pang Tong Devises the Chain-Linking Strategy",content:"阚泽冒险赴曹营，呈上黄盖的诈降书，凭借机智应答骗过了曹操。庞统，即\"凤雏\"，主动投奔曹营，以北兵不耐水战为由，建议曹操将战舰用铁链连在一起，曹操中计，将数百艘战舰连锁成片，为火攻创造了绝佳条件。\nKan Ze braves Cao Cao's camp to deliver Huang Gai's surrender letter, convincing Cao Cao through quick-witted answers under questioning. Pang Tong — 'Young Phoenix' — then visits Cao Cao and recommends chaining his warships together to reduce seasickness. Cao Cao takes the advice, unknowingly creating a perfect target for a fire attack."},
{id:48,title:"宴长江曹操赋诗，锁战船北军用武",english:"Cao Cao Composes Poetry on the Great River; the Chained Warships Are Prepared",content:"曹操在大江上设宴，意气风发，赋《短歌行》表达统一天下的豪情，横槊赋诗，一代枭雄的风采尽现。然而此时，火攻之计已经布置妥当，周瑜只等东南风起，便要以万火之势扫灭曹军。\nCao Cao hosts a grand banquet on the Great River, composing his famous poem 'Though short our lives' with his spear in hand, expressing his ambition to unite the empire. The scene captures a great man at his most magnificent — unaware that his beautiful chained fleet is a deathtrap, awaiting only the southeast wind."},
{id:49,title:"七星坛诸葛祭风，三江口周瑜纵火",english:"Zhuge Liang Summons the Southeast Wind at the Seven-Star Altar; Zhou Yu Launches the Fire Attack",content:"赤壁之战，东南风是关键。诸葛亮建七星坛，装作祭风，实际是利用气象知识预判了东南风的到来。东南风起，黄盖率火船冲向曹军水寨，万箭齐发，火烧赤壁，曹操八十三万大军顷刻化为灰烬，赤壁之战奠定了三国鼎立的基础。\nAt the Battle of Red Cliffs, the southeast wind is critical. Zhuge Liang builds an altar and performs rituals — actually using his knowledge of meteorology to predict the wind's arrival. When it comes, Huang Gai's fire ships smash into Cao Cao's chained fleet. The resulting inferno destroys Cao Cao's army. Three Kingdoms era begins."},
{id:50,title:"诸葛亮智算华容，关云长义释曹操",english:"Zhuge Liang Strategically Deploys Troops at Huarong Road; Guan Yu Releases Cao Cao out of Old Obligation",content:"曹操大败，在华容道走投无路，遭遇了关羽的拦截。曹操以昔日恩情和人情相求，关羽念及曹操过去的厚待，放了曹操，事后甘愿受军令状的惩罚。诸葛亮早已料定关羽会放走曹操，此举乃不欲曹操死于此时。\nDefeated and fleeing, Cao Cao's path is blocked by Guan Yu at Huarong Road. Cao Cao appeals to Guan Yu's sense of honor and their past relationship. Guan Yu, remembering Cao Cao's generosity, lets him pass — fully aware he will face punishment and offering his own head if challenged. Zhuge Liang had foreseen it, and allowed it."},
{id:51,title:"曹仁大战东吴兵，孔明一气周公瑾",english:"Cao Ren Battles Eastern Wu; Zhuge Liang Infuriates Zhou Yu for the First Time",content:"赤壁之战后，刘备趁势夺取了荆州众多郡县，周瑜负责攻取的南郡却还未拿下。诸葛亮趁周瑜与曹仁激战之际，暗中夺取了城池，令周瑜气愤不已。这是诸葛亮三气周瑜的第一气，两人的明争暗斗就此开始。\nAfter Red Cliffs, Liu Bei cleverly seizes Jing Province's districts while Zhou Yu and Cao Ren are fighting. When Zhou Yu finally conquers Nanjun, Zhuge Liang has already occupied it. Zhou Yu is furious. This is the first of three times Zhuge Liang infuriates Zhou Yu — the rivalry between the two geniuses begins in earnest."},
{id:52,title:"诸葛亮智取桂阳，赵子龙计取桂阳",english:"Zhuge Liang Takes Guiyang; Zhao Yun's Honorable Refusal",content:"刘备派赵云去取桂阳，桂阳太守赵范不战而降，欲将守寡的嫂嫂许配给赵云。赵云以'兄弟之妻不可娶'为由严词拒绝，展现了其高尚的品格。赵云不仅武艺高强，更是一位品德高尚、廉洁自守的大将。\nLiu Bei sends Zhao Yun to take Guiyang. The governor surrenders without a fight and offers his widowed sister-in-law in marriage to Zhao Yun. Zhao Yun firmly refuses: 'One does not marry one's brother's widow.' The episode shows that Zhao Yun's extraordinary character matches his extraordinary courage."},
{id:53,title:"关云长义释黄汉升，孙仲谋大战张文远",english:"Guan Yu Nobly Releases Huang Zhong; Sun Quan Fights Zhang Liao",content:"关羽与老将黄忠交战，黄忠马失前蹄，关羽不乘人之危，放黄忠离去。次日黄忠滴水不漏了关羽的面子，以好箭射中关羽盔缨，以此回报。两人互相欣赏对方的气节，此段充满了英雄相惜的情谊。\nGuan Yu and the veteran general Huang Zhong fight an inconclusive duel. When Huang Zhong's horse stumbles, Guan Yu refuses to strike a fallen enemy and lets him go. Next day Huang Zhong repays the courtesy by shooting Guan Yu's helmet plume with his best arrow rather than killing him. The episode is a meditation on the honor of warriors."},
{id:54,title:"吴国太佛寺看新郎，刘皇叔洞房续佳偶",english:"Lady Wu Inspects the Bridegroom at the Temple; Liu Bei's Wedding Night in the Bridal Chamber",content:"周瑜设美人计，以孙权之妹孙尚香为诱饵，欲骗刘备入东吴，趁机扣押以夺回荆州。然而孙权之母吴国太真心喜欢刘备，弄假成真，刘备真的娶了孙尚香，平白得了一位美貌夫人，令周瑜哭笑不得。\nZhou Yu devises a honeytrap: offer Sun Quan's sister in false marriage to lure Liu Bei to Eastern Wu and hold him hostage for Jing Province. But the plan misfires — Sun Quan's mother genuinely approves of Liu Bei and insists on a real wedding. Liu Bei gains a beautiful wife; Zhou Yu's scheme completely backfires."},
{id:55,title:"玄德智激孙夫人，孔明二气周公瑾",english:"Liu Bei's Clever Tactics Win Over Lady Sun; Zhuge Liang Infuriates Zhou Yu a Second Time",content:"刘备成婚后，周瑜仍图谋夺回荆州，以刘备之母病危的假消息骗刘备回荆州，趁机伏兵截杀。诸葛亮早已料到，临行前给刘备三个锦囊妙计，每个锦囊在关键时刻化解危机。刘备和孙夫人顺利逃回荆州，周瑜再度气恼。\nZhou Yu tries to lure Liu Bei to his death with news that his mother is ill. But Zhuge Liang has given Liu Bei three sealed letters to open at specific moments; each contains a perfect countermeasure. Liu Bei and Lady Sun escape; Zhou Yu is outmaneuvered again. Zhuge Liang's foresight is almost supernatural."},
{id:56,title:"曹操大宴铜雀台，孔明三气周公瑾",english:"Cao Cao's Grand Banquet at Bronze Sparrow Tower; Zhuge Liang Infuriates Zhou Yu for the Third Time",content:"周瑜最终因三气成疾，加之旧伤复发，临终长叹\"既生瑜，何生亮\"，年仅三十六岁即英年早逝。诸葛亮亲赴柴桑吊丧，祭文情真意切，令东吴众人皆泣，深感诸葛亮之心胸旷达，器量非凡。\nZhou Yu's humiliations at Zhuge Liang's hands — three times outmaneuvered — exacerbate his old battle wound. Dying at 36, he cries 'If Heaven made Zhou Yu, why make Zhuge Liang?' Zhuge Liang personally attends his funeral and delivers a eulogy so moving that all of Wu weeps, even those who came expecting to be angry."},
{id:57,title:"柴桑口卧龙吊丧，耒阳县凤雏理事",english:"Sleeping Dragon Mourns at Chaisang; Young Phoenix Administers Leiyang County",content:"庞统凤雏一直未被刘备重用，在耒阳县令任上故意懈怠，刘备发现后，庞统当场处理了百日积案，令刘备大为折服，之后与诸葛亮并为军师，一齐辅助刘备。凤雏之才，不在卧龙之下。\nPang Tong — 'Young Phoenix' — has been neglected by Liu Bei and assigned a minor post. He deliberately does no work for three months, then in a single morning disposes of all accumulated cases when challenged. Liu Bei is astonished and immediately promotes him alongside Zhuge Liang as co-advisor. The two geniuses serve together."},
{id:58,title:"马孟起兴兵雪恨，曹阿瞒割须弃袍",english:"Ma Chao Raises Army to Avenge His Family; Cao Cao Cuts His Beard and Sheds His Robe to Escape",content:"曹操杀死马腾，马超与韩遂联手起兵报复，大败曹操。潼关之战，马超追杀曹操，曹操为了逃跑，将长须剪去，脱下战袍，才得以脱险。马超之勇，与吕布并称，使曹操生平最狼狈的一次逃跑。\nCao Cao executes Ma Chao's father; Ma Chao and Han Sui raise an army of revenge. At Tong Pass Ma Chao's ferocious attack routs Cao Cao's army; Cao Cao cuts off his famous beard and discards his distinctive robe to avoid recognition as he flees. This is Cao Cao's most humiliating defeat — his own appearance becomes his enemy."},
{id:59,title:"许褚裸衣斗马超，曹操抹书问韩遂",english:"Xu Chu Fights Ma Chao Bare-Chested; Cao Cao's Letter Breaks the Alliance",content:"许褚与马超大战，难分胜负，许褚脱去战袍，赤裸上身，与马超力拼，两人筋疲力竭，一时未分高下。曹操随即用贾诩之计，伪造了一封似乎在暗示韩遂背叛马超的信件，在两人之间制造嫌隙，联盟就此瓦解。\nXu Chu, Cao Cao's ferocious bodyguard, fights Ma Chao to exhaustion; he strips off his armor to fight bare-chested, demonstrating animal power. Then Cao Cao follows Jia Xu's advice and forges a letter that seems to show Han Sui betraying Ma Chao. The alliance between the two generals fractures — Cao Cao wins without a battle."},
{id:60,title:"张永年反难杨修，庞士元议取西蜀",english:"Zhang Songn Outargues Yang Xiu; Pang Tong Plans the Conquest of Western Shu",content:"张松出使曹操，遭曹操轻慢，反投刘备，献上益州地图。庞统向刘备提出进取益州的计策，认为益州沃野千里，是帝业的基础，刘备在诸葛亮的支持下，开始谋划进入益州的行动。\nZhang Song, turned away contemptuously by Cao Cao, defects to Liu Bei and gives him a detailed map of Yi Province. Pang Tong urges Liu Bei to take Yi Province — its fertile lands are the foundation of empire. With Zhuge Liang's support, Liu Bei begins planning his move into the strategically vital southwest."},
{id:61,title:"赵云截江夺阿斗，孙权遗书退老瞒",english:"Zhao Yun Intercepts the Boat to Rescue the Young Lord; Sun Quan's Letter Makes Cao Cao Retreat",content:"孙夫人思念东吴，欲带阿斗回江东，实为东吴的要挟。赵云得知后单舟截江，从孙夫人手中夺回阿斗，张飞赶来接应，刘备之后再次得回儿子。孙权向曹操写信，暗示可以进取荆州，令曹操撤兵退回北方。\nLady Sun takes young Liu Shan to return to Eastern Wu — effectively kidnapping him as a hostage. Zhao Yun intercepts the boat alone, reclaims the child from Lady Sun, and escapes with Zhang Fei's help. The child's safety secured, Liu Bei can continue his plans."},
{id:62,title:"取涪关杨高授首，攻雒城庞统陨命",english:"Yang Huai and Gao Pei Lose Their Heads at Fucheng; Pang Tong Dies Attacking Luo City",content:"刘备借机杀死了益州两员守将，拉开了取益州的序幕。攻打雒城时，庞统因乘刘备坐骑白额马，被守城弓箭手认出，被乱箭射死于落凤坡，年仅三十六岁。\"凤雏\"就此陨落，刘备失去了一只臂膀。\nLiu Bei's conquest of Yi Province begins. Attacking Luo City, Pang Tong is riding Liu Bei's distinctive horse when he is recognized by archers and killed in a hail of arrows at Fallen Phoenix Slope — at exactly 36 years old, the same age as Zhou Yu. The 'Young Phoenix' falls; Liu Bei loses his most brilliant co-advisor."},
{id:63,title:"诸葛亮痛哭庞统，张翼德义释严颜",english:"Zhuge Liang Weeps for Pang Tong; Zhang Fei Releases the Captured Yan Yan with Honor",content:"庞统阵亡后，诸葛亮率军入川，张飞分路进兵，一路攻克险关。老将严颜被擒，张飞敬其年老有节，以礼相待，严颜大为感动，归顺刘备，并引路助张飞攻克了西川各险关，展现了张飞粗中有细的一面。\nAfter Pang Tong's death, Zhuge Liang enters Shu with Zhang Fei on a separate route. Zhang Fei captures the veteran Yan Yan — then treats the old general with such respect that Yan Yan, moved, surrenders and leads them through all the difficult passes. Zhang Fei's rough exterior conceals genuine chivalry."},
{id:64,title:"孔明定计捉张任，杨阜借兵破马超",english:"Zhuge Liang's Strategy Captures Zhang Ren; Yang Fu Defeats Ma Chao",content:"益州悍将张任智勇双全，多次令刘备军队陷入困境。诸葛亮最终以诱敌深入之计，将张任引入伏击圈，活捉了张任。张任誓死不降，壮烈就义。马超被韩遂联合的势力击败后，投奔刘备，成为刘备的重要战将。\nThe Shu general Zhang Ren is both brave and intelligent — repeatedly troubling Liu Bei's advance. Zhuge Liang finally lures him into an ambush and captures him. Zhang Ren refuses to surrender and is executed with honor. Ma Chao, defeated in the northwest, joins Liu Bei and becomes a prized general."},
{id:65,title:"马超大战葭萌关，刘备自领益州牧",english:"Ma Chao's Great Battle at Jiameng Pass; Liu Bei Declares Himself Governor of Yi Province",content:"刘璋求马超驻守葭萌关，马超与张飞大战，势均力敌，两人激战一夜，各自折服于对方的武勇。随着益州局势明朗，刘璋开城投降，刘备占据了整个益州，奠定了三国鼎立中蜀国的基础，隆中对的战略初步实现。\nLiu Zhang deploys Ma Chao at Jiameng Pass; he and Zhang Fei fight all night to a draw — mutual respect between two supreme warriors. When Liu Zhang's position becomes untenable, he surrenders and hands over Yi Province. Liu Bei's long dream of a base from which to restore the Han is realized. The Longzhong Plan is taking shape."},
{id:66,title:"关云长单刀赴会，伏皇后为国捐生",english:"Guan Yu Attends the Single-Sword Meeting; Empress Fu Dies for the Empire",content:"孙权欲夺荆州，以鸿门宴相邀，关羽只带周仓和几名随从，单刀赴会。席间气氛剑拔弩张，鲁肃提出荆州之事，关羽以喝酒为由避而不答，豪气干云，令东吴众人不敢轻举妄动，最终安全离去。\nSun Quan attempts to recover Jing Province by inviting Guan Yu to a banquet-ambush. Guan Yu attends with only a few attendants, carrying only his sword. At the table, surrounded by armed men, he drinks calmly and deflects all attempts to raise the Jing Province issue with magnificent composure, departing safely."},
{id:67,title:"曹操平定汉中地，张辽威震逍遥津",english:"Cao Cao Pacifies Hanzhong; Zhang Liao's Brilliant Defense at Xiaoyao Ford",content:"张辽以八百精兵逆袭孙权十万大军，在逍遥津大破东吴，孙权险些被擒，幸得众将拼死护卫。此战令张辽威名大震，\"张辽止啼\"的故事流传江东，东吴小儿闻张辽之名便不敢夜哭。\nZhang Liao leads 800 men in a preemptive strike against Sun Quan's army of 100,000 at Xiaoyao Ford, routing them and nearly capturing Sun Quan himself. Zhang Liao's audacious brilliance becomes legendary: it is said that in Jiangnan, mothers used his name to stop babies crying at night."},
{id:68,title:"甘宁百骑劫魏营，左慈掷杯戏曹操",english:"Gan Ning's Hundred-Horse Night Raid on the Wei Camp; the Immortal Left Ci Mocks Cao Cao",content:"甘宁率一百骑兵夜袭曹操大营，横冲直撞，从容来去，无人能挡，凯旋而归，东吴无人不服其胆略。曹操被奇异的道士左慈戏弄，无论如何追杀，左慈总能凭道法逃脱，令曹操无可奈何。\nGan Ning leads a hundred horsemen on a night raid directly through Cao Cao's camp — thundering in, creating chaos, and thundering out before anyone can react. Eastern Wu marvels at his audacity. Meanwhile the eccentric Daoist Zuo Ci torments Cao Cao with supernatural tricks that leave Cao Cao baffled and helpless."},
{id:69,title:"卜周易管辂知机，讨汉贼五臣死节",english:"The Diviner Guan Lu Foretells the Future; Five Ministers Die for the Han Cause",content:"神算管辂以《易》道推演，预言了多人的命运，无不应验。五位忠于汉室的臣子合谋诛杀曹操，事败被杀，以身殉国。汉室气数虽尽，却有无数忠义之士为其流血，令后世感慨不已。\nThe brilliant diviner Guan Lu reads the Book of Changes and predicts several people's fates with uncanny accuracy. Five Han loyalists conspire to kill Cao Cao; their plot is discovered and all five are executed. Though the Han dynasty is doomed, such acts of loyalty give the dying dynasty a tragic dignity."},
{id:70,title:"猛张飞智取瓦口关，老黄忠计夺天荡山",english:"Zhang Fei's Clever Capture of Wakou Pass; Old Huang Zhong's Night Raid on Tiandang Mountain",content:"刘备占据益州后，发兵夺取汉中，对曹操形成战略威胁。张飞用激将法使张郃上当，夺取了瓦口关。老将黄忠力不及壮年，却以智谋和勇气出奇制胜，夜袭天荡山，大败曹军，证明了老当益壮的英雄本色。\nLiu Bei launches the Hanzhong campaign against Cao Cao. Zhang Fei uses psychological tactics to goad Zhang He into an error, taking Wakou Pass. The elderly Huang Zhong — past his physical peak — uses a night raid on Tiandang Mountain to defeat Cao Cao's forces, proving that wisdom can overcome the decline of age."},
{id:71,title:"占对山黄忠逸待劳，据汉水赵云寡胜众",english:"Huang Zhong's Strategic Position at Duishan; Zhao Yun's Brilliant Defense of the Han River",content:"黄忠在定军山以逸待劳，斩杀曹操大将夏侯渊，夺取定军山，为汉中之战的胜利奠定了基础。赵云以少胜多，保住了粮草辎重，曹操赞叹\"子龙一身是胆\"，后来刘备也称赞赵云为\"虎威将军\"。\nHuang Zhong waits for the enemy at the advantageous position of Dingjun Mountain, then cuts down Xiahou Yuan in a sudden strike — a decisive blow in the Hanzhong campaign. Zhao Yun, with a tiny force, opens his camp gates when surrounded to confuse the attackers; Cao Cao himself reportedly says 'Zhao Yun is all courage.'"},
{id:72,title:"诸葛亮智取汉中，曹阿瞒兵退斜谷",english:"Zhuge Liang's Strategy Wins Hanzhong; Cao Cao Retreats Through Xie Valley",content:"汉中之战，曹操损兵折将，军心动摇，发出了\"鸡肋\"的口令，意为汉中如同鸡肋，食之无味，弃之可惜。杨修猜透曹操心意，令军队收拾行装，被曹操以动摇军心的罪名斩杀。曹操随后撤出汉中。\nIn the Hanzhong campaign Cao Cao gives the password 'chicken rib' — meaning something not worth keeping but too valuable to discard. Yang Xiu correctly interprets this as a signal to retreat, tells his men to pack up, and is executed by Cao Cao for undermining morale. Cao Cao abandons Hanzhong to Liu Bei."},
{id:73,title:"玄德进位汉中王，云长攻拔襄阳郡",english:"Liu Bei Is Proclaimed King of Hanzhong; Guan Yu Attacks Xiangyang",content:"刘备在夺取汉中后，在众臣力谏下自立汉中王，距皇帝之位更进一步。此时关羽在荆州出兵，发动了襄樊之战，水淹七军，擒于禁，斩庞德，威震华夏，令曹操一度考虑迁都以避其锋。\nAfter taking Hanzhong, Liu Bei accepts the title King of Hanzhong at his ministers' insistence — one step closer to emperor. Guan Yu simultaneously launches a campaign against Xiangyang, floods the seven armies of Yu Jin by releasing river water, capturing Yu Jin and beheading Pang De. Guan Yu's power shakes the entire north."},
{id:74,title:"庞德抬棺死战关公，于禁降服水淹七军",english:"Pang De Goes to Battle with His Own Coffin; Yu Jin Surrenders When the Seven Armies Are Flooded",content:"庞德以抬棺出战表明必死之志，与关羽激战，不落下风。曹仁部将于禁统率七支军队，被关羽以汉水上涨淹没了大营，于禁投降，庞德誓死不降被斩。关羽威名达到顶峰，令整个中原震动。\nPang De brings his own coffin to battle as a declaration that he will die rather than retreat; his duel with Guan Yu is a near thing. But when Guan Yu releases flood waters on the Seven Armies, Yu Jin surrenders and Pang De is captured and executed — refusing to kneel even facing death. Guan Yu's power is at its absolute peak."},
{id:75,title:"关云长刮骨疗毒，吕子明白衣渡江",english:"Guan Yu Has the Poison Scraped from His Bone; Lu Meng Crosses the River in White Clothing",content:"关羽中毒箭，神医华佗为其刮骨疗毒，关羽面不改色，谈笑自若，华佗叹服。与此同时，东吴吕蒙以白衣渡江的奇计，乔装成商人，偷渡过荆州防线，趁关羽北伐之际，兵不血刃夺取了荆州。\nGuan Yu is struck by a poisoned arrow; the great doctor Hua Tuo scrapes the bone to clean the wound while Guan Yu plays chess, showing no pain. Meanwhile Lu Meng crosses the Yangtze with his troops disguised as merchants, taking Jing Province without a fight while Guan Yu is focused on the north."},
{id:76,title:"徐公明大战沔水，关云长败走麦城",english:"Xu Huang's Great Battle at the Mian River; Guan Yu's Retreat to Mai City",content:"关羽发现荆州失守，后路断绝，与徐晃大战，未能取胜，只得引兵南撤。关羽困守麦城，兵少粮绝，派廖化突围求援，刘封、孟达见死不救，关羽被迫出城突围，中了吴军的埋伏。\nGuan Yu discovers Jing Province is lost, fights Xu Huang without success, and retreats to Mai City. Surrounded, cut off, starving, he breaks out with a tiny escort. His final campaign, from the height of power to this desperate flight, is one of history's most dramatic falls."},
{id:77,title:"玉泉山关公显圣，洛阳城曹操感神",english:"Guan Yu's Spirit Appears on Jade Spring Mountain; Cao Cao Is Moved by the Divine Apparition",content:"关羽被孙权所杀，首级送往曹操处。曹操以王侯之礼厚葬关羽首级，追封为荆王。关羽死后显灵于玉泉山，当地百姓立庙祭祀，关羽的神格化从此开始，其忠义精神千古流传，后世被尊为\"武圣\"。\nGuan Yu is captured and executed by Sun Quan's forces. His head is sent to Cao Cao, who has it buried with full royal honors. Guan Yu's spirit reportedly appears on Jade Spring Mountain; local people build a temple. His deification begins immediately — the loyal warrior becomes a god of war and righteousness, worshipped for two thousand years."},
{id:78,title:"治风疾神医身死，传遗命奸雄数终",english:"The Doctor Dies Treating the Headache; the Arch-Hero Approaches His End",content:"曹操头风病发，欲请华佗医治，华佗诊断须开颅治疗，曹操以为华佗要谋害他，将华佗下狱致死。曹操英雄一世，临终前分配遗产，言辞之间，尽见枭雄本色。建安二十五年，曹操病逝，一代枭雄就此谢幕。\nCao Cao's chronic headaches worsen; the great doctor Hua Tuo recommends brain surgery, but Cao Cao — ever suspicious — has him imprisoned and he dies. Cao Cao himself dies shortly after, making careful provisions for his household. The arch-villain and genuine statesman — the most complex figure of the age — departs the stage."},
{id:79,title:"兄逼弟曹植赋诗，侄陷叔刘封伏法",english:"Cao Pi Forces Cao Zhi to Write a Poem; Liu Feng Is Executed",content:"曹操死后，曹丕嗣位，加紧排除异己，以七步之内赋诗相威逼曹植，曹植即兴赋出\"本是同根生，相煎何太急\"，令曹丕悻悻而止。刘备之子刘封因见死不救关羽而被刘备处死，令人唏嘘。\nAfter Cao Cao's death, Cao Pi consolidates power. He challenges his brother Cao Zhi to compose a poem in seven steps or face death; Cao Zhi composes 'We grew from the same root — why must you burn me so eagerly?' Liu Bei executes his own adopted son Liu Feng for failing to aid Guan Yu — a painful but politically necessary act."},
{id:80,title:"曹丕废帝篡炎刘，汉王正位续大统",english:"Cao Pi Deposes the Emperor and Founds Wei; Liu Bei Continues the Han Line as Emperor",content:"曹丕废汉献帝，自立为魏文帝，汉朝正式灭亡。刘备随即在成都称帝，国号汉，以继承汉室正统自居。汉朝复辟的梦想，从此成为蜀汉君臣的历史使命，诸葛亮的北伐大业，将是这个梦想的最终表达。\nCao Pi formally deposes Emperor Xian and declares the Wei dynasty — the Han is over. Liu Bei immediately responds by declaring himself Emperor of Han in Chengdu, claiming the mandate to restore the dynasty. The dream of Han restoration becomes the defining mission of Liu Bei and, after his death, of Zhuge Liang."},
{id:81,title:"急兄仇张飞遇害，雪弟恨先主兴兵",english:"Zhang Fei Is Murdered Avenging His Brother; Liu Bei Launches a War to Avenge Guan Yu",content:"张飞因关羽之死悲愤欲绝，每日醉酒，苛责部下，范强、张达趁张飞酒醉将其杀死，提着首级投奔了孙权。刘备痛失两位结义兄弟，不顾诸葛亮劝阻，举倾国之兵伐吴，誓为关羽、张飞报仇雪恨。\nGrief-stricken over Guan Yu's death, Zhang Fei becomes tyrannical in his misery. His subordinates murder him in his sleep and defect to Eastern Wu. Liu Bei, having lost both sworn brothers in rapid succession, ignores Zhuge Liang's advice against it and launches a massive invasion of Eastern Wu."},
{id:82,title:"孙权降魏受九锡，先主征吴秉六师",english:"Sun Quan Submits to Wei; Liu Bei's Six Armies March Against Wu",content:"孙权为应对蜀汉的威胁，暂时向魏称臣，接受了九锡之赐。刘备率七十万大军东征吴国，兵锋所向，势如破竹，连营七百里，水陆并进，声势浩大，吴国上下惶惶不安，孙权求和不成，只好力战。\nTo counter the Shu threat, Sun Quan temporarily submits to Wei. Liu Bei's massive 700,000-man army — camps stretching seven hundred li — advances rapidly. Eastern Wu, unable to negotiate a settlement, must fight for survival against this tide of vengeance."},
{id:83,title:"战猇亭先主得仇人，守江口书生拜大将",english:"Liu Bei Defeats His Enemies at Xiaoting; Sun Quan Appoints a Young Scholar as Grand Commander",content:"蜀军势如破竹，东吴形势危急，孙权拜陆逊为大都督，统领全军。陆逊年轻，资历不深，众将不服，但陆逊坚守不出，令蜀军师老兵疲。时值盛夏，蜀军入驻密林避暑，陆逊寻得战机，准备发动决定性的火攻。\nWith Shu forces advancing rapidly, Sun Quan appoints the young scholar-general Lu Xun as grand commander. Veterans resent the young man. Lu Xun does nothing for months — waiting while the Shu army, stuck in dense forest in summer heat, grows tired and complacent. Then he sees his opportunity."},
{id:84,title:"陆逊营烧七百里，孔明巧布八阵图",english:"Lu Xun Burns Seven Hundred Li of Camps; Zhuge Liang's Eight Formation Arrays Stops the Pursuit",content:"陆逊发动火攻，七百里连营同时燃起，刘备大军全线崩溃，死伤无数，刘备仅以身免，逃至白帝城。蜀汉元气大伤，夷陵之战成为三国史上决定性的战役之一。诸葛亮设八阵图于鱼腹浦，阻止了追兵。\nLu Xun simultaneously fires all seven hundred li of Liu Bei's camps; the Shu army collapses. Liu Bei barely escapes to Baidicheng. The Battle of Yiling is one of the most decisive engagements of the Three Kingdoms era. The retreating army is stopped by Zhuge Liang's Eight Formation labyrinth on the river bank."},
{id:85,title:"刘先主遗诏托孤儿，诸葛亮安居平五路",english:"The Dying Emperor Entrusts His Son to Zhuge Liang; Zhuge Liang Deals with Five Threatening Armies",content:"刘备在白帝城病重，召诸葛亮托孤，遗诏中对诸葛亮说：若嗣子可辅，则辅之；若其不才，君可自取。诸葛亮感激涕零，誓死扶持幼主。刘备随后驾崩，刘禅即位，诸葛亮开始了鞠躬尽瘁的辅政生涯。\nLiu Bei on his deathbed summons Zhuge Liang and entrusts his son to him: 'If the heir is worthy, support him; if not, you may take the throne yourself.' Zhuge Liang weeps and pledges his life to the boy. Liu Bei dies; the young and weak Liu Shan becomes emperor. Zhuge Liang's era of devoted service begins."},
{id:86,title:"难张温秦宓逞天辩，破曹丕徐盛用火攻",english:"Qin Mi Defeats Zhang Wen in Debate; Xu Sheng Uses Fire Against Cao Pi",content:"东吴使臣张温出使蜀汉，廷议之间遭蜀汉学者秦宓以天文奥义问倒，黯然失色而归。曹丕三路大军伐吴，徐盛以芦苇扎成假城，令曹军误以为江南坚城难破，不战而退，东吴以智谋一次次化解危机。\nEastern Wu's envoy Zhang Wen is publicly outwitted in astronomical and philosophical debate by Shu's scholar Qin Mi. Cao Pi's three-army invasion of Wu is repelled through Xu Sheng's ingenious stratagem of fake fortified cities made from reeds — another Wei army turns back without a real battle."},
{id:87,title:"征南寇丞相大兴师，抗天兵蛮王初受执",english:"Prime Minister Zhuge Liang Launches the Southern Campaign; the Barbarian King Is Captured",content:"南中地区孟获叛乱，诸葛亮率军南征。诸葛亮的战略不是单纯的军事征服，而是\"攻心为上\"，意在使蛮人心悦诚服。诸葛亮七擒七纵孟获，最终孟获心服口服，誓不再反，南方从此稳定，诸葛亮解除了北伐的后顾之忧。\nThe southern tribes under Meng Huo rebel; Zhuge Liang campaigns south. His strategy is not conquest but conversion: capture hearts and minds. He captures and releases Meng Huo seven times, each time demonstrating superior virtue and wisdom. After the seventh release Meng Huo pledges eternal loyalty. The south is secured for the north."},
{id:88,title:"渡泸水再缚番王，识诈降三擒孟获",english:"Crossing the Lu River; Meng Huo Is Captured Again Through His Own Treachery",content:"孟获虽被擒数次，却始终不肯真心降服，每次都寻找新的理由和借口。诸葛亮每次将其释放，不是因为软弱，而是因为深谋远虑，要彻底折服其心。孟获引来各种援军和妖法，均被诸葛亮一一化解。\nMeng Huo is captured several times but refuses genuine submission, always finding new excuses. Each release by Zhuge Liang is not weakness but calculation — the goal is complete psychological surrender. Meng Huo brings foreign armies and magic; Zhuge Liang counters them all with characteristic calm."},
{id:89,title:"武乡侯四番用计，南蛮王五次遭擒",english:"Zhuge Liang Uses Strategy Four Times; the Barbarian King Is Captured a Fifth Time",content:"南征战事有条不紊，诸葛亮每逢强敌皆能以奇计应对，展示了其超凡的战略思维。云南地区的各族首领在亲眼目睹诸葛亮的仁义和智慧之后，纷纷归顺，南中各地得以平定，为蜀汉北伐提供了稳定的后方。\nZhuge Liang's southern campaign proceeds methodically; every formidable obstacle is overcome through intelligent strategy rather than brute force. Tribal leaders, witnessing his combination of power and humanity, submit willingly. The entire south is pacified, giving Liu Bei's empire the secure rear that the Longzhong Plan required."},
{id:90,title:"驱巨象七擒孟获，泸水烧藤甲兵",english:"War Elephants Are Driven Off; the Rattan-Armored Soldiers Are Burned at the Lu River",content:"孟获最后引来藤甲兵，藤甲入水不沉，刀枪不入，令蜀军一筹莫展。诸葛亮以火攻破藤甲，将藤甲兵大批烧死。诸葛亮叹\"吾虽有功于社稷，必损阴寿矣\"，可见其仁心，七擒孟获的故事展现了以德服人的最高境界。\nMeng Huo's rattan-armored soldiers cannot be harmed by steel or drowned. Zhuge Liang burns them alive with fire. He sighs: 'Though I serve the state, I must have shortened my life with this killing.' After the seventh capture, Meng Huo is genuinely moved. The Seven Captures story is the novel's supreme example of governing through virtue."},
{id:91,title:"祭泸水汉相班师，伐中原武侯上表",english:"Zhuge Liang Performs the Ceremony at the Lu River; He Submits His Memorial to Advance on the Central Plain",content:"平定南方后，诸葛亮班师回朝，在泸水渡口用面团制成人头祭祀阵亡将士。随后诸葛亮上书《出师表》，历数先帝之遗志，表达北伐中原、兴复汉室的决心，感情真挚，令后世每读此文必为之动容。\nAfter the southern campaign, Zhuge Liang returns and submits 'The Memorial on Going to War' — one of Chinese literature's most celebrated documents. He reviews the founding mission, the Emperor's trust, and his own unworthiness, expressing absolute commitment to restoring Han with such genuine emotion that it has moved readers for 1,800 years."},
{id:92,title:"赵子龙力斩五将，诸葛亮智取三城",english:"Zhao Yun Kills Five Generals; Zhuge Liang Captures Three Cities by Strategy",content:"诸葛亮第一次北伐，赵云虽年老，却仍能在战场上所向披靡，先后斩杀了多员魏将，令曹军刮目相看。诸葛亮以离间计和兵威，不战而取了三座城池，魏国西北边境震动。\nZhuge Liang's First Northern Expedition begins. Zhao Yun, now elderly, still kills five Wei generals in quick succession — his age undiminished by time. Through a combination of psychological pressure and strategic positioning, three cities fall to Shu without a major battle."},
{id:93,title:"姜伯约归降孔明，武乡侯骂死王朗",english:"Jiang Wei Defects to Zhuge Liang; the Prime Minister Verbally Destroys Wang Lang",content:"天水郡守将姜维识破了诸葛亮的计策，反被诸葛亮所器重，最终归降蜀汉，成为诸葛亮最得意的弟子。在军阵之前，年迈的魏国老臣王朗向诸葛亮喊话，欲以言辞相激，诸葛亮一番历数是非的厉声回骂，王朗气绝坠马而死。\nJiang Wei, a talented young Wei officer, is captured by Zhuge Liang. Rather than seeing an enemy, Zhuge Liang sees a successor and wins him over completely. In front of the armies, the aged Wei minister Wang Lang tries to morally challenge Zhuge Liang; Zhuge Liang's devastating rhetorical counter causes Wang Lang to literally fall dead from his horse."},
{id:94,title:"诸葛亮乘雪破羌兵，司马懿克日擒孟达",english:"Zhuge Liang Destroys the Qiang Army in the Snow; Sima Yi Captures Meng Da in Record Time",content:"诸葛亮北伐途中，以大雪和地形条件，设伏全歼羌族援军，展示了超凡的战术才能。司马懿以闪电速度，在孟达与蜀汉勾连叛魏之前，就率军突袭将孟达捉拿斩首，以迅雷不及掩耳的决断力令天下侧目。\nZhuge Liang uses snowfall and terrain in a perfect ambush against the Qiang reinforcements. Sima Yi moves with extraordinary speed to capture the defecting Meng Da before he can link up with Shu — demonstrating the decisiveness that will eventually make him Zhuge Liang's most formidable opponent."},
{id:95,title:"马谡拒谏失街亭，武侯弹琴退仲达",english:"Ma Su Ignores Advice and Loses Jieting; Zhuge Liang Plays the Lute to Make Sima Yi Retreat",content:"诸葛亮第一次北伐因马谡不听号令，在街亭安营山顶而不据守山下水源，被张郃大军断水而败，被迫全线撤退。西城空虚之际，诸葛亮临危不乱，打开城门，独坐城头弹琴，司马懿疑有埋伏，引兵退去，史称\"空城计\"。\nMa Su, ignoring all orders, camps on a mountaintop instead of blocking the road, and is defeated when his water is cut off — forcing the entire expedition to withdraw. At West City, with only a handful of men, Zhuge Liang opens the gates and plays his lute on the battlements; Sima Yi, suspecting a trap, withdraws. The 'Empty City Stratagem' becomes legendary."},
{id:96,title:"孔明挥泪斩马谡，周鲂断发赚曹休",english:"Zhuge Liang Weeps While Executing Ma Su; Zhou Fang Cuts His Hair to Deceive Cao Xiu",content:"诸葛亮依军法处死了马谡，自己也降职三级以示承担责任，此举令众人深为佩服。与此同时，东吴将领周鲂以苦肉计断发示降，骗取曹休信任，配合陆逊在石亭大败曹休，东吴再次展现出在战略博弈中的精妙。\nZhuge Liang weeps but executes Ma Su for insubordination — his public demonstration of impartiality strengthening rather than weakening his authority. He demotes himself three ranks. Meanwhile Eastern Wu's Zhou Fang cuts off his own hair as a 'proof of surrender' to deceive Cao Xiu, who is then routed at Shiting."},
{id:97,title:"讨魏国武侯再上表，破曹兵姜维诈献书",english:"Zhuge Liang Submits His Second Memorial to Campaign Against Wei; Jiang Wei Feigns a Letter Offering Surrender",content:"诸葛亮再上出师表，坚定北伐的意志，感人肺腑。第二次北伐出师，粮草不继，功败垂成。诸葛亮每次北伐都面临后勤补给的巨大压力，蜀道之难是制约北伐成败的关键因素之一。\nZhuge Liang submits his second memorial, reaffirming the commitment to restoring Han with renewed conviction. The second Northern Expedition fails again due to supply problems — the treacherous mountain roads of Shu impose severe constraints that all of Zhuge Liang's genius cannot fully overcome."},
{id:98,title:"追汉军王双受诛，袭陈仓武侯取胜",english:"Wang Shuang Is Killed Pursuing the Shu Army; Zhuge Liang Captures Chen Cang",content:"北伐期间，魏将王双多次袭扰蜀军后路，诸葛亮设伏将其诛杀。诸葛亮采用声东击西之计，表面上攻打陈仓，实际上绕道奇袭，屡出奇兵，令魏国防线疲于奔命。\nThe Wei general Wang Shuang repeatedly harasses Shu's rear; Zhuge Liang ambushes and kills him. Zhuge Liang then employs feints and flanking maneuvers, attacking Chen Cang as a diversion while his real forces strike elsewhere. Wei's defensive commanders are kept perpetually off-balance."},
{id:99,title:"诸葛亮大破魏兵，司马懿入寇西蜀",english:"Zhuge Liang Defeats the Wei Army; Sima Yi Invades Western Shu",content:"北伐期间，诸葛亮与司马懿之间的博弈是整部小说后半段的主线。司马懿深知自己不如诸葛亮，采取坚守不战的策略，拖延时间，消耗蜀军的粮草和士气。诸葛亮以女装赠送司马懿，讥讽其只知坚守，不敢进攻，司马懿竟处之泰然。\nThe duel between Zhuge Liang and Sima Yi dominates the latter half of the novel. Sima Yi knows he cannot match Zhuge Liang directly, so he simply refuses to fight, wearing down Shu's logistics. When Zhuge Liang sends him a woman's dress as an insult for his passivity, Sima Yi cheerfully wears it — infuriating his own generals but vindicating his strategy."},
{id:100,title:"汉兵劫寨破曹真，武侯斗阵辱仲达",english:"Zhuge Liang's Camp Raid Defeats Cao Zhen; He Humiliates Sima Yi Through Formation Tactics",content:"诸葛亮在第四次北伐中，与曹真、司马懿正面交锋。曹真病重不能出战，司马懿坚守营寨，诸葛亮数次挑战均无功而返。此时诸葛亮已感体力渐衰，北伐的时间窗口在一点一点关闭，令人扼腕。\nIn the Fourth Northern Expedition, Zhuge Liang faces both Cao Zhen and Sima Yi. Cao Zhen is too ill to command; Sima Yi refuses all battle. Zhuge Liang challenges repeatedly without success. His own health is declining — the window of opportunity for restoring Han is closing, a tragedy playing out in slow motion."},
{id:101,title:"出陇上诸葛妆神，奔剑阁张郃中计",english:"Zhuge Liang Appears as a Supernatural Being in the Longxi; Zhang He Falls into His Trap at Sword Pass",content:"诸葛亮布下奇阵，以木牛流马运输粮草，解决了后勤问题。魏将张郃急于追击，入了木门道埋伏，乱箭射死，张郃是曹魏最后一位能与诸葛亮对抗的将才，其死令曹魏大为震动。\nZhuge Liang invents the wooden ox and gliding horse — mechanical transport devices that solve his supply problem along the mountain roads. He lures Zhang He into a narrow gorge ambush; the Wei general is killed by a volley of arrows. Zhang He was Wei's last commander who could genuinely contest Zhuge Liang; his death is a major blow."},
{id:102,title:"司马懿占北原渭桥，诸葛亮造木牛流马",english:"Sima Yi Holds the Wei River Bridge; Zhuge Liang's Mechanical Transport Innovation",content:"诸葛亮的木牛流马解决了蜀道运粮的难题，令司马懿叹服不已。司马懿坚守渭水北岸，凭借险要地形拒不出战，双方相持日久，诸葛亮的宿疾渐重，已能感觉到自己生命的流逝。\nZhuge Liang's wooden transport devices leave Sima Yi in admiration of his ingenuity. Sima Yi holds the north bank of the Wei River and refuses engagement. The standoff drags on; Zhuge Liang's old illness worsens. He can feel his life running out as the armies face each other across the river."},
{id:103,title:"上方谷司马受困，五丈原诸葛禳星",english:"Sima Yi Is Trapped in the Upper Valley; Zhuge Liang Tries to Extend His Life at Wuzhang Plains",content:"诸葛亮在上方谷将司马懿父子困入火中，眼看大功告成，却突降大雨，将火浇灭，司马懿得以逃脱。诸葛亮深知自己命不久矣，在五丈原军中秘密举行禳星法事，以七星灯延命，却被魏延踢灭，禳星失败。\nZhuge Liang traps Sima Yi in a valley fire — final victory seemingly at hand — when rain extinguishes the flames and Sima Yi escapes. Zhuge Liang knows his time is nearly gone. In his tent he performs a secret ritual to extend his life; but the candle is accidentally knocked over, ending the ceremony. Heaven will not be cheated."},
{id:104,title:"陨大星汉丞相归天，见木像魏都督丧胆",english:"The Star Falls — the Prime Minister Passes Away; a Wooden Image Frightens the Wei Commander",content:"诸葛亮在五丈原病逝，遗命秘不发丧，安排有序撤退。蜀军悄然退去，司马懿追至，看见车上坐着诸葛亮的木像，以为诸葛亮未死，惊慌撤退，百姓皆笑称\"死诸葛走生仲达\"。诸葛亮鞠躬尽瘁，死而后已，千古忠臣之典范。\nZhuge Liang dies at Wuzhang Plains, his last act the arrangement of an orderly retreat. When Sima Yi cautiously pursues, he sees a lifelike wooden effigy of Zhuge Liang and retreats in alarm — giving rise to the saying 'the dead Zhuge frightened away the living Zhongda.' The people weep. An undying symbol of absolute devotion is gone."},
{id:105,title:"武侯预伏锦囊计，魏主拆取承露盘",english:"Zhuge Liang's Sealed Strategies Are Opened After His Death; Cao Rui's Hubris",content:"诸葛亮临终留下了多封锦囊，每一封都对应着未来可能发生的危机，弟子们按时开启，均能在危急时刻化险为夷。诸葛亮身后，其智慧仍在护佑蜀汉，令人感叹其谋深虑远，令人肃然起敬。\nZhuge Liang leaves sealed letters with specific instructions for specific future crises — his forethought proving so accurate that opening each one at the right moment rescues Shu from danger after danger. Even in death his intelligence continues to protect what he loved. The depth of his foresight is staggering."},
{id:106,title:"公孙渊兵败死襄平，司马懿诈病赚曹爽",english:"Gongsun Yuan Is Defeated and Dies; Sima Yi Feigns Illness to Trap Cao Shuang",content:"司马懿远征辽东，彻底消灭了公孙渊的割据势力。回朝后，曹爽专权，司马懿装病蛰伏，麻痹曹爽。待曹爽随皇帝扫墓出城之时，司马懿以迅雷不及掩耳之势发动政变，夺取了朝廷大权，为司马家族篡魏奠定了基础。\nSima Yi campaigns far northeast to destroy Gongsun Yuan's independent state. Back at court, he feigns senile illness to lull his rival Cao Shuang into complacency. When Cao Shuang leaves the capital, Sima Yi strikes instantly, seizing the government in a coup. The path to the Jin dynasty has begun."},
{id:107,title:"魏主政归司马氏，姜维兵败牛头山",english:"Wei's Government Falls to the Sima Clan; Jiang Wei Is Defeated at Ox Head Mountain",content:"曹爽被迫投降，随即被司马懿以谋反罪灭族，曹魏大权尽归司马氏。姜维继承了诸葛亮的北伐遗志，多次出兵，却缺乏诸葛亮的全局谋略，战绩参差不齐，难以取得决定性的成果。\nCao Shuang surrenders and is executed with his family for 'treason' — a transparent pretext. Wei is now Sima Wei in all but name. Jiang Wei inherits Zhuge Liang's mission of northern expeditions but lacks the comprehensive strategic vision; his campaigns are brave but inconclusive."},
{id:108,title:"丁奉雪中奋短兵，孙峻席间施密计",english:"Ding Feng's Brave Winter Battle; Sun Jun's Secret Plot at the Banquet",content:"东吴方面，权力争夺激烈，诸葛恪专权被孙峻设计诛杀。丁奉在雪中以轻装兵士袭击魏军，以奇兵大胜，是东吴晚期少见的精彩战例。三国末期，各方都陷入了内乱与权力斗争，英雄时代渐渐远去。\nIn Eastern Wu, intrigue and power struggles replace heroism. Zhuge Ke is assassinated by Sun Jun at a banquet. Ding Feng wins a brilliant winter battle through audacious light infantry tactics — one of the few genuine military highlights of the late Three Kingdoms period. The age of heroes is fading."},
{id:109,title:"困司马汉将奇谋，废曹芳魏家抱怨",english:"The Sima Clan Is Momentarily Trapped; Cao Fang Is Deposed",content:"司马师废黜曹芳，另立曹髦为帝，曹魏皇帝名存实亡，不过是司马氏的傀儡。忠于曹魏的将领毌丘俭、文钦起兵讨伐司马师，义举感人，但终因实力悬殊而失败，司马氏的权力愈发稳固。\nSima Shi deposes the Wei emperor Cao Fang and installs a new puppet. The loyal generals Guanqiu Jian and Wen Qin rise in a final rebellion against the usurpation — a courageous if doomed gesture. Their defeat consolidates Sima power. The Wei emperor is increasingly a figure of pure ceremony."},
{id:110,title:"文鸯单骑退雄兵，姜维背水破大敌",english:"Wen Yang Single-Handedly Holds Off an Army; Jiang Wei Wins with His Back to the River",content:"文鸯之勇，堪比赵云，单骑冲突，来回数次，令司马师所部不敢追赶。姜维北伐，以背水一战的绝境之策，激励蜀军奋勇出击，以少胜多，取得北伐以来难得的大胜，令魏军心惊胆战。\nWen Yang's bravery — single-handedly holding off pursuing armies — is compared to the great Zhao Yun. Jiang Wei, with his back to the river in a do-or-die position, inspires his troops to win against a larger force — one of the few genuine successes of Shu's late northern expeditions."},
{id:111,title:"邓士载智败姜伯约，诸葛诞义讨司马昭",english:"Deng Ai Outwits Jiang Wei; Zhuge Dan Raises a Righteous Army Against Sima Zhao",content:"邓艾是魏国后期最出色的将领，多次挫败姜维，以勤奋好学和出色的战场判断著称。诸葛诞以忠义之名起兵反抗司马昭，司马昭御驾亲征，诸葛诞兵败被杀，曹魏最后一支独立武装力量覆灭。\nDeng Ai is Wei's most brilliant late general, repeatedly defeating Jiang Wei through superior strategic insight. Zhuge Dan raises the last major loyal Wei force against Sima Zhao; Sima Zhao personally commands the suppression. Zhuge Dan is defeated and killed. The last independent Wei military power is extinguished."},
{id:112,title:"救寿春于诠死节，取长城伯约鏖兵",english:"Yu Quan Dies Heroically Defending Shouchun; Jiang Wei's Hard Fighting at the Long Wall",content:"寿春之役，诸葛诞兵败，部将于诠誓死守节，战死沙场，令对手也为之动容。姜维在北伐战场上几经沉浮，虽屡建奇功，却难以从根本上改变蜀弱魏强的大势，三国统一的大幕正在缓缓拉开。\nAt Shouchun, the loyal officer Yu Quan fights to the death rather than surrender — moving even his enemies. Jiang Wei continues his northern campaigns with occasional brilliance, but cannot overcome the fundamental imbalance of resources between Shu and Wei. The endgame of the Three Kingdoms era is approaching."},
{id:113,title:"丁奉定计斩孙綝，姜维斗阵破邓艾",english:"Ding Feng Kills Sun Chen; Jiang Wei Outmaneuvers Deng Ai in Battle Formation",content:"东吴权臣孙綝被皇帝吴景帝与丁奉合谋诛杀，东吴再度政归皇室。姜维与邓艾在战场上进行了多次精彩的对决，两位天才将领的斗智斗勇，是三国末年最精彩的军事看点，两人惺惺相惜，却又必须生死相博。\nSun Chen, the power behind the Wu throne, is killed in a palace coup. In the north, Jiang Wei and Deng Ai wage an extended campaign of brilliant tactical dueling — two military geniuses who respect each other forced by their respective loyalties to try to destroy each other."},
{id:114,title:"曹髦驾车死南阙，姜维弃粮胜魏兵",english:"Emperor Cao Mao Drives His Own Chariot to Die; Jiang Wei Abandons Grain to Defeat Wei",content:"曹魏皇帝曹髦不甘为傀儡，亲率宫人攻打司马昭，在宫门前被杀，惨烈而悲壮。司马昭另立曹奂为帝，大权独揽更甚。姜维以弃粮诱敌之计，设伏大破魏军，却终究无法改变天下大势。\nEmperor Cao Mao, refusing to live as a puppet, personally leads palace servants in an attack on Sima Zhao and is killed at the palace gate — a pitiable and heroic death. Sima Zhao installs yet another puppet. Jiang Wei wins tactical victories through brilliant maneuver but cannot alter the strategic reality."},
{id:115,title:"诏班师后主信谗，托屯田姜维避祸",english:"Liu Shan Recalls His Army Believing Slander; Jiang Wei Takes Refuge in Farming",content:"宦官黄皓在后主刘禅面前谗毁姜维，屡次阻挠北伐。姜维为躲避祸害，请求屯田沓中，远离朝廷。蜀汉内部的腐败已到了不可收拾的地步，忠臣义士报国无门，亡国之祸已难以避免。\nThe eunuch Huang Hao poisons Liu Shan against Jiang Wei, repeatedly blocking northern expeditions. Jiang Wei retreats to farm in the frontier to avoid court intrigue. Shu Han's internal corruption has become terminal; loyal officers can no longer serve effectively. The fall of Shu approaches."},
{id:116,title:"钟会分兵汉中道，武侯显圣定军山",english:"Zhong Hui Divides His Forces for the Hanzhong Campaign; Zhuge Liang's Spirit Appears at Dingjun Mountain",content:"司马昭制定灭蜀的战略，以钟会率主力正面进攻汉中，邓艾奇兵偷渡阴平。在出发之前，将士们来到诸葛亮墓前祭祀，传说诸葛亮英灵显现，为出征将士送行，令蜀汉将士心中涌起悲凉与敬意。\nSima Zhao plans the conquest of Shu: Zhong Hui attacks Hanzhong frontally while Deng Ai makes a secret flanking march. Before the campaign, Wei soldiers visiting Zhuge Liang's tomb reportedly feel a divine presence — the great man's spirit still inspiring awe even among his enemies, years after his death."},
{id:117,title:"邓士载偷度阴平，诸葛瞻战死绵竹",english:"Deng Ai's Secret Crossing of Yinping; Zhuge Zhan Dies at Mianzhu",content:"邓艾以出人意料的勇气，率兵从无人居住的阴平山道穿越，开凿山石，悬崖放毡而下，翻越了重重险阻，出现在成都平原。诸葛亮之子诸葛瞻率军迎战，兵败战死于绵竹，父子皆为汉室鞠躬尽瘁。\nDeng Ai leads his army through the uninhabited mountain passes of Yinping in an act of extraordinary audacity — cutting through rock, wrapping himself and soldiers in felt blankets to slide down cliffs. He emerges on the Chengdu plain behind all Shu defenses. Zhuge Liang's own son Zhuge Zhan dies fighting this advance; the family's devotion continues to the end."},
{id:118,title:"哭祖庙一王死孝，入西川二士争功",english:"Liu Shan Surrenders Weeping at the Ancestral Temple; the Two Wei Commanders Quarrel Over Glory",content:"成都外无援兵，内无战心，刘禅听从谯周劝告，举白旗投降。蜀汉就此灭亡，历四十三年。\"此间乐，不思蜀\"的典故从此传世，刘禅或愚或智，至今众说纷纭。邓艾与钟会争功，司马昭对二人均存疑忌。\nWith no relief army coming, Liu Shan accepts the advice to surrender without a fight. Shu Han ends after 43 years. In captivity Liu Shan says he is happy and doesn't miss Shu — making him either a fool or a brilliantly self-protective actor. Deng Ai and Zhong Hui immediately quarrel over credit, both now expendable to Sima Zhao."},
{id:119,title:"假投降巧计成虚话，再受禅依样画葫芦",english:"A False Surrender Plan Becomes Empty Talk; the Abdication Is Repeated for the Second Time",content:"钟会心怀野心，欲据益州自立，联络被扣押的姜维共谋，却被部下告发。乱军中钟会、姜维均被杀，邓艾也在混乱中被冤杀。一代英雄豪杰在功成之际相互倾轧，令人唏嘘。曹魏也随即灭亡，司马炎建立晋朝。\nZhong Hui, ambitious, attempts to declare independence in Shu and enlists the captured Jiang Wei. His own officers revolt and kill him; Jiang Wei dies fighting in the chaos; Deng Ai is unjustly executed in the confusion. The three men who conquered Shu all die within months. Wei itself is then replaced by the Jin dynasty."},
{id:120,title:"荐杜预老将献新谋，降孙皓三分归一统",english:"The Veteran Du Yu's New Strategy; Sun Hao Surrenders — the Three Kingdoms Reunite Under Jin",content:"晋武帝司马炎命王濬、杜预等人灭亡东吴，孙皓在暴虐中荒废了江山，东吴百姓饱受苦难。王濬楼船顺流而下，势如破竹，孙皓出降，东吴灭亡，三国归晋，天下重归一统，百年乱世宣告终结。\nJin's Emperor Wu launches the final campaign against Eastern Wu. Wang Jun's great fleet sweeps down the Yangtze; the brutal emperor Sun Hao surrenders without significant resistance. Eastern Wu falls; the Three Kingdoms are unified under Jin after nearly a century of war. The wheel of history turns, as the novel's opening proclaims: unity follows division, division follows unity."}
],

hongloumeng: [
{id:1, title:"甄士隐梦幻识通灵，贾雨村风尘怀闺秀", english:"Zhen Shiyin Dreams of the Magic Jade; Jia Yucun Pines for the Beauty", content:"此回讲述了甄士隐在梦中得遇一僧一道，见到了通灵宝玉的来历，以及贾雨村寄居葫芦庙时对甄家丫鬟娇杏的倾慕。\nThis chapter introduces Zhen Shiyin, who dreams of a monk and a Taoist priest carrying a lustrous jade, and Jia Yucun, a poor scholar lodging in Gourd Temple who secretly admires Ying-chun, a maid of the Zhen household."},
{id:2, title:"贾夫人仙逝扬州城，冷子兴演说荣国府", english:"Lady Jia Passes Away in Yangzhou; Leng Zixing Describes the Rong Mansion", content:"林如海之妻贾敏病逝，贾雨村受林如海之托护送黛玉进京。冷子兴向贾雨村介绍荣国府的人口结构与近况。\nJia Min, wife of Lin Ruhai, passes away. Jia Yucun is entrusted to escort the young Lin Daiyu to the capital. Meanwhile, Leng Zixing gives Jia Yucun a detailed account of the Jia family's Rong Mansion and its many inhabitants."},
{id:3, title:"托内兄如海荐西宾，接外孙贾母惜孤女", english:"Lin Ruhai Recommends a Tutor; Grandmother Jia Welcomes Her Orphaned Granddaughter", content:"林如海向贾母写信荐举贾雨村，黛玉乘船进京，初见外祖母贾母及荣国府众人，宝玉与黛玉初次相见，宝玉摔玉。\nLin Ruhai writes to recommend Jia Yucun as a tutor. Daiyu travels by boat to the capital and is warmly received by her grandmother, Lady Dowager Jia. She meets the various members of the Rong household and encounters Bao-yu for the first time, who famously throws his jade to the ground."},
{id:4, title:"薄命女偏逢薄命郎，葫芦僧判断葫芦案", english:"An Ill-Fated Girl Meets an Ill-Fated Youth; The Gourd Monk Judges the Gourd Case", content:"贾雨村审理薛蟠打死人命案，在门子指点下徇私枉法，放过薛蟠。薛家母子进京投靠贾家，薛宝钗由此进入荣国府。\nJia Yucun presides over the murder case involving Xue Pan and, guided by a corrupt clerk, bends the law in Xue Pan's favor. The Xue family then travels to the capital to stay with the Jias, bringing the beautiful Xue Baochai into the Rong Mansion."},
{id:5, title:"游幻境指迷十二钗，饮仙醪曲演红楼梦", english:"Bao-yu Visits the Land of Illusion; The Twelve Beauties of Jinling Are Revealed", content:"宝玉随贾母等赴宁国府赏梅，午睡时游太虚幻境，警幻仙子向其展示金陵十二钗正副册及红楼梦曲，暗示众女命运。\nBao-yu accompanies Lady Dowager to Ning Mansion for a plum-blossom viewing. During an afternoon nap he visits the Land of Illusion, where the Fairy Disenchantment shows him the registers of the Twelve Beauties of Jinling and plays the Dream of Red Mansions songs, foreshadowing the fates of all the girls."},
{id:6, title:"贾宝玉初试云雨情，刘姥姥一进荣国府", english:"Bao-yu's First Awakening to Love; Granny Liu's First Visit to Rong Mansion", content:"宝玉与袭人初试云雨之情。穷苦农妇刘姥姥带孙子板儿第一次进荣国府，向王熙凤借钱，王熙凤给了她二十两银子。\nBao-yu has his first intimate experience with the maid Aroma. Meanwhile, the poor country woman Granny Liu arrives at Rong Mansion for the first time with her grandson Ban-er, seeking financial help from Wang Xifeng, who gives her twenty taels of silver."},
{id:7, title:"送宫花贾琏戏熙凤，宴宁府宝玉会秦钟", english:"Palace Flowers Are Delivered; Bao-yu Meets Qin Zhong at a Ning Mansion Banquet", content:"薛宝钗托周瑞家的送宫花，宝玉在宁府认识了秦钟，两人一见如故。贾珍之妻尤氏邀请众人吃年酒。\nXue Baochai sends palace flowers as gifts through the servant Zhou Rui's wife. At a banquet in Ning Mansion, Bao-yu meets Qin Zhong and the two immediately become close friends. Jia Zhen's wife You-shi hosts a New Year feast."},
{id:8, title:"比通灵金莺微露意，探宝钗黛玉半含酸", english:"Golden Oriole Hints at the Destined Match; Daiyu Shows a Touch of Jealousy", content:"宝玉去梨香院探望宝钗，莺儿说宝钗金锁上的字与宝玉玉上的字恰好相配，暗示金玉良缘。黛玉赶来，心存醋意。\nBao-yu visits Baochai in the Pear Fragrance Court. The maid Oriole hints that the words on Baochai's golden locket match those on Bao-yu's jade, suggesting a destined match. When Daiyu arrives and notices the attention, she cannot conceal a hint of jealousy."},
{id:9, title:"恋风流情友入家塾，起嫌疑顽童闹学堂", english:"Friends Enter the Family School; Trouble Breaks Out Among the Students", content:"宝玉与秦钟一同入贾家家塾读书，薛蟠也在其中。贾瑞对凤姐产生邪念。学堂中贾蔷与香怜闹出风波。\nBao-yu and Qin Zhong begin attending the Jia family school together, where Xue Pan is also enrolled. Meanwhile, Jia Rui develops an improper infatuation with Wang Xifeng. A scandal erupts in the school involving Jia Qiang and a young student named Xiang-lian."},
{id:10, title:"金寡妇贪利权受辱，张太医论病细穷源", english:"The Greedy Widow Is Humiliated; Dr. Zhang Carefully Diagnoses the Illness", content:"秦可卿病重，贾蓉之父贾珍请来名医张友士诊治，张太医详细分析秦可卿的病情，认为是忧思过度所致。\nQin Keqing falls gravely ill. Jia Zhen summons the renowned physician Zhang Youshi, who carefully examines Qin Keqing and diagnoses her condition as resulting from excessive worry and emotional distress. His prognosis is not optimistic."},
{id:11, title:"庆寿辰摆宴于东府，见熙凤贾瑞起淫心", english:"A Birthday Feast at the East Mansion; Jia Rui's Infatuation with Xifeng", content:"贾敬寿辰，荣宁两府设宴庆贺。贾瑞见到王熙凤，色心大动，贾瑞向凤姐示爱遭拒，凤姐设计戏弄贾瑞。\nJia Jing's birthday is celebrated with a grand banquet attended by both the Rong and Ning households. Jia Rui encounters Wang Xifeng and becomes infatuated. When he declares his feelings, Xifeng rebuffs him sharply and devises a scheme to punish him for his impertinence."},
{id:12, title:"王熙凤毒设相思局，贾天祥正照风月鉴", english:"Xifeng Sets a Cruel Trap; Jia Rui Gazes into the Romantic Mirror", content:"贾瑞中了王熙凤的圈套，两次受到捉弄，大病不起。道士赠他风月宝鉴，嘱咐只看背面，贾瑞不听，最终一命呜呼。\nJia Rui falls into Xifeng's trap twice and becomes gravely ill. A Taoist priest gives him a magical mirror called the Romantic Mirror, warning him to look only at the back. Jia Rui disobeys, stares at the front, and eventually dies from his obsession."},
{id:13, title:"秦可卿死封龙禁尉，王熙凤协理宁国府", english:"Qin Keqing Dies; Wang Xifeng Takes Charge of Ning Mansion", content:"秦可卿病逝，托梦凤姐提醒及早谋划后事。贾珍大办丧事，王熙凤协理宁国府，展现出卓越的管理才能。\nQin Keqing dies. Her spirit appears to Xifeng in a dream, urging her to plan ahead for the family's future. Jia Zhen arranges an extravagant funeral, and Wang Xifeng steps in to manage the affairs of Ning Mansion, displaying remarkable organizational skill."},
{id:14, title:"林如海捐馆扬州城，贾宝玉路谒北静王", english:"Lin Ruhai Passes Away in Yangzhou; Bao-yu Meets Prince Bei-jing on the Road", content:"黛玉父亲林如海病逝扬州，黛玉彻底成为孤儿。宝玉等人送秦可卿灵柩出城，途中宝玉与北静王水溶相见，互赠礼物。\nLin Ruhai, Daiyu's father, passes away in Yangzhou, leaving Daiyu a complete orphan. The Jia family escorts Qin Keqing's coffin out of the city, and along the way Bao-yu meets the gracious Prince Bei-jing, and they exchange gifts."},
{id:15, title:"王熙凤弄权铁槛寺，秦鲸卿得趣馒头庵", english:"Xifeng Abuses Her Power at Iron Threshold Temple; Qin Zhong Has a Dalliance at Steamed Bun Convent", content:"王熙凤在铁槛寺借权谋私，收受贿赂，致使两人殉情而死。秦钟与尼姑智能在馒头庵私会，宝玉得知后颇为羡慕。\nXifeng abuses her position at Iron Threshold Temple by accepting a bribe to manipulate a legal case, leading to the tragic deaths of two people. Qin Zhong has a secret tryst with the novice nun Zhi-neng at Steamed Bun Convent, much to Bao-yu's envious amusement."},
{id:16, title:"贾元春才选凤藻宫，秦鲸卿夭逝黄泉路", english:"Jia Yuanchun Is Chosen as an Imperial Consort; Qin Zhong Passes Away", content:"贾元春被选入宫，封为贤德妃，贾家上下欢欣鼓舞，开始筹备省亲别院。秦钟因病与智能私奔未成，含恨而终。\nJia Yuanchun is selected as an Imperial Noble Consort, bringing great joy to the Jia family, who begin preparations for a grand reception garden. Qin Zhong, weakened by illness and grief over his failed elopement with Zhi-neng, passes away."},
{id:17, title:"大观园试才题对额，荣国府归省庆元宵", english:"Bao-yu's Talent Shines in Grand View Garden; Yuanchun Returns for the Lantern Festival", content:"贾政带宝玉等人游大观园，为各处题写匾额，宝玉才思敏捷，深得贾政称赞。元春省亲，大观园一派热闹景象。\nJia Zheng tours the newly completed Grand View Garden with Bao-yu and others to compose inscriptions. Bao-yu's quick wit and literary talent earn rare praise from his father. The garden is then filled with celebration as Yuanchun makes her ceremonial visit home."},
{id:18, title:"皇恩重元妃省父母，天伦乐宝玉呈才藻", english:"The Imperial Consort Visits Her Parents; Bao-yu Displays His Literary Talent", content:"元春回贾府省亲，与家人相聚，流泪感慨身在深宫之苦。命宝玉等人作诗，宝玉才情出众，元春赐各处新名。\nYuanchun's visit to her family is filled with emotion as she tearfully laments the loneliness of palace life. She asks Bao-yu and the girls to compose poems, and Bao-yu's verses stand out. Yuanchun renames the pavilions and halls of Grand View Garden with new poetic titles."},
{id:19, title:"情切切良宵花解语，意绵绵静日玉生香", english:"On a Sweet Night Flowers Speak of Feeling; On a Quiet Day Jade Breathes Its Fragrance", content:"元春省亲后，命众姊妹与宝玉移居大观园。袭人劝说宝玉用功读书，宝玉体贴黛玉，两人感情日益深厚。\nAfter Yuanchun's visit, she decrees that Bao-yu and the girls shall live in Grand View Garden. Aroma gently urges Bao-yu to study harder. Bao-yu and Daiyu grow ever closer, their bond deepening through small acts of tenderness and understanding."},
{id:20, title:"王熙凤正言弹妒意，林黛玉俗语见真情", english:"Xifeng Rebukes Jealousy; Daiyu Reveals True Feeling in Plain Words", content:"宝玉与黛玉因小事赌气，宝玉向黛玉赔礼道歉。王熙凤出面调解，笑骂两人像夫妻一样斗嘴。黛玉吐露真情。\nBao-yu and Daiyu quarrel over a trifle, and Bao-yu humbly apologizes. Wang Xifeng steps in as a playful mediator, teasing the two that they bicker like an old married couple. Daiyu, moved, lets slip her true feelings in plain, unguarded words."},
{id:21, title:"贤袭人娇嗔箴宝玉，俏平儿软语救贾琏", english:"Aroma Gently Reproves Bao-yu; Ping-er Tactfully Saves Jia Lian", content:"袭人以情动人，劝说宝玉改掉坏习惯，宝玉答应她三件事。贾琏与鲍二家的私通，被凤姐发现大闹，平儿从中周旋。\nAroma appeals to Bao-yu's better nature, persuading him to give up three bad habits. Bao-yu agrees. Meanwhile, Jia Lian's affair with Bao-er's wife is discovered by Xifeng, who creates a violent scene. Ping-er skillfully mediates to calm the situation."},
{id:22, title:"听曲文宝玉悟禅机，制灯谜贾政悲谶语", english:"Bao-yu Ponders Zen While Listening to Opera; Jia Zheng Is Saddened by Riddle Omens", content:"元宵节贾母令众人猜灯谜，元春所制灯谜令贾政心感不祥。宝玉从戏曲中悟出禅机，感叹人生无常，黛玉开解他。\nAt the Lantern Festival, the family gathers to guess riddles. Yuanchun's riddle fills Jia Zheng with a sense of foreboding. Bao-yu, moved by the opera, reflects on the impermanence of life. Daiyu comforts him with gentle words."},
{id:23, title:"西厢记妙词通戏语，牡丹亭艳曲警芳心", english:"Lines from The Western Chamber Spark Flirtatious Banter; Melodies from The Peony Pavilion Stir Daiyu's Heart", content:"宝玉以《西厢记》词句调笑黛玉，黛玉先怒后笑。黛玉听到《牡丹亭》唱词，感同身受，悄然落泪，心有所触。\nBao-yu teases Daiyu with lines from The Western Chamber; she first flushes with anger, then dissolves into laughter. Later, overhearing melodies from The Peony Pavilion, Daiyu is deeply moved by the romantic lyrics and sheds quiet tears, feeling a profound resonance."},
{id:24, title:"醉金刚轻财尚义侠，痴女儿遗帕惹相思", english:"The Drunken Monk Values Loyalty Over Gold; A Lovesick Girl's Handkerchief Stirs Longing", content:"贾芸托倪二向宝玉示好，在大观园谋得差事。小红对宝玉有爱慕之情，将手帕传递给宝玉，引出一段相思。\nJia Yun, aided by the generous drunkard Ni Er, secures a job in Grand View Garden through Bao-yu's favor. The maid Xiao-hong secretly admires Bao-yu and contrives to exchange handkerchiefs with him, setting her heart aflutter with longing."},
{id:25, title:"魇魔法姊弟逢五鬼，红楼梦通灵遇双真", english:"A Sorcery Curse Afflicts the Siblings; The Magic Jade Encounters Two Immortals", content:"马道婆受赵姨娘贿赂，用魇魔法害宝玉与凤姐，二人昏迷不醒。癞头和尚与跛足道人出现，令通灵宝玉显灵，两人方才苏醒。\nMa Dao-po is bribed by Concubine Zhao to cast a malevolent spell on Bao-yu and Xifeng, plunging both into a coma. A bald monk and a lame Taoist appear and use the magic jade to break the curse, and both victims gradually recover."},
{id:26, title:"蜂腰桥设言传心事，潇湘馆春困发幽情", english:"A Message Is Passed at Wasp-Waist Bridge; Spring Languor Stirs Poetic Feeling in Bamboo Lodge", content:"小红借佳蕙向贾芸传递情意。宝玉去潇湘馆探视黛玉，见其春睡初醒，娇美无比，两人谈笑。燕子归巢，春意盎然。\nXiao-hong uses Jia-hui as a go-between to convey her feelings to Jia Yun. Bao-yu visits Daiyu in the Bamboo Lodge and finds her just waking from an afternoon nap, exquisitely beautiful. They chat and laugh together as swallows return to their nests in the spring warmth."},
{id:27, title:"滴翠亭杨妃戏彩蝶，埋香冢飞燕泣残红", english:"Baochai Chases Butterflies at the Green Pavilion; Daiyu Buries Fallen Petals at the Flower Mound", content:"宝钗追蝴蝶至滴翠亭，无意听到小红与坠儿的私语，以林黛玉为由脱身。黛玉一人葬花，吟诵《葬花吟》，凄美动人。\nBaochai, chasing butterflies, accidentally overhears Xiao-hong and Zhui-er's private conversation near the Green Pavilion and cleverly deflects suspicion onto Daiyu. Meanwhile, Daiyu alone buries fallen petals at the Flower Mound and recites her moving and melancholy Burial of Flowers elegy."},
{id:28, title:"蒋玉菡情赠茜香罗，薛宝钗羞笼红麝串", english:"Jiang Yuhan Gives a Crimson Sash; Baochai Blushes Over Her Musk Bracelet", content:"宝玉结识戏子蒋玉菡，互赠汗巾。宝钗无意中将手套在宝玉手腕上，觉得失态，忙缩回，令宝玉念念不忘。\nBao-yu befriends the actor Jiang Yuhan at a private banquet; they exchange sashes as tokens of friendship. Separately, while trying on a bracelet, Baochai accidentally clasps Bao-yu's wrist and quickly withdraws, flustered, leaving Bao-yu charmed and distracted."},
{id:29, title:"享福人福深还祷福，痴情女情重愈斟情", english:"The Fortunate Pray for More Fortune; The Lovesick Girl Is Ever More Lovesick", content:"贾母携众人去清虚观打醮，张道士为宝玉提亲，宝玉不悦。宝黛因通灵玉之事再次争吵，互相赌气，宝玉砸玉。\nLady Dowager leads the family to a Taoist temple for a religious ceremony. A Taoist priest proposes a match for Bao-yu, who rejects it irritably. Back home, Bao-yu and Daiyu quarrel again over the jade and the golden locket, and Bao-yu smashes the jade in frustration."},
{id:30, title:"宝钗借扇机带双敲，龄官画蔷痴及局外", english:"Baochai Delivers a Double Rebuke Through Fan Talk; Ling-guan Draws Roses in the Dust, Oblivious to Bystanders", content:"薛宝钗借扇子话题，一语双关，同时敲打宝玉和黛玉。宝玉在蔷薇花圃旁，见戏子龄官独自在地上画蔷字，痴态可掬。\nBaochai uses the occasion of a borrowed fan to deliver a veiled double rebuke at both Bao-yu and Daiyu. Later, Bao-yu stumbles upon the young actress Ling-guan near the rose trellis, repeatedly tracing the character for her beloved Jia Qiang in the dirt, lost in her own world."},
{id:31, title:"撕扇子作千金一笑，因麒麟伏白首双星", english:"Tearing a Fan Earns a Thousand-Gold Smile; The Kylin Portends a Lifelong Union", content:"晴雯因打碎扇坠与宝玉置气，宝玉为博她一笑，任由她撕扇。史湘云佩戴麒麟，宝玉也有一枚，暗示两人缘分。\nQing-wen quarrels with Bao-yu over a broken fan pendant. To make her laugh, Bao-yu lets her tear fans to her heart's content. Separately, Shi Xiang-yun's gold kylin pendant matches one that Bao-yu carries, hinting at a predestined connection between the two."},
{id:32, title:"诉肺腑心迷活宝玉，含耻辱情烈死金钏", english:"Bao-yu Bares His Heart; Jin-chuan Dies in Shame", content:"宝玉向袭人诉说对黛玉的真心，恰被黛玉听到，心中大喜。金钏被王夫人逐出，含羞投井而死，宝玉悲痛万分。\nBao-yu confesses his feelings for Daiyu to Aroma; Daiyu overhears every word and is overwhelmed with joy. Then comes the tragedy: Jin-chuan, a maid dismissed in humiliation by Lady Wang, drowns herself in a well, and the news devastates Bao-yu."},
{id:33, title:"手足耽耽小动唇舌，不肖种种大承笞挞", english:"Jealous Lips Move Against Bao-yu; He Receives a Severe Beating", content:"贾环向贾政告发宝玉勾引金钏，贾政大怒，将宝玉打得皮开肉绽，几乎要了他的命，贾母出面才救下宝玉。\nJia Huan maliciously reports to Jia Zheng that Bao-yu had seduced the maid Jin-chuan. Jia Zheng, in a fury, beats Bao-yu savagely, nearly killing him. Only the intervention of Lady Dowager stops the punishment."},
{id:34, title:"情中情因情感妹妹，错里错以错劝哥哥", english:"Feeling Within Feeling Moves the Sister; Mistake Upon Mistake Counsels the Brother", content:"宝玉伤愈期间，托晴雯给黛玉送去旧手帕，黛玉领会其意，感动落泪，题诗于帕上。宝钗来探伤，借机规劝宝玉。\nDuring his recovery, Bao-yu sends two old handkerchiefs to Daiyu via Qing-wen as a token of his heart. Daiyu understands perfectly, weeps with emotion, and inscribes poems on the handkerchiefs. Baochai also visits to check on him and takes the opportunity to counsel him gently."},
{id:35, title:"白玉钏亲尝莲叶羹，黄金莺巧结梅花络", english:"Bai Yu-chuan Tastes the Lotus Soup; Golden Oriole Cleverly Knots a Plum-Blossom Cord", content:"宝玉病中，白玉钏喂他莲叶羹，宝玉百般讨好。莺儿为宝玉编织梅花络，宝钗在旁指点，又一次展现出宝钗的贤惠。\nBao-yu is pampered during his illness. The maid Bai Yu-chuan feeds him lotus-leaf broth. The maid Oriole knits him an intricate plum-blossom cord while Baochai supervises, once again displaying her gentle competence and warmth."},
{id:36, title:"绣鸳鸯梦兆绛芸轩，识分定情悟梨香院", english:"Embroidering Mandarin Ducks; Understanding Destiny in Pear Fragrance Court", content:"宝玉回房，见袭人在绣鸳鸯，朦胧入梦，梦中唤黛玉之名。宝玉去梨香院探望龄官，见她与贾蔷情深意切，若有所悟。\nBao-yu returns to his rooms and sees Aroma embroidering mandarin ducks; he drowses off calling Daiyu's name in his sleep. He then visits Ling-guan in Pear Fragrance Court and observes her deep devotion to Jia Qiang, sensing something important about the nature of love and destiny."},
{id:37, title:"秋爽斋偶结海棠社，蘅芜苑夜拟菊花题", english:"The Crab-apple Poetry Club Is Founded at Autumn Freshness Studio; Chrysanthemum Poem Topics Are Chosen at Alpinia Park", content:"探春发起成立海棠诗社，众姊妹积极响应，各取雅号。宝钗、黛玉、湘云等人在蘅芜苑共议菊花诗题，诗社活动开始。\nTan-chun proposes forming a poetry club centered on crab-apple blossoms, and the girls enthusiastically agree, each taking a literary nickname. At Alpinia Park, Baochai, Daiyu, Xiang-yun and others propose chrysanthemum poem topics for the club's next gathering."},
{id:38, title:"林潇湘魁夺菊花诗，薛蘅芜讽和螃蟹咏", english:"Lin Daiyu Wins the Chrysanthemum Poetry Contest; Xue Baochai Composes a Satirical Crab Poem", content:"海棠诗社以菊花为题赋诗，黛玉三首夺魁。众人螃蟹宴上，宝钗作《螃蟹咏》讽刺横行霸道之人，众人叫绝。\nThe poetry club holds a chrysanthemum poem contest, and Daiyu wins first place with three magnificent poems. At a subsequent crab feast, Baochai composes a brilliant satirical poem on crabs, mocking those who bully and swagger their way through life, to universal applause."},
{id:39, title:"村姥姥是信口开河，情哥哥偏寻根究底", english:"Granny Liu Tells Tall Tales; Bao-yu Tries to Trace Them to Their Source", content:"刘姥姥在大观园游玩，讲述茗玉小姐的故事，众人欢笑。宝玉将信将疑，亲自去探访，心中有所触动，为茗玉设香火。\nGranny Liu entertains the household with folk tales during her garden visit, including a charming story about a young girl named Mingyu. Bao-yu is fascinated and half-believes it; he goes looking for the shrine and sets up incense for the girl, moved by his romantic imagination."},
{id:40, title:"史太君两宴大观园，金鸳鸯三宣牙牌令", english:"Lady Dowager Hosts Two Banquets in the Garden; Golden Mandarin Duck Leads the Ivory Domino Game", content:"贾母两次在大观园设宴，请刘姥姥参观，刘姥姥闹出许多笑话。鸳鸯主持牙牌令，众人轮流说令，场面热闹欢快。\nLady Dowager hosts two garden banquets for Granny Liu's entertainment. The country woman's rustic antics provide much merriment. The head maid Yuan-yang presides over an ivory domino game with witty forfeits, filling the garden with laughter and warmth."},
{id:41, title:"栊翠庵茶品梅花雪，怡红院劫遇母蝗虫", english:"Tasting Plum-Blossom Snow Tea at Green Gauze Convent; Granny Liu's Mayhem at Happy Red Court", content:"妙玉以梅花上的雪水泡茶，款待贾母等人，显示出妙玉的高洁品味。刘姥姥误入宝玉卧室，闹出笑话，醉卧花中。\nMiao-yu serves tea brewed from snow gathered from plum blossoms, revealing her refined and ascetic taste. Granny Liu, tipsy from wine, wanders into Bao-yu's bedchamber and causes uproarious confusion before being discovered asleep among the flowers."},
{id:42, title:"蘅芜君兰言解疑癖，潇湘子雅谑补余香", english:"Baochai Gives Gentle Counsel; Daiyu Offers Witty Comfort", content:"宝钗向黛玉讲述自己因贪看杂书而被训诫的故事，劝黛玉不要沉溺诗词；黛玉心有所感，感谢宝钗的好意。\nBaochai tells Daiyu about being reprimanded for reading forbidden books, and gently advises her not to become too absorbed in poetry and romance. Daiyu is genuinely touched by Baochai's candid concern and thanks her sincerely, their friendship momentarily deepening."},
{id:43, title:"闲取乐偶攒金庆寿，不了情暂撮土为香", english:"An Impromptu Birthday Celebration Is Arranged; A Makeshift Incense Honors the Dead", content:"众人为贾母凑份子庆生，热闹非凡。宝玉记挂金钏的忌日，偷偷溜出去祭奠，用土代香，心中哀思难以言表。\nThe residents of the garden pool their resources for a joyful birthday celebration for Lady Dowager. On the same day, Bao-yu remembers the anniversary of Jin-chuan's death, slips away, and offers earth in place of incense at her grave, his grief private and wordless."},
{id:44, title:"变生不测凤姐泼醋，喜出望外平儿理妆", english:"An Unexpected Jealous Scene from Xifeng; Ping-er Unexpectedly Gets to Dress Up", content:"凤姐发现贾琏与鲍二家的有染，大发醋意，闹得满府皆知。事后贾琏央求平儿说情，凤姐令平儿重新梳妆打扮，以示恩赏。\nXifeng discovers Jia Lian's affair and erupts in a jealous fury that rocks the whole household. Afterwards, Jia Lian begs Ping-er to mediate. Xifeng, in an unexpectedly generous mood, asks Ping-er to dress up properly with fine clothes and jewelry as a reward for her loyalty."},
{id:45, title:"金兰契互剖金兰语，风雨夕闷制风雨词", english:"Two Friends Share Their Innermost Thoughts; On a Stormy Evening, a Melancholy Lyric Is Composed", content:"黛玉与宝钗在风雨之夜互吐心声，情同金兰，黛玉深感宝钗之真诚。黛玉独坐听雨，有感而发，创作《秋窗风雨夕》。\nOn a stormy night, Daiyu and Baochai share their innermost thoughts with unusual candor, and Daiyu is genuinely moved by Baochai's sincerity. Alone afterward, listening to the rain, Daiyu is overcome with melancholy and composes her famous poem Autumn Window Rain Night."},
{id:46, title:"尴尬人难免尴尬事，鸳鸯女誓绝鸳鸯偶", english:"An Awkward Person in an Awkward Situation; Yuan-yang Vows to Remain Unwed", content:"贾赦看上鸳鸯，托邢夫人来说合，鸳鸯当众发誓，宁死不嫁，并剪发明志，感动众人，贾母也为之动容。\nJia She sets his sights on the head maid Yuan-yang and sends Lady Xing to arrange the match. Yuan-yang publicly and dramatically refuses, swearing before the whole household that she would rather die than marry, and cuts her hair as a pledge, moving everyone including Lady Dowager."},
{id:47, title:"呆霸王调情遭苦打，冷郎君惧祸走他乡", english:"The Dull Bully Flirts and Gets Beaten; The Cold Young Man Flees Trouble", content:"薛蟠调戏柳湘莲，被柳湘莲痛打一顿，大出洋相。薛蟠羞愧难当，借机出门经商，离开了这是非之地。\nXue Pan makes crude advances toward the handsome young actor Liu Xiang-lian and receives a thorough beating for his insolence, greatly embarrassing himself. Ashamed, Xue Pan takes the opportunity to leave the capital on a trading venture."},
{id:48, title:"滥情人情误思游艺，慕雅女雅集苦吟诗", english:"A Fickle Man Wastes His Days in Pleasure; A Refined Girl Suffers Through a Poetry Gathering", content:"贾赦强娶鸳鸯未成，迁怒邢夫人。宝玉等人在大观园举行诗会，黛玉身体不佳，强撑着参加，才情依然出众。\nJia She, having failed to obtain Yuan-yang, takes his anger out on Lady Xing. Meanwhile, Bao-yu and the girls hold a poetry gathering in the garden. Daiyu, unwell, pushes herself to attend and still produces the most remarkable verse of the evening."},
{id:49, title:"琉璃世界白雪红梅，脂粉香娃割腥啖膻", english:"A Crystal World of White Snow and Red Plum; The Fragrant Girls Eat Venison and Lamb", content:"大雪后大观园银装素裹，宝玉与众姊妹赏雪。湘云豪爽，与众人围炉烤鹿肉，畅快淋漓。宝钗折梅赋诗，雅趣横生。\nAfter a heavy snowfall, Grand View Garden is transformed into a dazzling white world. Bao-yu and the girls enjoy the snow-scape. The spirited Xiang-yun roasts venison with the group around a brazier in high spirits. Baochai picks red plum blossoms and composes an elegant poem."},
{id:50, title:"芦雪庭争联即景诗，暖香坞雅制春灯谜", english:"Competing Linked Verse at Reed Snow Pavilion; Crafting Spring Riddles at Warm Fragrance Studio", content:"众人在芦雪庭联诗，湘云与黛玉联得最佳，宝玉却落了最后，被罚去折梅。探春的暖香坞，众人又制作春灯谜助兴。\nThe poetry club holds a linked-verse competition at Reed Snow Pavilion in the snow. Xiang-yun and Daiyu are declared the winners; Bao-yu comes last and is sent to fetch red plum blossoms as a forfeit. Later at Tan-chun's studio, everyone crafts Spring Festival lantern riddles."},
{id:51, title:"薛小妹新编怀古诗，胡庸医乱用虎狼药", english:"Xue Baocin Composes Poems on Ancient Sites; A Quack Doctor Prescribes Dangerous Medicine", content:"薛宝琴新到，才思出众，作怀古诗十首，令众人叹服。晴雯受寒生病，庸医开了虎狼之药，宝玉心疼，急忙另请良医。\nThe newly arrived Xue Bao-qin demonstrates her remarkable talent by composing ten poems on historical sites, astonishing everyone. The maid Qing-wen falls ill with a cold; a quack doctor prescribes harsh medicine, alarming Bao-yu, who quickly arranges for a better physician."},
{id:52, title:"俏平儿情掩虾须镯，勇晴雯病补雀金裘", english:"Clever Ping-er Conceals the Missing Bracelet; Brave Qing-wen Mends the Peacock Coat While Ill", content:"平儿为保全小红，隐瞒虾须镯失窃之事。晴雯带病连夜补好宝玉的雀金裘，以铁针穿刺，手指流血，令宝玉心疼不已。\nPing-er tactfully conceals the theft of a bracelet to protect the maid Xiao-hong. Meanwhile Qing-wen, burning with fever, heroically spends the night repairing Bao-yu's damaged peacock-feather coat stitch by stitch, her fingers bleeding from the needle, as Bao-yu watches in helpless admiration."},
{id:53, title:"宁国府除夕祭宗祠，荣国府元宵开夜宴", english:"New Year's Eve Ancestral Rites at Ning Mansion; Lantern Festival Night Banquet at Rong Mansion", content:"宁国府除夕祭祖，礼仪隆重庄严。荣国府元宵夜宴，贾母、众媳妇儿孙满堂，热闹非凡，宝玉表演节目，其乐融融。\nNing Mansion holds a solemn ancestral rite on New Year's Eve. Rong Mansion hosts a lavish Lantern Festival banquet where three generations gather; Bao-yu performs to entertain the company, and Lady Dowager presides over the joyful scene with a grandmother's contentment."},
{id:54, title:"史太君破陈腐旧套，王熙凤效戏彩斑衣", english:"Lady Dowager Discards Stale Convention; Wang Xifeng Acts the Clown to Amuse Her Elders", content:"贾母批评才子佳人小说陈腐套路，见识超群。凤姐讲笑话，学小丑逗贾母欢笑，众人皆赞凤姐口才好，贾母大乐。\nLady Dowager offers incisive criticism of clichéd romance fiction, showing surprising sophistication. Wang Xifeng then entertains the company by telling jokes and mimicking a clown to make Lady Dowager laugh, delighting everyone with her wit and comic timing."},
{id:55, title:"辱亲女愚妾争闲气，欺幼主刁奴蓄险心", english:"A Foolish Concubine Vents Spite on Her Daughter; A Scheming Servant Harbors Malice Against the Young Master", content:"赵姨娘与贾环因小事争吵，赵姨娘为贾环出气，反被众人嘲笑。探春管家期间，赵姨娘来生事，探春当众维护了家法。\nConcubine Zhao and her son Jia Huan quarrel over a trifle; Concubine Zhao makes a fool of herself trying to defend him. When Tan-chun is managing the household, Concubine Zhao comes to stir up trouble, and Tan-chun publicly upholds the household rules without regard for her birth mother."},
{id:56, title:"敏探春兴利除宿弊，时宝钗小惠全大体", english:"Clever Tan-chun Introduces Reforms; Practical Baochai Grants Small Favors for the Greater Good", content:"探春主持家政，大力兴利除弊，取消不合理的旧例，将大观园承包给下人耕种，节省开支，展现出卓越的管理才能。\nWith Tan-chun managing the household, she boldly abolishes wasteful practices and introduces sensible reforms, including leasing parts of Grand View Garden to servants for cultivation, saving expenses. Baochai supports the reforms with tactful concessions that win everyone's goodwill."},
{id:57, title:"慧紫鹃情辞试莽玉，慈姨妈爱语慰痴颦", english:"Clever Zi-juan Tests Bao-yu's Feelings for Daiyu; Kind Aunt Xue Comforts the Weeping Girl", content:"紫鹃谎称黛玉要回苏州，宝玉信以为真，大病一场，情深义重令人动容。姨妈薛姨妈安慰黛玉，以母亲之心对待她。\nDaiyu's maid Zi-juan tests Bao-yu's love by falsely claiming Daiyu is returning to Suzhou. Bao-yu is shattered and falls gravely ill, his distress proving the depth of his feelings. Aunt Xue Yima comforts the anxious Daiyu with motherly warmth and reassurance."},
{id:58, title:"杏子阴假凤泣虚凰，茜纱窗真情揆痴理", english:"False Phoenixes Weep Under the Apricot Tree; True Feeling Is Understood Through the Red Gauze Window", content:"宝玉在杏树下见两只燕子交颈依依，感叹情深缘浅。芳官唱曲，宝玉听后颇有所感。龄官因思念贾蔷而哭泣，宝玉旁观心有戚戚。\nBao-yu watches two swallows nestled together under an apricot tree and reflects on fleeting bonds. The actress Fang-guan sings a moving song. Bao-yu observes Ling-guan weeping for her beloved Jia Qiang and realizes with sudden clarity that each person's tears belong to only one person."},
{id:59, title:"柳叶渚边嗔莺咤燕，绛云轩里召将飞符", english:"A Quarrel Among the Birds by the Willow Isle; Bao-yu Summons Help with a Paper Spell", content:"春燕因柳枝之事与其母起了口角，众丫头围观嬉笑。宝玉为解燕儿之困，写了一道符令，命丫头传去，化解了风波。\nChun-yan quarrels with her mother over trimming the willow branches; the other maids watch in amusement. Bao-yu writes a mock paper charm to defuse the dispute and sends it over, turning the quarrel into a lighthearted episode."},
{id:60, title:"茉莉粉替去蔷薇硝，玫瑰露引来茯苓霜", english:"Jasmine Powder Replaces Rose Nitrate; Rose Dew Leads to the Discovery of Poria Cream", content:"芳官将蔷薇硝换了茉莉粉给赵姨娘，引起误会和口角。柳五儿之母因贩卖玫瑰露与茯苓霜，引出一段小风波。\nThe actress Fang-guan gives Concubine Zhao jasmine powder instead of rose nitrate, causing a misunderstanding. The sale of purloined rose dew and poria cream from the garden pantry creates a small scandal involving the maid Liu Wu-er's family."},
{id:61, title:"投鼠忌器宝玉瞒赃，判冤决狱平儿行权", english:"Bao-yu Conceals a Theft to Protect the Innocent; Ping-er Administers Justice", content:"司棋表妹柳五儿被疑偷盗，宝玉为保护无辜，隐瞒了实情，最终平儿出面，以智慧平息了这场误会，还了柳五儿清白。\nLiu Wu-er, cousin of Si-qi, is suspected of theft. Bao-yu conceals what he knows to protect an innocent person. Ping-er ultimately steps in with good judgment, clears up the misunderstanding, and restores Liu Wu-er's reputation."},
{id:62, title:"憨湘云醉眠芍药茵，呆香菱情解石榴裙", english:"Xiang-yun Falls Asleep Drunk Among the Peonies; Fragrant Chrysanthemum Stains Her Pomegranate Skirt", content:"湘云饮酒大醉，卧于芍药花丛中酣睡，众人发现，颇觉有趣。香菱无意弄脏了石榴裙，换下后，众人取笑她痴呆。\nXiang-yun drinks too much wine at a birthday party and falls asleep amid the peony blossoms, her face flushed and beautiful in her drunken repose. Fragrant Chrysanthemum (Xiang-ling) accidentally stains her pomegranate-red skirt, and the others tease her good-naturedly for her absentmindedness."},
{id:63, title:"寿怡红群芳开夜宴，死金丹独艳理亲丧", english:"A Night Banquet Celebrates Bao-yu's Birthday; Jia Jing Dies from Elixir Abuse", content:"怡红院众人给宝玉过生日，夜宴欢乐，行酒令，黛玉掣得芙蓉签。与此同时，贾敬因吞食仙丹过多而死，宁府治丧。\nThe residents of Happy Red Court celebrate Bao-yu's birthday with a joyful late-night banquet and wine games; Daiyu draws the hibiscus flower card. Meanwhile, Jia Jing dies from over-consuming Taoist elixirs, and Ning Mansion goes into mourning."},
{id:64, title:"幽淑女悲题五美吟，浪荡子情赴家塾中", english:"A Gentle Girl Composes Poems on Five Famous Beauties; A Dissolute Youth Pursues a Fancy to the Family School", content:"黛玉以五位古代美人为题，写出《五美吟》，借古人之命运，寄托自身的身世之感。薛蟠归来，带了香菱进京。\nDaiyu composes the Five Beauties poems, five elegant verses on ill-fated women of antiquity through which she veils her own sorrows and premonitions. Xue Pan returns from his travels, bringing Xiang-ling with him to the capital."},
{id:65, title:"贾二舍偷娶尤二姐，尤三姐思嫁柳二郎", content:"贾琏在宁府偷娶尤二姐为外室，金屋藏娇。尤三姐心仪柳湘莲，坚等其归来成婚，拒绝一切他人求亲，矢志不渝。", english:"Jia Lian Secretly Takes You Er-jie as a Second Wife; You San-jie Waits Faithfully for Liu Xiang-lian"},
{id:66, title:"情小妹耻情归地府，冷二郎一冷入空门", english:"The Passionate Girl Meets a Tragic End; The Cold Young Man Enters the Monastery", content:"柳湘莲回京，因听说了尤三姐的荒唐名声，退了婚事。尤三姐含冤自刎而死，柳湘莲深受触动，遁入空门为僧。\nLiu Xiang-lian returns to the capital but, having heard rumors about You San-jie's past, breaks off the engagement. You San-jie, her honor impugned, kills herself with his sword. Stricken with remorse, Liu Xiang-lian cuts off his hair and follows a Taoist into the mountains."},
{id:67, title:"见土仪颦卿思故里，闻秘事凤姐讯家童", english:"Gifts from Home Make Daiyu Think of Her Native Place; Hearing a Secret, Xifeng Interrogates a Page", content:"薛蟠从南方带回土仪，黛玉见到江南之物，触景生情，思念故乡，愁绪满怀。凤姐听到贾琏纳妾的风声，开始调查。\nXue Pan returns from the south with local gifts. When Daiyu sees objects from the Jiangnan region, she is overcome with homesickness and melancholy longing for her native place. Meanwhile, Xifeng hears rumors of Jia Lian's secret marriage and begins to investigate."},
{id:68, title:"苦尤娘赚入大观园，酸凤姐大闹宁国府", english:"Crafty Xifeng Lures You Er-jie into the Garden; Vinegary Xifeng Creates a Scene at Ning Mansion", content:"凤姐将尤二姐骗入大观园，表面亲热，暗中折磨。凤姐又在宁国府大闹，揭露贾琏纳妾之事，令贾琏颜面扫地。\nXifeng lures You Er-jie into the safety of the garden while secretly tormenting her. She then makes a dramatic scene at Ning Mansion, publicly exposing Jia Lian's secret marriage and humiliating him before the whole household."},
{id:69, title:"弄小巧用借剑杀人，觉大限吞生金自逝", english:"Xifeng Uses Borrowed Knives to Kill; You Er-jie, Sensing the End, Swallows Gold", content:"凤姐借刀杀人，逼得尤二姐的腹中孩儿夭折，尤二姐走投无路，吞金自尽。贾琏悲痛欲绝，只能草草安葬。\nXifeng engineers the death of You Er-jie's unborn child and crushes her spirit through relentless cruelty. With no way out, You Er-jie swallows gold and dies. Jia Lian, grief-stricken and powerless, can only arrange a simple burial for her."},
{id:70, title:"林黛玉重建桃花社，史湘云偶填柳絮词", english:"Daiyu Reconvenes the Peach Blossom Poetry Club; Xiang-yun Improvises a Willow Catkin Lyric", content:"黛玉重开诗社，以桃花为题，众人赋诗。湘云偶填柳絮词，清丽自然。宝玉见黛玉题诗，心有所感，爱怜更深。\nDaiyu revives the poetry club with a peach blossom theme. The girls compose poems, and Xiang-yun improvises a charming lyric about willow catkins. Bao-yu reads Daiyu's poem and is moved by its beauty, his love and tenderness for her deepening."},
{id:71, title:"嫌隙人有心生嫌隙，鸳鸯女无意遇鸳鸯", english:"Those Who Seek Fault Will Find It; Yuan-yang Unwittingly Encounters a Romantic Scene", content:"贾母八十大寿，众人操办得隆重热闹。宴席上妯娌之间出现嫌隙，邢夫人寻衅滋事。鸳鸯无意间目睹了一对偷情者。\nLady Dowager's eightieth birthday is celebrated with great pomp. During the festivities, tensions emerge among the sisters-in-law, with Lady Xing causing trouble. The maid Yuan-yang unwittingly witnesses a clandestine romantic encounter."},
{id:72, title:"王熙凤恃强羞说病，来旺妇倚势霸成亲", english:"The Strong-Willed Xifeng Refuses to Acknowledge Her Illness; A Servant's Wife Uses Influence to Force a Match", content:"凤姐久病不愈，却强撑精神不肯示弱，暗中已是心力交瘁。来旺家的仗着凤姐的势，强逼一门不情愿的婚事成功。\nXifeng's health continues to deteriorate, but she refuses to show weakness, pushing herself past all sensible limits. A servant's wife exploits Xifeng's power and influence to force a marriage that neither party wants."},
{id:73, title:"痴丫头误拾绣春囊，懦小姐不问累金凤", english:"A Foolish Maid Picks Up the Embroidered Pouch; A Weak Young Lady Fails to Question the Golden Phoenix", content:"小丫头在园中拾到一个绣春囊，引起轩然大波，王夫人大为震怒，命人彻查大观园。迎春软弱，丢失金凤钗却不追究。\nA little maid finds an embroidered purse with erotic designs in the garden, causing a scandal. Lady Wang is outraged and orders a thorough search of Grand View Garden. Ying-chun, meanwhile, loses a golden phoenix hairpin but is too passive to demand it back from those who took it."},
{id:74, title:"惑奸谗抄检大观园，制昏庸椎杀晴雯", english:"Misled by Slanderous Words, the Garden Is Searched; Blameless Qing-wen Is Driven Out and Dies", content:"王夫人受人挑唆，命人抄检大观园，芳官、司棋等人相继被驱逐。晴雯遭受不白之冤，被逐出贾府，病中含冤而死。\nLady Wang, influenced by malicious gossip, orders a night search of Grand View Garden. Several maids including Fang-guan and Si-qi are expelled. The innocent Qing-wen is unjustly accused and banished from the household, and she dies of illness, her name uncleared."},
{id:75, title:"开夜宴异兆发悲音，赏中秋新词得佳谶", english:"Strange Omens at a Night Banquet; New Mid-Autumn Poems Yield Prophetic Lines", content:"中秋夜宴，贾珍等人于宁府饮宴嬉游，忽闻悲声，众人惊恐。宝玉与黛玉、湘云联诗，湘云的诗句暗含悲谶之语。\nAt a Mid-Autumn night banquet at Ning Mansion, the revelers are frightened by the sound of strange weeping. Bao-yu, Daiyu, and Xiang-yun compose linked verse by moonlight; Xiang-yun's lines contain an unconscious prophecy of sorrows to come."},
{id:76, title:"闷制桃花扇，悲题竹叶诗", english:"Crafting a Peach Blossom Fan in Gloom; Composing Bamboo Leaf Poems in Sorrow", content:"黛玉在中秋之夜悲愁难遣，与妙玉联诗，妙玉续完黛玉未尽之作，隐含哀音。黛玉独处，制了一把桃花扇寄托哀思。\nOn the melancholy Mid-Autumn night, Daiyu composes sad verses with Miao-yu, who completes Daiyu's unfinished poem, both full of hidden sorrow. Daiyu alone makes a peach blossom fan as an outlet for her grief and loneliness."},
{id:77, title:"俏丫环抱屈夭风流，美优伶斩情归水月", english:"A Lovely Maid Dies Unjustly; A Beautiful Actor Renounces Worldly Love", content:"晴雯含冤而死，宝玉悲痛，作《芙蓉女儿诔》祭奠，寄托哀思。芳官、藕官、蕊官三人出家为尼，斩断红尘情缘。\nQing-wen dies unjustly, and the grief-stricken Bao-yu composes an eloquent elegy for her, the Eulogy to the Hibiscus Maid. The three young actresses Fang-guan, Ou-guan, and Rui-guan take religious vows and leave the secular world."},
{id:78, title:"老学士闲征姽婳词，痴公子杜撰芙蓉诔", english:"An Old Scholar Casually Elicits Warrior Verses; The Infatuated Young Master Composes a Hibiscus Elegy", content:"贾政令宝玉等人作姽婳将军诗，赞美女将军之英勇。宝玉独自作《芙蓉女儿诔》悼念晴雯，借以抒发对黛玉的深情。\nJia Zheng asks Bao-yu and others to compose poems about a heroic female general named Gui-hua. Alone, Bao-yu writes his Hibiscus Maid Elegy for Qing-wen, but in composing it he is also speaking his truest feelings for Daiyu."},
{id:79, title:"薛文龙悔娶河东狮，贾迎春误嫁中山狼", english:"Xue Wen-long Regrets Marrying a Shrew; Jia Ying-chun Mistakenly Weds a Brute", content:"薛蟠娶了夏金桂，不料其性情悍烈，薛家上下鸡飞狗跳，薛蟠悔不当初。迎春嫁给孙绍祖，不久即受尽折磨。\nXue Pan marries Xia Jin-gui only to discover she is a tyrannical shrew, plunging the Xue household into chaos. Ying-chun is married off to Sun Shao-zu, who soon reveals his brutal nature and subjects her to cruel mistreatment."},
{id:80, title:"美香菱屈受贪夫棒，王道士胡诌妒妇方", english:"The Beautiful Xiang-ling Is Beaten by a Greedy Brute; A Taoist Quack Concocts a Cure for Jealousy", content:"夏金桂嫉妒香菱，对其百般折磨，甚至诬告香菱，令薛蟠对香菱大打出手。道士以荒诞的方子为凤姐治妒，众人大笑。\nXia Jin-gui, jealous of Xiang-ling, persecutes her relentlessly and even frames her, provoking Xue Pan into beating her. Meanwhile a charlatan Taoist offers a ridiculous remedy for jealousy, prescribing a cure for Xifeng's jealousy that makes everyone laugh."},
{id:81, title:"占旺相四美钓游鱼，奉严词两番入家塾", english:"Four Beauties Fish in the Garden; Bao-yu Is Sent Back to School Under Strict Orders", content:"探春、宝钗、宝琴、岫烟在大观园中钓鱼，闲适雅致。贾政回京，严命宝玉用功读书，宝玉奉命入家塾，无奈从命。\nTan-chun, Baochai, Bao-qin, and Xiu-yan spend a pleasant afternoon fishing in the garden. Jia Zheng returns to the capital and sternly orders Bao-yu to study properly. Bao-yu reluctantly obeys and returns to the family school."},
{id:82, title:"老学究讲义警顽心，病潇湘痴魂惊恶梦", english:"An Old Scholar's Lesson Stirs a Reluctant Student; Sick in Bamboo Lodge, Daiyu Is Troubled by a Nightmare", content:"宝玉在家塾中受先生教导，心有所感，对读书有了新的认识。黛玉病中做了一个可怕的噩梦，梦见被弃，悲啼而醒。\nAt school, the old tutor's earnest lecture touches something in Bao-yu, giving him a new perspective on study. Meanwhile, the ailing Daiyu is tormented by a terrible nightmare in which she is abandoned by Bao-yu and wakes up sobbing."},
{id:83, title:"省宫闱贾元妃染恙，入朝堂贾老爷忧惧", english:"Yuanchun Becomes Ill in the Palace; Jia Zheng Is Troubled at Court", content:"宫中传来消息，贾元春身体抱恙，贾家上下忧心忡忡。贾政在朝中受到牵连，忧虑不安，家道开始出现颓势的苗头。\nWord comes from the palace that Yuanchun has fallen ill, filling the Jia household with anxiety. Jia Zheng encounters political difficulties at court, and for the first time the shadow of the family's coming decline begins to fall over the household."},
{id:84, title:"试文字宝玉始提亲，探惊风贾环重结怨", english:"Bao-yu's Marriage Prospects Are Broached; Jia Huan Renews His Grudge After a Fright", content:"贾母、王夫人议及宝玉婚事，倾向于宝钗。宝玉对此一无所知。贾环受到惊吓，将祸事归咎于宝玉，母子二人怨恨更深。\nLady Dowager and Lady Wang discuss Bao-yu's future marriage, leaning toward Baochai as the choice. Bao-yu knows nothing of these deliberations. Jia Huan, frightened by a mishap, blames Bao-yu, deepening the resentment between the two half-brothers."},
{id:85, title:"贾存周报升郎中任，薛文龙提充马快手", english:"Jia Zheng Is Promoted to a New Post; Xue Pan Is Arrested and Impressed into Service", content:"贾政升任郎中，贾家暂时迎来好消息。薛蟠在外惹祸，被迫充当衙役，薛姨妈忧心如焚，薛家开始走向衰落之路。\nJia Zheng receives a promotion, briefly lifting the family's spirits. Outside the capital, Xue Pan gets into serious trouble and is impressed into government service as a runner, causing his mother great distress. The Xue family's decline begins."},
{id:86, title:"接大任贾政赴外省，见刑司宝玉证同参", english:"Jia Zheng Departs for a Provincial Post; Bao-yu Is Present at a Legal Proceeding", content:"贾政奉命出任外省官员，离开京城。宝玉被带去旁听一起诉讼案件，见到了人情冷暖，世道炎凉，若有所悟。\nJia Zheng is appointed to a provincial post and leaves the capital. Bao-yu is taken along to observe a court proceeding, where he witnesses the cold realities of official justice and the cruelty of the world, and begins to understand what lies beyond the garden walls."},
{id:87, title:"感秋深抚琴悲往事，坐禅寂走火入邪魔", english:"Autumn Deepens and Daiyu Plays the Qin in Sorrow; Meditating, Miao-yu Falls Into a Trance", content:"黛玉在秋风中抚琴，回忆往事，悲从中来，弹出一曲哀音，令人动容。妙玉坐禅时走火入魔，精神大受刺激，颇为可虑。\nDaiyu plays the qin on a sorrowful autumn night, her music infused with all her longing and grief. Separately, Miao-yu falls into a dangerous trance while meditating, her unstable mental state a cause for concern."},
{id:88, title:"博庭欢宝玉赞孤儿，正家法贾珍鞭悍仆", english:"Bao-yu Praises an Orphan at a Family Gathering; Jia Zhen Flogs a Defiant Servant", content:"贾母设家宴，宝玉对巧姐百般爱护，令贾母欣慰。宁国府仆人仗势欺人，贾珍依家法予以惩处，整顿府中风气。\nLady Dowager hosts a family dinner, and Bao-yu's tender care for the little girl Qiao-jie warms her grandmother's heart. At Ning Mansion, an arrogant servant is publicly flogged by Jia Zhen to restore discipline in the household."},
{id:89, title:"人散后幽斋踏访，情深时药苦难言", english:"Visiting a Quiet Study After the Guests Depart; Words Fail When Feeling Is Deep and Medicine Is Bitter", content:"众人散去后，宝玉独自去探访黛玉，见其形容憔悴，心痛不已。黛玉强为宝玉宽心，实则自己已预感到命运将尽。\nAfter the family gathering disperses, Bao-yu visits Daiyu alone and is alarmed by how thin and pale she has become. Daiyu tries to reassure him, speaking cheerfully, but she herself already senses that her time is running out."},
{id:90, title:"失绵衣贫女耐嗷嗷，送果品小郎得觊觎", english:"A Poor Girl Endures the Cold Without a Padded Coat; A Boy Delivering Fruit Harbors Ill Intentions", content:"迎春嫁后受苦，冬日无棉衣御寒，贾府众人唏嘘不已。王仁之子送果品入府，心存觊觎，图谋不轨，贾家人警觉。\nYing-chun suffers greatly in her husband's household, enduring winter without warm clothing. The Jia family is saddened by her fate. A young man from the Wang family uses the pretext of delivering fruit to gain entry to the mansion, harboring ulterior motives."},
{id:91, title:"纵淫心宝蟾工设计，布疑阵宝玉妄猜疑", english:"The Licentious Bao-chan Sets a Trap; Bao-yu Falls Into Groundless Suspicion", content:"夏金桂的丫头宝蟾图谋不轨，设计诬陷香菱。宝玉因黛玉一事心存疑虑，胡思乱想，情绪不稳，令众人担忧。\nXia Jin-gui's maid Bao-chan schemes to frame Xiang-ling. Meanwhile, Bao-yu torments himself with unfounded suspicions and jealous imaginings regarding Daiyu, his emotional instability alarming those around him."},
{id:92, title:"评女传巧姐慕贤良，玩母珠贾政纳邪言", english:"Reading Women's Biographies, Qiao-jie Admires Virtue; Fondling Prayer Beads, Jia Zheng Accepts Slander", content:"巧姐读《列女传》，心慕贤良，立志以古代贤女为榜样。贾政听信谗言，对宝玉的言行更加不满，父子关系趋于紧张。\nThe little girl Qiao-jie reads Classic Biographies of Exemplary Women and resolves to emulate their virtues. Jia Zheng, misled by slanderous reports about Bao-yu's behavior, grows increasingly critical of his son, deepening the tension between them."},
{id:93, title:"甄家仆投靠贾家门，水月庵掀翻风月案", english:"The Zhen Family's Servants Seek Refuge with the Jias; A Scandal Is Uncovered at the Water Moon Convent", content:"甄家被抄，家人仆役前来贾家投靠。水月庵中爆出一起丑闻，庵中尼姑与人私通，令贾府大为尴尬，急忙掩盖处置。\nThe Zhen family suffers a government confiscation and their servants come to seek shelter with the Jias. A scandal breaks at the Water Moon Convent when a nun's secret liaison is exposed, deeply embarrassing the Jia family, who hurry to suppress the matter."},
{id:94, title:"宴海棠贾母赏花妖，失宝玉通灵知祸兆", english:"Enjoying Crab-apple Blossoms, Lady Dowager Senses an Omen; Bao-yu's Magic Jade Is Lost, Foretelling Disaster", content:"深冬海棠花反常开放，贾母觉得不祥。宝玉的通灵宝玉忽然失踪，众人遍寻不着，宝玉精神失常，痴呆起来，贾家大乱。\nA crab-apple tree blooms unseasonably in midwinter, and Lady Dowager senses that this is an ill omen. Then Bao-yu's magic jade suddenly disappears, and he loses his mind entirely, becoming vacant and incoherent. The whole household falls into panic."},
{id:95, title:"因讹成实元妃薨逝，以假混真宝玉疯癫", english:"A Rumor Becomes Reality: Yuanchun Passes Away; The Substitution Deceives and Bao-yu Loses His Wits", content:"贾元春在宫中病逝，贾家犹如塌了天。宝玉仍痴痴呆呆，贾母决定冲喜，为宝玉和宝钗定下婚事，以假婚来迷惑宝玉。\nJia Yuanchun dies in the palace, a devastating blow to the family. With Bao-yu still mentally absent, Lady Dowager decides that a wedding might restore him. She arranges for Bao-yu to marry Baochai, concealing the truth by letting him believe he is marrying Daiyu."},
{id:96, title:"瞒消息凤姐设奇谋，泄机关颦儿迷本性", english:"Xifeng Devises a Clever Deception; The Secret Leaks and Daiyu Loses Her Bearings", content:"王熙凤设计调包之计，令宝玉以为娶的是黛玉，实则是宝钗。黛玉得知消息后，病情急转直下，神志有些迷乱。\nWang Xifeng devises the substitution scheme that will allow the family to trick Bao-yu into marrying Baochai while believing he is marrying Daiyu. When word of this reaches Daiyu, her health collapses catastrophically and she begins to lose her grip on reality."},
{id:97, title:"林黛玉焚稿断痴情，薛宝钗出闺成大礼", english:"Lin Daiyu Burns Her Manuscripts and Breaks Her Lovesick Heart; Xue Baochai Leaves Her Chamber as a Bride", content:"黛玉在弥留之际，烧掉了宝玉赠予的手帕和自己的诗稿，口中喊着宝玉的名字，含恨而终。宝钗同时在拜堂成亲。\nDaiyu, in her final hours, burns the handkerchiefs Bao-yu sent her along with all her poems, calling his name with her dying breath. At the very same moment, Baochai is going through the wedding ceremony in the bridal chamber, becoming Bao-yu's wife."},
{id:98, title:"苦绛珠魂归离恨天，病神瑛泪洒相思地", english:"The Crimson Pearl Spirit Returns to the Realm of Sorrow; The Divine Attendant Weeps on the Earth of Longing", content:"黛玉死后，宝玉得知真相，悲痛欲绝，泪如雨下。新婚之夜，宝玉掀开盖头，发现新娘是宝钗而非黛玉，精神彻底崩溃。\nAfter Daiyu's death, Bao-yu learns the full truth and is overwhelmed with grief. On his wedding night, he lifts the bridal veil and realizes he has married Baochai, not Daiyu. His spirit breaks completely, and he falls into a deep mental collapse."},
{id:99, title:"守官箴恶奴同破例，阻求配情女自摧残", english:"A Wicked Servant Breaks the Rules He Should Enforce; A Lovesick Girl Harms Herself to Prevent a Forced Match", content:"贾家家奴仗势弄权，破坏官府规矩，为非作歹。迎春的陪嫁丫头司棋因恋情遭拆散，含冤而死，令人扼腕叹息。\nCorrupt Jia family servants abuse their master's connections to break the law. The maid Si-qi, whose love affair is forcibly separated, dies of a broken heart, another victim of the family's decline and the cruelty of those in power."},
{id:100, title:"破好事香菱结深恨，悲远嫁宝琴谱新词", english:"Xiang-ling's Happiness Is Destroyed, Leaving Deep Bitterness; Bao-qin Composes New Songs Before Her Distant Marriage", content:"夏金桂变本加厉，陷害香菱，香菱处境愈发艰难，心灰意冷。宝琴远嫁，临别前与众人依依惜别，赋词留念。\nXia Jin-gui intensifies her persecution of Xiang-ling, whose situation becomes increasingly desperate and hopeless. Bao-qin prepares for her distant marriage and composes farewell songs, taking leave of her friends in the garden with quiet sadness."},
{id:101, title:"大观园月夜感幽魂，散花寺神签惊异兆", english:"A Ghostly Presence Is Felt in the Garden by Moonlight; A Temple Oracle Foretells Strange Omens", content:"大观园在月夜中显得格外幽寂，有人疑见鬼魂出没，人心惶惶。凤姐去散花寺烧香，得一签文，语意不祥，心中忐忑。\nGrand View Garden seems haunted on moonlit nights, and fearful rumors circulate among the servants. Xifeng goes to a temple to burn incense and draws a fortune stick whose cryptic words fill her with unease and foreboding about her future."},
{id:102, title:"宁国府骨肉病灾侵，大观园符水驱妖孽", english:"Illness and Disaster Strike the Ning Mansion Household; Talismans and Holy Water Are Used to Drive Out Evil", content:"宁国府多人生病，人心惶惶，以为有邪祟作怪。贾珍请来道士作法驱妖，在大观园中贴符画水，折腾了一番，并无实效。\nSickness strikes Ning Mansion, and the frightened residents believe malevolent spirits are at work. Jia Zhen summons Taoist priests to perform exorcism rites throughout Grand View Garden, pasting talismans and sprinkling holy water, all to no avail."},
{id:103, title:"施毒计金桂自焚身，昧真禅雨村空谈禅", english:"Jin-gui's Poison Plot Backfires and Burns Her; Jia Yucun Talks Emptily of Zen", content:"夏金桂图谋以毒药害香菱，不料阴谋败露，反被自己的毒药所害，一命呜呼。贾雨村与人谈禅，不过是附庸风雅而已。\nXia Jin-gui's scheme to poison Xiang-ling is exposed, and through a twist of fate her own poison kills her. She dies as she lived, by treachery. Separately, Jia Yucun engages in showy discussions of Zen Buddhism, revealing himself as a man of hollow pretension."},
{id:104, title:"趁剩宴胡诌三种花，昧真禅雨村谈妄语", english:"At a Leftover Banquet, Three Flowers Are Fancifully Named; Jia Yucun Speaks More Empty Words of Wisdom", content:"贾家众人以残宴为乐，席间随口命名三种花，引出一番谈话。贾雨村自诩懂禅，实则不过是迎合权贵、趋炎附势之人。\nThe Jia household enjoys a casual leftover banquet. The conversation touches on flowers and their fanciful names. Meanwhile Jia Yucun, who has always curried favor with the powerful, presents himself as a man of spiritual insight while being nothing of the sort."},
{id:105, title:"锦衣军查抄宁国府，贾政主回赦恩旨", english:"The Imperial Guard Raids Ning Mansion; Jia Zheng Returns to Receive an Amnesty Decree", content:"朝廷派锦衣卫抄查宁国府，贾珍、贾蓉被拘押，贾家遭受重创。幸有圣旨颁下，贾赦、贾珍等人虽受处分，尚得保全。\nImperial guards raid Ning Mansion, and Jia Zhen and Jia Rong are taken into custody. The Jia family suffers a devastating blow. However, an imperial decree offers partial clemency; Jia She and Jia Zhen face punishment but their lives are spared."},
{id:106, title:"王熙凤致祸抱羞惭，贾太君祷天消祸患", english:"Wang Xifeng's Past Misdeeds Come Back to Haunt Her; Lady Dowager Prays to Heaven to Avert Disaster", content:"凤姐昔日弄权受贿的罪行被揭露，她在忧虑与病痛中一蹶不振。贾母在佛前长跪祈祷，请求上天保佑贾家度过难关。\nXifeng's past crimes of bribery and abuse of power are brought to light, and she collapses under the weight of illness and shame. Lady Dowager kneels for a long time before the Buddha altar, praying fervently for divine protection for the family."},
{id:107, title:"散余资贾母明大义，复世职政老沐天恩", english:"Lady Dowager Distributes Her Savings with a Magnanimous Spirit; The Family Title Is Restored Through Imperial Grace", content:"贾母将毕生积蓄拿出，资助贾家度过难关，展现出贾母的大义凛然。贾家世职得以恢复，贾政沐浴皇恩，暂渡难关。\nLady Dowager nobly donates her entire life savings to help the family through the crisis, demonstrating selfless generosity. Through imperial grace the family's hereditary title is partially restored, and Jia Zheng receives the favor that gives them breathing room."},
{id:108, title:"强欲夺宫花村妇惊，报私仇迷人应遭报", english:"A Village Woman Greedily Seizes the Palace Flowers and Meets with Fright; Private Revenge Brings Its Own Retribution", content:"王仁与贾芸合谋，将巧姐卖给藩王。所幸刘姥姥出手相救，巧姐被板儿之父接出，终得一个平淡安稳的归宿。\nWang Ren and Jia Yun conspire to sell the little girl Qiao-jie to a princely household. But Granny Liu intervenes and rescues Qiao-jie, who ultimately finds safety and a quiet life in the countryside, fulfilling the destiny foretold by her name."},
{id:109, title:"候芳魂五儿承错爱，还孽债迷人本帐难", english:"Wu-er Receives Mistaken Affection While Waiting for a Departed Spirit; Old Debts of Sin Are Hard to Clear", content:"宝玉精神恍惚，将柳五儿误认为晴雯，对其百般爱护，柳五儿虽受宠，内心却明白宝玉的心思始终在别处。\nBao-yu, still mentally confused, mistakes Wu-er for the ghost of Qing-wen and showers her with misplaced affection. Wu-er, though grateful for his care, understands that his heart is forever somewhere else."},
{id:110, title:"史太君寿终归地府，王凤姐力竭伏诛亡", english:"Lady Dowager Passes Away and Returns to the Underworld; Wang Xifeng Exhausts Her Strength and Dies", content:"贾母在忧郁中病逝，享年八十余岁，贾家失去了最后的精神支柱。王熙凤心力交瘁，在贫病交加中死去，红颜薄命。\nLady Dowager dies of grief and illness at over eighty years of age, and the family loses its last pillar of support. Wang Xifeng, her body and spirit utterly spent, dies in poverty and sickness, her brilliant and ruthless life ending in desolation."},
{id:111, title:"鸳鸯女殉主登太虚，狗彘奴欺天招雷殛", english:"Yuan-yang Follows Her Mistress in Death and Ascends to the Void; A Wicked Servant's Lies Are Struck Down by Thunder", content:"鸳鸯在贾母死后，以身殉主，以死报答贾母多年的知遇之恩，其忠烈之情令人感叹。作恶的仆人遭到报应，受天谴。\nYuan-yang takes her own life to follow Lady Dowager in death, fulfilling her oath of loyalty. Her sacrifice moves everyone who hears of it. A servant who had committed many evil acts receives his divine punishment, struck down as if by heavenly retribution."},
{id:112, title:"活冤孽妙尼遭大劫，呆根由不了旧时因", english:"Miao-yu Meets a Terrible Fate; The Foolish Root Cannot Escape Old Karma", content:"妙玉被贼人劫持，花落他处，从此下落不明，令宝玉等人扼腕叹息。宝玉自责，觉得妙玉之遭遇与自己的因果有关。\nMiao-yu is abducted by robbers, her fate thereafter unknown — one of the most poignant of the novel's many tragedies. Bao-yu is haunted by guilt, feeling that her fate is somehow entangled with his own karma."},
{id:113, title:"忏宿冤凤姐托村妪，释旧憾情婢感恩主", english:"Xifeng's Ghost Entrusts Her Daughter to the Village Woman; A Grateful Maid Repays an Old Debt of Feeling", content:"临死前，凤姐托梦刘姥姥，请她照看女儿巧姐，刘姥姥答应了。巧姐的贴身丫头在患难中对巧姐不离不弃，恩情可感。\nBefore dying, Xifeng's spirit appears to Granny Liu in a dream, entrusting her to watch over the little girl Qiao-jie. Granny Liu agrees. Qiao-jie's faithful maid remains by her side through all their hardships, showing true loyalty."},
{id:114, title:"王熙凤历幻返金陵，甄应嘉蒙恩还玉阙", english:"Xifeng's Spirit Revisits Jinling in a Vision; Zhen Ying-jia Receives Grace and Returns to the Imperial City", content:"凤姐的魂魄在临死前游历了金陵旧地，见到了昔日繁华的残迹，心生感慨。甄家蒙赦，得以返回，阴阳相照。\nIn a final vision, Xifeng's departing spirit revisits Jinling and the scenes of her former glory, now reduced to ruins and memories. The Zhen family, whose fate has always mirrored the Jia family's, receives imperial clemency and is permitted to return."},
{id:115, title:"惑偏私惊散投鼠计，欲绝凰失宝玉发癫", english:"A Scheming Plot Is Foiled by Misplaced Partiality; Bao-yu Goes Mad at the Loss of What He Loves", content:"贾环等人阴谋陷害宝玉，幸被识破。宝玉因黛玉之死的创伤，精神时常出现恍惚，终日痴痴呆呆，众人忧心如焚。\nA conspiracy by Jia Huan and others to harm Bao-yu is exposed and foiled. But Bao-yu remains spiritually shattered by Daiyu's death, wandering through his days in a daze, his vitality gone, to the deep worry of those who love him."},
{id:116, title:"得通灵幻境悟仙缘，送慈柩故乡全孝道", english:"Recovering the Magic Jade, Bao-yu Awakens to His Immortal Destiny; Escorting the Coffin Home Fulfills the Duty of Filial Piety", content:"通灵宝玉失而复得，宝玉精神有所好转。宝玉护送贾母灵柩回金陵祖籍安葬，此行令他对人生有了更深的感悟。\nThe magic jade is recovered, and Bao-yu's mind begins to clear. He accompanies Lady Dowager's coffin back to the ancestral home in Jinling for burial, and the journey deepens his understanding of impermanence, family, and what truly matters in a human life."},
{id:117, title:"阻超升聪明累聪明，送人情义兄薄义兄", english:"Cleverness Traps the Clever; A Supposed Brother Proves to Be No Brother at All", content:"贾雨村见贾家式微，开始落井下石，忘恩负义，昔日的恩情一笔勾销，令人感叹人情冷暖，世态炎凉。\nJia Yucun, seeing the Jia family's power wane, abandons his benefactors and actively works against them. His ingratitude is the bitterest commentary on the world of officialdom that the novel offers."},
{id:118, title:"记微嫌舅兄欺弱女，惊谜语妻子谏痴人", english:"A Grudge-Bearing Uncle Mistreats His Niece; A Wife Tries to Counsel Her Foolish Husband", content:"宝玉勘破尘缘，一心向佛，宝钗心痛劝说，宝玉婉言谢绝。贾家女眷各有际遇，巧姐在刘姥姥帮助下终得安宁。\nBao-yu sees through the vanity of the world and turns his heart fully toward the spiritual path. Baochai, heartbroken, pleads with him, but Bao-yu gently declines to be held back. The women of the family each face their separate fates, while Qiao-jie finds peace with Granny Liu's help."},
{id:119, title:"中乡魁宝玉却尘缘，沐皇恩贾家延世泽", english:"Bao-yu Passes the Imperial Examination Then Severs His Worldly Ties; Imperial Grace Continues the Jia Family Line", content:"宝玉在贾政的期望下参加科举，高中乡魁，完成了世俗意义上对家族的最后责任。随后便遁入空门，与贾政永别。\nBao-yu sits the imperial examination, passes with honors, fulfilling his last obligation to his father and the family name. Having discharged this duty, he renounces the world and disappears into the company of the monk and priest, taking his final leave of Jia Zheng."},
{id:120, title:"甄士隐详说太虚情，贾雨村归结红楼梦", english:"Zhen Shiyin Fully Explains the Land of Illusion; Jia Yucun Concludes the Dream of Red Mansions", content:"甄士隐向贾雨村详细解说太虚幻境的来龙去脉，点明全书的主旨：人生如梦，富贵荣华不过是一场空。红楼梦至此画上句号。\nZhen Shiyin appears to Jia Yucun and explains in full the meaning of the Land of Illusion and the great story that has unfolded. The novel's central truth is spoken plainly at last: life is a dream, and all glory, wealth, and love are ultimately empty. The Dream of Red Mansions comes to its close."}
]
};
